# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:12
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_7f31fb74:

    # "I make it in time for class, though not in time for breakfast."
    "我趕上了課堂，但沒趕上早餐。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:14
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_76acec4f:

    # "The classroom is bathing in the gentle light of the sun."
    "教室沐浴在暖陽溫柔的光中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:16
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_84b35954:

    # "This means that it's going to be intolerably hot in the afternoon. For now, though, it's pleasant."
    "這意味著下午會把人熱死的。不過至少現在，天氣很舒適。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:18
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ef36b290:

    # "I look at Misha and Shizune's animated discussion about whatever, Hanako staring out of the classroom window, Mutou stumbling into the classroom four minutes late and with no recollection of what he's supposed to be teaching today."
    "我看見米莎和靜音正興致勃勃地談論著什麼，華子望向窗外，武藤遲到了四分鐘，踉蹌地衝進教室，似乎想不起他今天要教些什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:20
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_bb7f4611:

    # "I could never imagine dropping out of school just like that, even if it's only for a few weeks."
    "我真是沒法想像像琳那樣曠課，哪怕只是數星期。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:22
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_bac92b0e:

    # "On the other hand, Rin doesn't seem to have a problem with the idea, or going through with it."
    "不過琳似乎對此沒什麼意見。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:24
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_5caa598f:

    # "Then again, somehow I got caught along in her insane isolation, even if we ended up hurting each other."
    "但是再一次，我又被拉入了她瘋狂的孤立世界中，哪怕我們最後總是傷害到對方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:26
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_9a496fce:

    # "Or did we? Maybe only I got hurt."
    "真的嗎？還是其實只有我受傷了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:31
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_3a907645:

    # "It takes me until late in the afternoon to realize that today is Monday. The art club meets today."
    "我到下午才意識到今天是週一。藝術社今天有活動。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:33
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_a416797a:

    # "Not just that. Due to the exams, this will be the last art club meeting before summer vacation."
    "不僅如此。由於考試，這次是藝術社在暑假前的最後一次聚會了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:36
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_c7a2ba03:

    # "I have no real business going there…"
    "我沒什麼去那兒的理由……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:38
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_692d23cb:

    # "But I want to talk with the teacher."
    "不過我想和老師談談。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:43
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_e0072604:

    # "So, I end up loitering awkwardly in front of the art room, waiting for the meeting to end."
    "於是，我便尷尬地在美術教室門前踱步，等著活動結束。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:45
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_cd742d22:

    # no "That's it for this trimester, everyone!"
    no "這個學期就到此為止了，大家！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:47
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_834b7f71:

    # "His voice is loud enough to be heard through the door and way too enthusiastic for it to be genuine."
    "他的聲音大到了隔著門都能聽清的地步，熱情得不可能是真誠的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:49
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2e218c04:

    # no "The next meeting is after summer vacations, on the Monday of the first week of next term."
    no "下次聚會是在暑假之後，下學期的第一個週一。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:51
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_931a477c:

    # no "I hope to see everyone there again!"
    no "希望到時候能再見到大家!"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:53
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2d4e2ee4:

    # no "Have a nice vacation!"
    no "暑假愉快！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:61
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_65ba730a:

    # "There's a confused answering chorus of voices, and the door to the classroom opens, releasing a flow of students."
    "傳起了一陣混亂的回答聲，教室的門打開了，一羣學生湧了出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:63
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_4ee3fa5a:

    # "I wait for everyone else to leave, so that I can talk to Nomiya alone. It's almost dinnertime, so I don't have to wait too long."
    "我等著大家都離開，以便和野宮單獨談話。現在已經快要到晚餐時間了，所以我不需要等太久。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:70
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ad927562:

    # "Without Rin, it feels pretty pointless to go there, but I want to talk with the teacher."
    "沒了琳，我感覺去那裡沒什麼意義，不過我想和老師談談。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:75
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_be2393a2:

    # "The meeting itself isn't noteworthy, just as my skills with water colors are not worth mentioning."
    "活動本身不值一提，就像我的水彩畫技一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:77
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_4fe8a008:

    # "Nomiya tries to encourage and advise me without sounding too condescending, but he's not doing a very good job of it."
    "野宮試圖鼓舞我，給我建議，他儘量讓自己聽上去不太屈尊，不過效果不太好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:79
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_46374257:

    # "If nothing else, joining the art club has taught me that I like art. It would be nice if I could actually try and make some art in the art club, though."
    "至少加入藝術社讓我意識到自己很喜歡藝術。不過，如果我能真的在藝術社裡做出一些藝術品就好了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:81
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_f0c94bcf:

    # "After the fruits of everyone's labor have been piled into a neat stack on the teacher's desk, he clears his throat to give a little speech."
    "當每個人的勞動成果都堆放在老師桌上時，他清了清嗓子，做了一番演講。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:86
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_cd742d22_1:

    # no "That's it for this trimester, everyone!"
    no "這個學期就到此為止了，大家！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:88
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ad24b41e:

    # "His voice is pretty loud and way too enthusiastic for it to be genuine."
    "他的聲音很大，而且熱情得不像是真的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:93
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2e218c04_1:

    # no "The next meeting is after summer vacations, on the Monday of the first week of next term."
    no "下次聚會是在暑假之後，下學期的第一個週一。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:95
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_931a477c_1:

    # no "I hope to see everyone there again!"
    no "希望到時候能再見到大家!"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:100
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2d4e2ee4_1:

    # no "Have a nice vacation!"
    no "暑假愉快！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:107
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_8ad95814:

    # "Everyone wishes him a nice vacation back as they file out the door."
    "每個人都祝願他假期愉快，同時湧出了門。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:109
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6f112a37:

    # "I stay behind, waiting until the two of us are alone. It's almost dinnertime, so I don't have to wait long."
    "我站在後面，等著只剩下我們兩個人。已經快到吃晚餐的時間了，所以我不必等多久。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:111
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_980d9bf6:

    # "Nomiya is looking through the paintings, some of which are actually pretty nice."
    "野宮正在看那些畫，有的其實很不錯。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:113
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_fb54616f:

    # "Rin might outclass everyone else in the art club, but she isn't the only one with talent."
    "琳可能超過了這班裡的所有其他人，但她不是唯一一個有才華的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:115
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_54219272:

    # hi "Excuse me, teacher…"
    hi "打擾一下，老師……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:122
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_54034757:

    # no "Hmm? What is it, Nakai?"
    no "嗯？什麼事，中井？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:124
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_3aab9384:

    # "He raises his eyebrows questioningly, smiling widely."
    "他疑惑地揚起了眉，大大咧咧地笑了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:126
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_31f4c323:

    # hi "It's about Rin…"
    hi "關於琳的事……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:131
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_36329094:

    # no "Oh? Is something wrong with Tezuka?"
    no "噢？手塚遇到了什麼問題嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:133
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_fc0a34fe:

    # hi "No, but…"
    hi "沒有，不過……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:135
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_d38f6202:

    # "I hesitate for a split second, not certain how to say what I want to say, giving Nomiya enough time to start blabbering by himself."
    "我躊躇了一秒，不知該怎麼說出來，結果野宮自己開始說個不停了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:140
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_e4bf3b74:

    # no "I saw her a few days ago when I was passing by at Sae's gallery."
    no "幾天前我去紗枝的畫廊時看見她了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:142
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_337601cf:

    # no "She said she'd get one or two more paintings done for the exhibition."
    no "她說她只用再為畫展畫一兩幅畫了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:147
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_8b9867f4:

    # no "I was quite pleased, she's a surprisingly hard worker. I'd always thought she was a bit lazy, doing what she wants instead of the assignments…"
    no "我挺高興的，她非常努力。我一直覺得她有些懶，總是做自己想做的事，把任務放在一邊……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:149
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_9f26bea0:

    # "He seems to notice my anxiety and realizes he is digressing, shutting up before finishing the thought."
    "他似乎注意到了我的焦躁，意識到自己在跑題，於是在說完前便停了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:154
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6257930d:

    # no "Ah, but you had something to talk about. What is it?"
    no "啊，你好像有話要說。怎麼了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:156
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_38c55f9b:

    # hi "I don't know… she feels detached from everything, as if she can't think of anything but the exhibition."
    hi "我不知道……她給人感覺像是和一切都疏遠了，像是她除了畫展外什麼都不去想一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:161
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_9f0b7322:

    # no "Well, isn't that good? She is focused on her painting, as she should be."
    no "啊，真是好，對吧？她在全神貫注地畫畫，就該那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:163
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6a3888e3:

    # hi "Yeah, but this is different. It's like she's obsessed. I went to see her, and…"
    hi "是啊，但這不一樣。像是她著了魔。我想要見她，而且……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:168
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ced88658:

    # no "Have you been bothering her?"
    no "你在打擾她？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:170
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_58bc905f:

    # "He cuts in before I finish saying what I meant to say, instantly looking quite irritated."
    "還沒等我說完想說的話，他就插嘴了，立刻變得惱怒起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:172
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_76d971b7:

    # hi "No… I don't… think so."
    hi "沒……我不……覺得。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:174
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_c9025062:

    # hi "I'm just concerned because she's stopped coming to school completely. She feels strange, too."
    hi "我只是擔心，她已經完全不來學校了。而且她給人感覺也不對勁。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:176
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ea4d8105:

    # hi "Stranger than usual, at the very least."
    hi "至少，比平常更不對勁。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:181
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2be6fe65:

    # no "Humbug! This is much more important for her than some lousy math class, or physics, or whatever."
    no "胡扯！這對她來說比什麼鬼數學課要重要得多，還有什麼物理，那種東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:183
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_49df6569:

    # no "This is exactly why this school is so flexible, to give every student a chance to fulfill themselves."
    no "所以這所學校才這麼靈活，能給每個學生一個實現自我的機會。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:188
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_07931ba5:

    # no "Tezuka is a painter, so she should paint, no? And have an exhibition. That's what artists do. She should be allowed to concentrate on that, not these other frivolous classes. She should be encouraged."
    no "手塚是個畫家，所以她該畫畫，不對嗎？還有畫展，那才是藝術家該做的事。她應該有機會把注意力集中在那上面，不是去操心其他無聊的課。她應該得到鼓勵。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:190
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_1f5efcfb:

    # no "If you think about it, it's really quite obvious."
    no "如果你仔細想想，會發現這事挺明顯的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:192
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_46db08e4:

    # "His counterarguments are not very convincing, but I'm having a hard time trying to make any kind of rebuttal."
    "他的反駁不是很有說服力，不過我想不出回應的話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:194
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_3c6f0e91:

    # "My grudging silence is interpreted as assent, and Nomiya turns to shuffle the stack of turned-in assignments on his desk like a deck of cards."
    "我勉強的沉默被理解成了默認，野宮開始整理那摞上交的作業，像是在整理一副撲克牌一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:199
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_4fd197c4:

    # no "I have to say, while we're talking about Tezuka's exhibition…"
    no "我得說，一談到手塚的畫展……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:201
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_7f74f1ac:

    # no "I'm very excited to see how it turns out."
    no "我就等不及想看看它結果怎樣了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:206
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_d0e69e36:

    # no "She's still so young, yet has such wonderful skill, and style!"
    no "她還這麼年輕，技巧和風格卻如此精妙絕倫！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:208
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_95a73d61:

    # "He's talking to the air, to relax the mood that got a bit too negative."
    "他對著空氣說著，想讓有些消沉的氣氛輕鬆起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:213
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6bbc934c:

    # no "I take it that you will be attending?"
    no "我猜你是要去看的吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:215
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_028d71b4:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess so."
    hi "嗯，應該是吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:220
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_5e0f21ac:

    # no "Well, we'll meet there next."
    no "哦，那我們就在那兒見了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:227
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_d991f2c6:

    # "I take that as my cue to leave. And I do, although I'm not happy about it."
    "我把那當作了讓我離開的信號。我也確實離開了，雖然感覺一點也不滿意。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:229
translate zh_hant a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ca80d7e4:

    # "My message didn't get through, to say the least."
    "毫不誇張地說，我想說的東西完全沒被聽見。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:240
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:249
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ff53f23f:

    # n "{vspace=270}The day after that, all the missed opportunities and things I should have said come crashing down on me. There's nothing left to do afterwards but brood."
    n "{vspace=270}那天之後，所有錯失的機會和該說出的話都砸落在了我身上。除了在鬱悶中等待外，我什麼也做不了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:251
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:258
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_9afb296f:

    # n "{vspace=270}Second day. I begin to feel anxious. I start doubting my doubt and it feels stupid, especially since I still can't think about anything else than Rin."
    n "{vspace=270}第二天，我開始感到焦慮。我開始懷疑自己的疑慮，而且感覺蠢極了，尤其是考慮到我除了琳之外什麼都想不了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:260
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:267
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e59a7803:

    # n "{vspace=270}Third day. Japanese exam, {b}and{/b} world history exam. Great. The thing I hate most about her is that she can make me feel this awful even though I should be focusing on entirely different stuff right now."
    n "{vspace=270}第三天是日語考試，{b}以及{/b}世界歷史測驗。棒呆了。我最恨她的一點，就是當我像現在這樣，應該把精力集中在完全不同的事上時，她還是能讓我感覺糟糕透頂。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:269
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:276
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_7bd0d1d0:

    # n "{vspace=270}Fourth day. Math exam. We have a math exam. It goes how it goes. I don't care."
    n "{vspace=270}第四天，數學測驗。我們有一場數學測驗。該怎樣就怎樣吧。我不在乎了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:278
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:285
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_c189afa1:

    # n "{vspace=270}Fifth day. Nomiya asks me again if I will attend the exhibition opening. I can't say no to him even though I seriously want to. I just don't want to discuss with him anything Rin-related so it's just better to take the path of least resistance."
    n "{vspace=270}第五天，野宮又問我要不要去畫展開幕式。我正經考慮過拒絕，但沒法這麼做。我只是完全不想和他談論任何同琳有關的事，所以最好還是選擇那條摩擦更少一些的路。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:287
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:296
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_784a49fa:

    # "On the sixth day, the day before the exhibition opening, I find Rin standing in the hallway in front of my room when I return to the dorms after dinner."
    "第六天是畫展開幕前的一天，當我吃完晚飯回寢室後，發現琳就站在我房間前的走廊裡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:300
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_31192155:

    # hi "What are you doing here?"
    hi "你在這兒幹嘛？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:302
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_6b0080ca:

    # "My tone is angrier than I intended. I'm a little disappointed that I was unable to restrain myself, but it can't be helped."
    "我的語調比預期的要憤怒。我有些失望自己竟然無法自控，但我也沒辦法。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:304
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_7b1bc929:

    # "Rin just stands there, like she just happened to coincidentally be standing around here where she has no business being. The way she reacts so coolly to everything annoys me now."
    "琳就站在那裡，像是她只是碰巧站到了這個她沒理由去的地方一樣。她對任何事的反應都是那麼冷靜，我開始覺得煩了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:306
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76bb851c:

    # "This is not good. It's been six days, and the sight of her has me boiling. She hasn't even opened her mouth yet."
    "這可不好，已經六天了，她的身影卻還是能讓我沸騰起來。她都還沒開口。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:311
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_574f5625:

    # rin "Finished painting."
    rin "畫完了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:313
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_0339551f:

    # hi "Shouldn't you be at the gallery? Preparing?"
    hi "你不是該在畫廊裡嗎？準備東西？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:318
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_32e621dd:

    # rin "They said no."
    rin "他們說不行。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:320
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_59f480b4:

    # "I guess the gallery owner does that part then, getting the paintings framed, hung on the walls and whatnot."
    "那我猜是畫廊主人在負責那部分了，裝裱畫作，把它們掛在牆上之類的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:322
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_72b47445:

    # hi "So, why are you here?"
    hi "那，你來這兒幹嘛？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:327
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_94a52e1f:

    # rin "Felt like it."
    rin "想要來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:329
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_6bdaaf03:

    # "This same old stupid pattern emerges again; me asking her questions to which she replies with answers that don't answer anything, because it's the only other way we can converse."
    "那種老一套的愚蠢模式又出現了；我問她問題，然後她用什麼也不能回答的話去回答，因為這就是我們能交流的唯一方式。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:331
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_663541e5:

    # "Apart from me listening to her blabbering about whatever, which isn't really a conversation."
    "除了那種我聽她不停胡言亂語的情況，不過那不算什麼交流。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:333
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_794ad679:

    # "Is this a play? Are there some unseen roles that we have unknowingly set ourselves into, dictating the rules of engagement whenever we see each other, inevitably leading to us hurting each other?"
    "這是場戲嗎？我們是不是無意間變成了一些角色，每次相遇時都要簽訂一份交戰協議，最終都不可避免地傷害對方？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:335
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_d4744e37:

    # "Her nonchalant answers accompanied by even more nonchalant shrugs leave me none the wiser. I guess I should be happy that the exhibition preparations are complete."
    "她那種若無其事的回答還要伴隨著更加若無其事的聳肩，讓我什麼也搞不懂。我猜我該慶幸畫展的準備工作已經完成了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:343
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_eb7842ab:

    # "When I walk into my room, I hear her footsteps following me in."
    "當我走回房間時，聽見她的腳步跟了進來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:345
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e50c3695:

    # "I didn't invite her in. I won't ask her to leave."
    "我沒邀請她進門。我也不會讓她出去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:359
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_51c8ea4c:

    # "She claims my bed without asking permission, making me wish that I had taken the time to make it before I left in the morning, then stands up again as though she sat on hot coals."
    "她沒取得許可，就坐在了我的床上，讓我後悔自己早上沒花點時間去整理一下，接著她又站起來了，像是坐到了熱炭上一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:364
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_76d044ed:

    # "I half-lean against the single corner of my desktop that isn't cluttered with stuff, to rest my legs at least a little bit."
    "我半靠著自己的桌上唯一沒堆滿東西的桌角，儘量讓自己的腳休息一下。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:369
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_9fc28e0d:

    # "Rin spends a few moments glancing curiously around my room. It makes me realize that she's never seen it before."
    "琳花了一些時間好奇地打量我的房間。讓我想起她之前從沒見過這裡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:371
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ad9059a3:

    # "For a moment, she actually looks like she's concentrating. Trying to get everything. This must be the eye for detail that makes her an artist."
    "有一瞬間，她看上去像是真的集中了注意一樣。試圖記住每一件事。一定是這種對細節的捕捉能力讓她成為了一個藝術家。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:376
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_15d65c2d:

    # "Since the room is small, she quickly runs out of things to look at, but nothing else transpires, allowing the uncomfortable silence to take over the atmosphere."
    "因為房間很小，她很快就找不到可以看的東西了，不過什麼也沒發生，一種令人不安的寂靜佔據了房間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:378
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_449f3709:

    # "The mood is chilly to say the least, and both of us are on guard, waiting for the other to make the first move."
    "那種感覺讓人不禁發寒，我們兩人都很警惕，等著對方邁下第一步。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:380
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_88ca76fd:

    # "Of course, Rin could play this game forever. So it has to be me."
    "當然，琳是可以把這遊戲一直玩下去的。所以開口的只能是我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:382
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_c85221a4:

    # hi "So…"
    hi "然後……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:384
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_2a535c94:

    # "I give up because she'd never try to open conversation, and because it seems that she wants to say something, and I want to get it over with."
    "我放棄了，因為她從來就不會去嘗試發起對話，因為她看起來想要說些什麼，我想要趕緊讓這情況結束。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:386
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_d7cffadc:

    # "Why else would she be here if she didn't want to talk?"
    "如果她不想說話，還來這兒幹嘛？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:388
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_14925818:

    # "I don't know what to say myself. I want to be angry, but I can't bring myself to yell at her or anything."
    "我也不知該說什麼。我想要發火，但沒法去吼她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:390
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_b908b896:

    # "My voice catches her attention, and she tries to search for words as well, but it seems that she is not entirely certain as to why she's here either."
    "我的聲音引起了她的注意，她也在試圖找詞說，不過看來她也不是很明白為什麼自己會在這兒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:400
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e3b745d1:

    # "And so, Rin simply takes a few steps to close the distance between us and rises on the tips of her toes to even out the height difference…"
    "於是，琳只是簡單地向前走了幾步，縮短了我們之間的距離，然後墊起腳尖，抹去了我們之間相差的身高……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:407
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_4cf20e4a:

    # centered "'It was a bad idea.'"
    centered "“這是個壞主意。”"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:409
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_b2968db4:

    # centered "'Maybe you should forget about it, and I will too.'"
    centered "“可能你應該把它忘了，我也一樣。”"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:413
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_90729675:

    # "It's a reflex, and almost as an afterthought, the words 'no,' 'yes' and 'maybe' simultaneously surface inside my mind."
    "這是一道本能反應，幾乎像是事後的想法，“別”，“好的”，還有“也許”，這些詞同時在我的腦海中浮現。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:415
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_d38d5f1d:

    # "My hand is between her lips and mine, a wall that I raised to guard against… something."
    "我的手擋在了她的脣和我之間，一道牆，被我鑄起來防衛……某事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:417
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_2bc22592:

    # "Her breath feels warm against my fingers. The scent of her skin lingers about, the mysterious indescribable sensation that captures me and draws my eyes deep into hers."
    "她的呼吸在我的手指上留下了暖意。她皮膚的清香依舊繚繞，一種無法描述的神祕感受捕獲了我，把我的目光牽引進她的眼中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:424
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_fb68f57c:

    # "The look in her eyes is surprised, quizzical as to why the impertinent hand prevented her advances."
    "她眼裡的神情非常驚訝，不知道為什麼會有一隻手擋住了她前進。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:426
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_03c5f631:

    # "Her eyes are really big and glistening with moisture, and staring right into my own with a soft gaze that I'm having a hard time to match."
    "她的眼睛真的很大，潮溼，閃閃發亮，用溫柔的目光直直地望進我的眼裡，我有些難以回視。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:428
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_03b9a4e4:

    # "Rin's half-open mouth makes her look even more confused, although the sensual way her lips are arching is signaling something completely different."
    "琳的嘴半張著，讓她看起來更困惑了，雖然她的嘴撅起的方式充滿情慾，在暗示全然不同的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:433
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ce0164c3:

    # rin "Please."
    rin "求求你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:438
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_1f1699db:

    # rin "I need you."
    rin "我需要你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:440
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_d927605a:

    # "The words come from her throat as a coarse whisper meant only for me, bypassing her tongue and teeth without giving them any chance to interrupt."
    "這句話直接從她的咽喉中傳出，變成了一道沙啞的耳語，僅僅是為了我而存在的，越過了她的舌頭和牙齒，不給它們任何妨礙的機會。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:447
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_acecb949:

    # "They sober me in an instant, and I clumsily flinch back to get a little bit of distance between us, painfully scraping against my desk in the process."
    "它們讓我立刻清醒過來，我笨拙地向後退了一步，以防和她靠得太近，同時痛苦地撞在了我的桌上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:449
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_c77bf8b9:

    # "Maybe it's her choice of words, maybe the way she says it, but something in it puts me off."
    "可能是因為她選詞的方式，可能是因為她說出來的感覺，不過那話中有東西讓我感覺很不舒服。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:451
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_9cc620ed:

    # "Something is wrong, something is terribly wrong again."
    "有東西不對勁，再一次，有的東西出了很嚴重的問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:453
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_25827a5e:

    # hi "Need me for what?"
    hi "需要我幹嘛？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:455
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e9163df2:

    # "All the unpleasant feelings emerge again, and I feel my heartbeat suddenly increasing at least tenfold."
    "所有那些不快的感受又出現了，我感覺自己的心跳驟然加快了十倍。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:460
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e17041e2:

    # "Rin's eyes go out of focus and back again as her body relaxes from its tensed state, and she stands upright again."
    "琳的眼睛失焦了，然後再次恢復，她的身體不再緊繃，又變成了直直的站姿。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:465
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_0bc155f7:

    # rin "I don't think I was thinking about anything. Why do you draw patterns in that dust on your night table?"
    rin "我不覺得我在想任何事。為什麼你要在床頭櫃上的灰裡畫畫？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:470
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_8c166848:

    # rin "There is a word for that kind of thing but I can't remember…"
    rin "有一個詞是說那種事的，但我記不清了……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:472
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_c2ef6a90:

    # "Her remark almost throws me off track and I glance over her shoulder at the small table next to my bed, but I can't see anything from this distance."
    "她的回覆幾乎讓我分了神，我越過她的肩膀去看自己床頭的小桌子，但沒法從這裡看到任何東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:474
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_456d4f56:

    # "So she needs me for nothing specific?"
    "也就是說，她不是為了任何別的事需要我的？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:476
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_deea301b:

    # "Just happened to come by because she thought I'd be glad to see her after she shut me out, no complaints accepted, for a week."
    "僅僅是來看看我，因為她以為我會在她把我踢開一星期，一句抱怨也不聽後還想見到她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:478
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_a00b83cc:

    # "Completely altruistic motives?"
    "完全無私的動機？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:480
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_329b80b2:

    # "Felt like it?"
    "只是想要來而已？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:482
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_909db814:

    # hi "Bullshit. I can answer myself."
    hi "狗屁，我自己都能回答。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:484
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_9fc58eff:

    # hi "To play mind games with whenever you want, to kiss whenever you want, to ignore whenever you want, to fulfill your whims whenever you want?"
    hi "是為了有人能讓你隨時耍著玩，隨時想吻就吻，想忽視就忽視，隨時能滿足你那些奇思怪想？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:486
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_f97a24e8:

    # hi "Is that it? What you need me for?"
    hi "是這些嗎？你就是為了這些需要我？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:488
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_0cfbf71f:

    # "My voice is sounding very angry again, even to myself."
    "我的聲音再次變得非常生氣了，連我自己聽起來都是。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:490
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_809d2f18:

    # extend " Good."
    extend " 很好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:495
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_a1c3fdcc:

    # "Rin too finally catches the mood and her curious expression changes instantly to something more uncharacteristic."
    "琳也終於意識到了我的語調，她好奇的表情立刻變成了某種異常的神色。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:500
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_13f95aea:

    # rin "No—"
    rin "不是的——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:502
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e282de84:

    # "She leaves it at that, her eyes restlessly wandering around, searching the room as if the words she tries to find were written in the tapestries of my walls."
    "她就這麼停住了，眼睛不停地四下張望，搜索著整個房間，像是那些她想說的話都寫在我的牆紙上一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:504
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_a461d02c:

    # hi "Then what?"
    hi "那是為什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:511
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_9af4a2f2:

    # rin "I needed to paint."
    rin "我需要畫畫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:513
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ad9b967e:

    # "Paint."
    "畫畫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:515
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_21700daa:

    # "Of course. That's what artists do."
    "當然了，那就是藝術家們做的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:517
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_06be40c7:

    # "The words reverberate through my being, beating in my blood over the piercing whistle of my anger."
    "那個詞在我的整個存在中迴盪，在我的血液中撞擊，混在我嘯叫著的怒火中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:521
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_01704145:

    # hi "Don't give me that, Rin! I'm not some damn muse of yours, free to play with for the sake of painting!"
    hi "別給我說那些，琳！我不是你的什麼鬼繆斯，為了畫畫可以隨便玩弄！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:523
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_5489b14d:

    # hi "I am not some medium for whatever you aspire to, I am me!"
    hi "我不是什麼你靈感的介質，我是我！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:525
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_26a3fc06:

    # hi "So what if I don't know anything about my future?"
    hi "對，我不知道自己以後會發生什麼，那又怎樣？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:527
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_da898656:

    # hi "There's things I want, and things I care about! Even I can dream of things other than nightmares!"
    hi "我有現在想要的事，現在關心的東西！誰都會夢見除了噩夢以外的事，就算是我也一樣！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:529
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_18b372de:

    # "I'm yelling, but I'm way past the point of caring about things like that."
    "我在喊了，但是我已經邁過了在乎這些事的時刻。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:534
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_6368f21f:

    # "Rin looks down at her toes and wiggles them a little melancholically while she takes in my outburst without saying anything to defend herself."
    "琳低頭看著自己的腳趾，憂鬱地扭著它們，承受著我的怒火，沒說一句話為自己辯解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:536
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_3478eebe:

    # "Only after I have finished does she try to respond somehow."
    "當我說完後，她才試著回應。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:541
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e5d99da7:

    # rin "I can't do anything else. Or I can do all sorts of things, but I… can't… do."
    rin "我沒法做別的事。或者說，我可以做很多事，但我……不能……做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:546
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_3ef381c4:

    # rin "It's the only thing I sort of do properly. Most of the time."
    rin "這是我唯一能做好的事。大多數時候。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:548
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ffcb8c64:

    # "I understand completely. Art first, everything else second, or thousandth."
    "我完全懂。藝術第一，別的一切都是第二，或者在千里之外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:550
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_c2142b2f:

    # hi "What about me? Am I nothing? When I was interested in art, did that make you feel like I was a little interesting, for a little while?"
    hi "那我呢？我什麼都不算？當我對藝術感興趣的時候，你覺得我只是在稍微感興趣，只是在暫時感興趣？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:552
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e245d512:

    # hi "Tell me. I really want to know. Did you ever think about my perspective, or is it just all you?"
    hi "告訴我。我真的想知道。你有從我的角度想過一次嗎，還是所有的一切都只是為了你？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:554
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_a3f931d8:

    # "The words rise like bile in my throat."
    "這些話像膽汁一樣在我的咽喉中湧起。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:559
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e34a9b74:

    # "She looks alarmed. And also completely uncomprehending, as if she just doesn't understand what I'm angry about."
    "她看上去有些驚恐。同時徹底茫然無知，像是根本不能明白我為什麼要生氣一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:561
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_10996ab4:

    # "I can't believe she could be so stupid."
    "我真不敢相信她竟會這麼蠢。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:566
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_d0190ebc:

    # rin "I didn't want to—?"
    rin "我不是想要——？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:568
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_9fbe4b85:

    # "This time it's Rin who interrupts herself in midsentence."
    "這次是琳自己把自己說的話給截斷了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:573
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_5f8cd9ff:

    # rin "Don't you understand? I can't."
    rin "你不明白嗎？我不能。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:575
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_b046783b:

    # hi "Can't what?"
    hi "不能幹嘛？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:577
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_bf421548:

    # hi "You never explain! How am I supposed to understand anything if you never say anything?"
    hi "你從來不解釋自己！如果你從不解釋自己，我怎麼可能弄懂任何事？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:579
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_fbab08c2:

    # hi "Why don't you ever talk?"
    hi "為什麼你從來都不說？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:581
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e360754c:

    # hi "Say something!"
    hi "說些什麼啊！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:583
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_0c8eefa8:

    # "But she doesn't."
    "但她沒有。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:585
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_2dc193f7:

    # "Venting my anger at her feels satisfying. It feels wrong to take so much satisfaction in it, but I can't stop."
    "對著琳發泄讓我感到滿足，同時這種滿足也讓我感覺很糟糕，可我就是停不下來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:590
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_3348afb5:

    # "Not wanting to face my anger head-on, Rin turns around to steadfastly look out of my window even though there is nothing to look at."
    "琳不願直面我的怒火，於是轉身，堅定地望著我的窗外，雖然外面什麼東西也沒有。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:592
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_74f1b510:

    # "The worst of my ire gone, I shut up as I can't be bothered to keep on yelling at the back of her head, so silence finally returns."
    "我怒意中最糟糕的那部分已經消失了，沒再開口，因為我沒法繼續對著她的腦後勺大吼，於是寂靜終於重回房間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:594
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_1a0101c7:

    # "I try to discern some hints of her reaction through my adrenaline-distorted vision."
    "透過被腎上腺素扭曲的視線，我試圖從她的反應中分辨出一些暗示。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:596
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_57528871:

    # "My feedback was not the best kind, but I hope Rin got the clue that she just can't ignore everything else whenever she feels like it."
    "結果不是太好，不過我希望琳已經明白了，她不能如她所願那樣，隨時忽略任何人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:598
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_c5280ef1:

    # "I'd hate it if she didn't. She never ever listens to anything, she's so unaffected by the world around her."
    "如果她沒弄明白，我真要發火的。她從來不去聽任何事，全然不會被周身的世界影響。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:600
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_159f59d9:

    # "Not this time, it seems."
    "不過看來這次不會了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:602
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_1371e84c:

    # "Her body is shaking like from holding back tears, but I already know that Rin is not crying."
    "她的身體在顫抖，像是在忍回淚水，但我早已明白琳是不會哭的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:604
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_4c154e58:

    # "Her indifference made me so furious. Now that it's gone, I'm at a loss. I wonder…"
    "她的冷漠曾讓我那麼憤怒。可現在怒火已經消失了，我感到迷惘，不知所措。我在想……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:606
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_4966d1e6:

    # "Did I go too far?"
    "我是不是太過分了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:608
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ca81d4a9:

    # hi "Look, I—"
    hi "聽著，我——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:613
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_1149e5d6:

    # rin "Go away."
    rin "走開。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:615
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e6915669:

    # rin "Go away, Hisao."
    rin "走開，久夫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:617
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_958e171d:

    # "Her voice is tiny and tired as she says this, but I hear the words clear as day."
    "她說這話時的聲音微弱又疲勞，不過我清楚地聽到了它們。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:619
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:621
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_e0f03b86:

    # "What is there to say any more?"
    "還有什麼能說的呢？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:623
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_7f393299:

    # hi "This is my room."
    hi "這是我房間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:625
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_7ec7dab5:

    # "The blunt, hollow remark is a fitting conclusion for this unpleasant discussion that became an even more unpleasant and very one-sided yelling match."
    "用這句直白空洞的話來結束這段不快的對話，再適合不過了，對話已經因為單向的怒吼變成越來越煩人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:630
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_2cbb4a3b:

    # "After a moment of collecting herself Rin just gives up, I can see it from the way she slumps her shoulders, and walks out."
    "琳調整了片刻，最後放棄了，我能從她聳下的肩看出來，她走出了門。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:635
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_af16ff33:

    # "Even though she deliberately looks to the other direction, I can see how she's biting the corner of her lip so hard it might start bleeding if she won't stop."
    "就算她在刻意看向另一個方向，我也能看見她正在咬著自己的嘴角，非常用力，假如她不停下來的話，可能會流血的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:637
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_81325e86:

    # "As she makes her exit, I realize that she left the door open when she came in and my yelling must've echoed around the dorm hallways."
    "她走出去後，我意識到她進來時沒關門，我的叫喊一定已經傳遍宿舍的走廊了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:639
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_64b0036f:

    # "I sigh. Now that she's gone, I am left alone with my guilt."
    "我嘆一口氣，現在她走了，只留下了我和自己的愧疚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:641
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_91dd6dfe:

    # "As the thumping in my chest slowly subdues, anxiety replaces it."
    "我胸中的撞擊聲逐漸減弱，變成了焦慮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:643
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_07372464:

    # "Somehow, I feel that none of this would've ever happened if not for me."
    "我有種感覺，如果不是因為我，所有的這一切都不會發生。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:645
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_be3e51ff:

    # "No matter how infuriating, unbearable and outrageous Rin is, she is not the Rin I thought I knew."
    "不論琳有多麼令人惱怒，讓人無法忍受，讓人容易被傷害，她也不是那個我以為自己了解的琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:647
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_17f8e076:

    # "The Rin that I expected Rin to be."
    "那個琳才是我希望琳成為的樣子。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:649
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:651
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_87b374e0:

    # "Was it me who caused all this by talking Rin into taking her chances with the exhibition?"
    "難道我才是那個說服琳去嘗試畫展，造成這一切的人嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:653
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_2ec4fcb3:

    # "Am I directly responsible for Rin becoming like she has been for the past weeks?"
    "琳變成最近幾個星期的樣子，我是不是該負直接責任？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:655
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_daa1faec:

    # "I can't think of any other explanation for her weird behavior than the exhibition and all the things that came along with it."
    "我想不出該怎麼去解釋她的反常舉止，除了這次畫展和所有隨之而來的事之外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:657
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_c3e57bc0:

    # "Maybe it was the only way that could have brought us closer, but all it did was separate us further away from each other, and now beyond the reach of either of us."
    "或許這曾是唯一能把我們變得更近的方式，不過最後的結果卻僅僅是把我們分開得更遠了，讓我們互相變得遙不可及。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:662
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_6e0c50f7:

    # "I bang my head hard against the wall."
    "我把頭向牆撞去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:669
translate zh_hant a4_rin_demused_498da18b:

    # "Twice, to make sure it hurts."
    "撞了兩次，確保我會疼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:686
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_e9ec2627:

    # "A headache is relentlessly thumping against the back of my head as I push open the door to the 22nd Corner."
    "當我推開二十二號街角的門時，頭疼不停地撞擊著我的後腦勺。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:688
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_4ec2eeed:

    # "Apart from that, I'm perfectly calm."
    "除此之外，我非常冷靜。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:692
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:695
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_69ee39bd:

    # n "{vspace=60}After venting on Rin all that anger that I had bottled inside, it felt like a great weight had been lifted from my heart."
    n "{vspace=60}我向琳發泄過所有那些鬱積在心中的怒火後，感覺心頭的一塊重物被挪走了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:697
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_18b060d2:

    # n "The tension that had grasped my mind for the past few weeks faded away without leaving even a shadow behind."
    n "過去數星期裡攥著我心的緊張感已經消失，不留一點痕跡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:699
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_35b9b761:

    # n "In this nearly Zen-like state of enlightenment I realized that perhaps it was a bad idea to yell at her like that."
    n "在這種近乎禪意的狀態中，我悟到了朝她大吼可能是個壞主意。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:701
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a6e98ad6:

    # n "{vspace=30}I really meant it, but what good does blowing up like that do? Nothing."
    n "那些話都是真心的，但那麼發火有什麼用？什麼用也沒有。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:703
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_de0cf754:

    # n "I am not like that. I don't normally yell at people. I don't know why I did yesterday."
    n "我不是那樣的人。我通常不會朝人大吼。我不知道為什麼自己昨天會變成那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:705
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_3256da36:

    # n "So I keep feeling really guilty about it and wanting to take my words back."
    n "所以我一直非常愧疚，想要收回說出的話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:707
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5d9486bc:

    # n "{vspace=60}Rin is probably upset too. Even more than my own behavior, her reaction shocked me."
    n "{vspace=60}琳可能也生氣了。和我自己的行為相比，她的反應讓我更震驚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:709
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_18a0c250:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=30}I've always thought of her as unchanging, detached from her surroundings so that seeing my yelling get her so upset felt… out of place."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=30}我一直認為她是泰然不變的，超然於周身的一切之外，所以當我看見自己的怒吼讓她變得心煩意亂時，我感覺……很奇怪。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:713
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_23cfa8b2:

    # n "{vspace=30}I wonder if she understands how I feel?"
    n "{vspace=30}她知道我的感受嗎？我想知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:715
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a416026e:

    # n "In Rin's world everything seems to be so absolute and subjective… absolutely subjective, as if she was completely unable to see things from other points of view than her own."
    n "在琳的世界中，一切都顯得那麼純粹主觀……純粹的主觀，像是她根本沒法從其他人的角度看世事一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:717
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_492227c4:

    # n "But ultimately, is anyone able to do it? Maybe objectivity and altruism are just illusions for people who like to think of themselves as compassionate."
    n "不過說到底，有誰真的不一樣嗎？或許客觀和利他主義不過是一道幻象罷了，只是那些認為自己充滿同情的人的一廂情願。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:719
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_84f03e94:

    # n "Just like art is an illusion for people who think reality is merely a veil for something greater."
    n "就如同在那些認為現實不過是一層遮蔽更偉大事物的面紗的人眼中，藝術也是一道幻象一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:721
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_c9f1153e:

    # n "Even when you stop thinking that the world revolves around you or start thinking outside of the mythical box, you are just inside another, bigger box that you can't escape."
    n "就算當你停止幻想世界是圍繞你而轉的，開始讓思想越過那個虛幻的盒子，你也只是到了另一個更大的盒子裡而已，無法逃脫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:723
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_c70301ec:

    # n "{vspace=30}Maybe that, ultimately, makes her like the rest of us."
    n "{vspace=30}或許出於這些原因，我們說到底都是和她一樣的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:727
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:740
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_d25001ff:

    # "I step through the door to find a gallery full of illusioned people."
    "我走進了門，看到畫廊裡充滿了幻象一般的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:742
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_3da58e1f:

    # "Despite Sae's remarks during my earlier visits I always thought it was very spacious, but now when it's crowded like this it looks positively cramped."
    "雖然紗枝在我先前拜訪時說了相反的話，但我一直認為這裡面是非常寬敞的，可現在，裡面已經被擠得水泄不通了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:747
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_cc50cec4:

    # "I immediately notice Sae standing in the middle of a lively discussion, busily chattering with some old gentlemen."
    "我立刻注意到紗枝正忙著同一位老紳士喋喋不休地談論。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:749
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_c361493f:

    # "She's actually pretty tall and kind of cool-looking, so she stands out in the crowd."
    "她比較高，而且看上去也挺酷的，所以在人羣中顯得出類拔萃。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:751
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a9ce38bc:

    # "There are a few dozen wine glasses laid on the tables along the back wall, filled with burgundy liquid. A vast majority of the guests are sipping from their own glasses."
    "黑牆邊的桌上有幾個酒杯，裝滿了深紫紅色的液體。大多數客人都在用自己的杯子喝。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:753
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_7cd827ac:

    # "The socialites and art connoisseurs are mingling happily, exchanging mild opinions about Rin's art which seems to be a secondary object of interest for most."
    "社會名流們和藝術鑑賞家愉快地攀談著，就琳的畫作交換著溫和的意見，不過對大多數人來說，這只是次要的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:755
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_d46da2da:

    # "I feel distanced, excluded from the other people here."
    "我感覺錯了位，被和這裡的其他人隔開了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:757
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_73ce016d:

    # "I can't claim even at a stretch to be a social chameleon, so this situation is quite unnerving."
    "我可一點都不算社交變色龍，所以這情況讓我非常緊張。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:759
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_6f96359c:

    # "Since I don't blend into the crowd at all, I just fake that I do, trying to look as cool and smooth as I can."
    "既然我完全沒法融進人羣中，便開始假裝，盡力讓自己看起來酷一些，圓滑一點。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:761
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_6d98206a:

    # "I wonder how Rin is handling all this. If it was me, I would be quite freaked out."
    "我想知道琳是怎麼應對這一切的。如果換做我，恐怕早就發瘋了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:769
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_cdc85e8e:

    # "Throwing the anxiety aside, I try to carefully navigate through the crowd, stealing peeks at the framed paintings now hanging on the walls."
    "我撇開了緊張的心情，小心翼翼地試著穿過人羣，偷偷看牆上那些裝裱好了的畫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:778
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_e37f01d4:

    # "Rin's exhibition takes about half of the gallery's wall space. Some paintings are less familiar than others, but I recognize most of them."
    "琳的畫展佔據了畫廊一半的牆。有的畫比別的畫更陌生，不過我還是認出了它們中的大多數。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:780
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_8051b9a2:

    # "Some I've seen being created at the club meetings after all, or remember from the time when Rin was choosing her portfolio."
    "畢竟有些是我看著她在畫室裡畫出來的，有的我記得在看琳選代表作時見過。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:782
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5c9641bc:

    # "I note that a couple of the unfinished paintings are framed and on the wall as well. Maybe that's what they call coincidental art?"
    "我注意到幾幅未完成的畫也被裝裱後掛在了牆上，或許他們說的巧合藝術就是這個？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:784
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_afe8fadc:

    # "Even Rin's failures, if you can call them that, became exhibits of her skill. Quite paradoxical."
    "哪怕琳的失敗之處，假如你能這麼說的話，也變成了對她技巧的展示。想起來挺矛盾的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:792
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_36595355:

    # "She herself is nowhere to be seen, which is strange because even though it's crowded, the gallery {b}is{/b} pretty small."
    "但哪兒都看不到她本人，這很奇怪，因為就算畫廊裡非常擁擠，這裡其實也{b}確實{/b}挺小的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:794
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_78ea3f71:

    # "It's fine, sort of. I don't know how to face her after yesterday. Maybe I shouldn't have even come."
    "不過沒關係，算是吧。我不知道該怎麼在昨天之後再面對她。或許我根本不該來的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:796
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_b7b167a0:

    # "But I promised various people, Rin included, that I would, so…"
    "不過我已經向不少人保證過會來了，包括琳，所以……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:798
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_43093a63:

    # "Damn, it sounds like I do the things I do because some kind of instinctual properness compels me to, not because it would be sensible (or not)."
    "真該死，聽上去像是我做這些事只是因為某種發自本能的守信行為罷了，和這麼做明不明智沒一點關係。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:808
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_993ea1ac:

    # "I sneak closer to Sae to wait for a lull in the conversation so I can chat her up too."
    "我溜到了紗枝身旁，等著談話出現空隙，以便和她搭訕。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:810
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_0ca65725:

    # "Even though her voice is almost completely buried under the general background noise, I hear bits and pieces of her talking about Rin."
    "雖然她的聲音幾乎完全被背景聲給埋沒了，我還是聽到了一些有關琳的隻言片語。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:812
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_3022a3f0:

    # sa "Yes, she is a high schooler at a local school… even though she's graduating next year I'm sure various art schools would be interested in…"
    sa "對，她在本地的一所學校讀高中……不過她明年就畢業了，我相信不少藝術學校都會有興趣……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:814
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5c97a6ee:

    # sa "…I thought it'd be interesting to have an exhibition of someone who is still in early stages of development…"
    sa "……我覺得為一個還在創造初期的人舉辦畫展挺有意思……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:816
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_206f5e36:

    # "It's so strange, it's like Rin is some kind of mini-celebrity even though this is nothing but a small exhibition opening at a small art gallery of a small town."
    "真奇怪，像是琳變成了某個小名人一樣，雖然這只不過是一次在小畫廊裡舉辦的小型畫展而已，還是在一個小鎮中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:818
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_07764980:

    # sa "In fact, there is a friend of mine from…"
    sa "事實上，我有一位朋友就是來自……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:823
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_40554ac7:

    # mystery "It's Hisao!"
    mystery "久夫！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:825
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_de462b46:

    # "My eavesdropping is interrupted by a familiar voice and a familiar slap to the back. I don't need to guess the source of either, even without turning around."
    "我的偷聽被一個熟悉的聲音打斷了，背上還捱了熟悉的一掌。我不用轉身，也能猜中是誰。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:827
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_2b3d4056:

    # hi "Hi Emi."
    hi "嗨，笑美。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:848
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_29e755bd:

    # emi "Hi! Are you like, a representative of the art club or something? I don't see anyone else from the school here…"
    emi "嗨！你是，呃，美術社的代表之類的什麼嗎？我都沒在這看到我們學校的其他人……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:853
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a594f5be:

    # hi "Umm… I don't know, really. I guess I am if that's the case."
    hi "呃……我不知道，真的。如果真是那樣的話，那我猜我算是吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:855
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_0583026f:

    # hi "What about you?"
    hi "你呢？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:860
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_de967264:

    # emi "What about me?"
    emi "我怎麼了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:862
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_f5a21f62:

    # hi "Err…"
    hi "呃……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:867
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_517d1d91:

    # emi "You didn't think I'm interested in art? Is that it, Hisao?"
    emi "你不覺得我對藝術感興趣？是不是，久夫？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:869
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_15f22183:

    # hi "No, that's not what I… well, maybe a little, if you put it that way."
    hi "不是，我不是那個……嗯，不過既然你這麼一說，可能有一點點。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:871
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a1c1b2d5:

    # hi "I mean, even though you hang out with Rin I've never heard you talk about art with her so…"
    hi "我是說，雖然你總是和琳在一起，但我從來沒聽你和她談過藝術，所以……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:876
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_83589a0d:

    # "Emi huffs and looks around her, looking discontented."
    "笑美嗤之以鼻，看了看四周，有些不滿。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:881
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_3e44e17a:

    # emi "It's true, I don't get it at all, but she came to my track meet so I thought it's only fair to return the favor."
    emi "沒錯，我一點都不懂，不過她都來看我的田徑賽了，所以我覺得應該回報一下。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:886
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_06111ba7:

    # "She leans closer, trying to look confidential but only managing to look conspiring."
    "她靠近了一些，試圖作出一副保密的神情，卻只讓人感覺像是在策劃陰謀。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:888
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_8221bfd4:

    # emi "Do you {b}get{/b} art?"
    emi "你{b}懂{/b}藝術嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:890
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_2c690564:

    # hi "No. No, I don't."
    hi "不懂。不，我不懂。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:892
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_689872df:

    # hi "At all."
    hi "一點都不懂。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:897
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_cce5fcc8:

    # "My emphasizing headshake draws a giggle and a cheery headshake of her own out of Emi."
    "我表示贊同的搖頭讓笑美咯咯笑出聲來，接著她自己也愉悅地搖了搖頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:902
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5b34a6d0:

    # emi "Me neither!"
    emi "我也一樣！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:907
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_b195e96f:

    # emi "Hey, let's go talk with Rin! I bet you haven't yet, because I haven't either."
    emi "喂，我們去找琳去！我打賭你還沒去找她，因為我也一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:912
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_269bc9d0:

    # emi "Come on!"
    emi "走吧！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:930
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a32ed3ae:

    # "Before she has a chance to forcefully drag me to Rin, Nomiya appears behind her with Rin in his tow."
    "還沒等她有機會用力拽著我去找琳，野宮就在她背後出現了，身後帶著琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:939
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_9160c98c:

    # "She's not dressed for the occasion, instead opting for the usual school uniform and unkempt hair."
    "她沒有穿什麼特別的衣服，只是一身平常的校服，以及蓬亂的頭髮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:941
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_f236e970:

    # "Maybe her natural look is what suits her the best."
    "可能她平常的模樣就是最適合的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:946
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_03739b69:

    # emi "Hello, teacher! Hi, Rin!"
    emi "你好，老師！嗨，琳！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:948
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_c73fdc78:

    # "Unfazed, Emi greets the teacher cheerfully, causing him to turn around and look down confusedly."
    "笑美泰然自若地向老師問好，讓他轉身困惑地低頭看去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:953
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_e5a20256:

    # no "Who are you?"
    no "你是誰？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:958
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_34fed68d:

    # emi "I'm Emi, from school, class 3-4. Don't you remember?"
    emi "我是笑美，我們學校的，3-4班，你不記得了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:960
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_89bce785:

    # "She looks positively shocked at the prospect that there could be a person who doesn't know her."
    "她看上去異常震驚，竟然會有一個不認識她的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:965
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_11ee8254:

    # no "Oh, sorry. You are in the same class as Tezuka is, right?"
    no "噢，抱歉。你和手塚是一個班的，是吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:970
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_b286e85a:

    # emi "Yeah!"
    emi "對！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:975
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_1daed64e:

    # no "You'll have to pardon me, I have trouble remembering students who don't take art."
    no "原諒我，我有些記不住那些沒選美術課的學生。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:980
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_f8e4b68f:

    # emi "Don't mind, don't mind!"
    emi "沒事，沒事！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:985
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_f9024bee:

    # emi "Hi Rin!"
    emi "嗨，琳!"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:990
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "你好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:995
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_9cda1dad:

    # emi "Congratulations for your super cool art thing! I'm sure you'll be a big hit!"
    emi "恭喜啦，這些藝術東西超級酷的！我覺得你肯定會變成個大名人！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:997
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_aed72305:

    # "She throws her arms into the air for boisterous emphasis, almost hitting me in the face."
    "她把雙臂在空中揮了揮，以示強調，差點打中了我的臉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1002
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a21e593c:

    # emi "And look, Hisao came too!"
    emi "還有，看吶，久夫也來了！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1007
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5f559886:

    # "Rin doesn't look at me, nor does she greet me."
    "琳沒看我，也沒向我問好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1009
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_503fd49a:

    # hi "Congratulations, Rin."
    hi "恭喜了，琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1011
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_08fc470e:

    # "She keeps averting her gaze, pointedly looking at her sandals."
    "她不停地避免目光接觸，直直地盯著自己的涼鞋。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1016
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_649d4c9b:

    # "Oblivious to the tension between us and ignorant of what happened yesterday, Emi keeps on blabbering about this and that to an unresponsive Rin."
    "笑美全然不顧我們間緊繃的氣氛，也無視昨天的事，繼續喋喋不休著，對著毫無反應的琳呱呱說個不停。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1018
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_e9294ae9:

    # "I guess she's used to not getting much out of her at times."
    "我猜她已經習慣琳偶爾什麼反應都沒有的時候了"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1043
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_e99d6ce1:

    # "Before long, Nomiya and Sae turn to Rin, introducing her."
    "不久後，野宮和紗枝就轉向了琳，開始介紹她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1045
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_9aa74b97:

    # "Expecting it, I catch the second of confusion when the guests see her arms."
    "不出所料，當客人們看見她的手臂時，露出了數秒的迷惑。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1050
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_6d88c598:

    # "Sae is luckily on the ball and briefly explains about our school."
    "好在紗枝掌控著局面，簡單地介紹了一下我們的學校。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1052
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_f47b727b:

    # "Doubtful faces quickly change to curious."
    "懷疑的神色立刻變成了好奇。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1054
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5f14c8e3:

    # "Man" "Would you mind telling us something about your art?"
    "Man" "男人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1056
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_68f9a3e4:

    # "Man" "I thought the development is quite easily noticeable, what do you yourself think of the differences between the older and more current works?"
    "Man" "男人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1058
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_98907ffb:

    # "Man" "It's quite rare for someone so young to dabble into abstraction."
    "Man" "男人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1060
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_4e19473e:

    # "Woman" "It would've been interesting to see how you work!"
    "Woman" "女人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1062
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_4834f385:

    # "Man" "Oh, definitely! I assume you use your feet? Must've been a great trouble to learn it, you should be proud."
    "Man" "男人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1067
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_7c641666:

    # rin "I… ummm…"
    rin "我……嗯……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1071
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_888dbb6e:

    # "Man" "Will you be pursuing a career as an artist after school?"
    "Man" "男人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1073
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_1598f9c5:

    # "She is bombarded with so many questions she can't even hope to answer all of them."
    "她被那麼多的問題同時圍攻，根本不可能全部回答它們。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1075
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_08ee072a:

    # "Maybe that's for the best, Rin tends to talk nonsense more than occasionally."
    "或許這樣最好，琳常常會口吐胡言。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1077
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_4da16c57:

    # "Man" "So where do you get your ideas?"
    "Man" "男人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1082
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_673dbc28:

    # rin "That's the fourth, I mean fifth worst…"
    rin "這是第四，我是說，第五個最糟的……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1084
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_ed5867c3:

    # "Rin keeps stumbling with her words, looking more and more vexed by the expectant inquiries."
    "琳繼續結結巴巴地說著，看上去被這些期盼中的提問者弄得越來越煩了。。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1089
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_b7f8fd67:

    # rin "Ah…"
    rin "啊……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1091
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_cecd7896:

    # "Everyone is waiting for her to say something, but she looks like a cat got her tongue."
    "每個人都在等著她開口，可她看上去像是被貓搶走了舌頭似的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1093
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_b75b20f1:

    # "Each question piling up just adds to her distress."
    "問題一個疊一個，讓她愈發煩惱。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1098
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a86cd36d:

    # "I fail to hear the question that is the proverbial one too many."
    "問題實在是太多了，我根本聽不過來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1100
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_225297ac:

    # "It's like a motor stalling."
    "簡直像是熄火中的引擎。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1121
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_7fd81128:

    # "Rin just freezes for a long, long second until she falls on her knees, hitting the floor ungracefully like a sack of potatoes."
    "琳凝住了很長，很長的一段時間，然後跪倒在了地上，像是一袋土豆一樣笨拙地撞在了地上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1123
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_be781a3f:

    # "Woman" "Are you all right?"
    "Woman" "女人"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1125
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_48efa8e6:

    # rin "I don't know…"
    rin "我不知道……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1127
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_96e070f8:

    # no "Tezuka? What's wrong, girl?"
    no "手塚？怎麼啦，姑娘？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1129
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_eab25463:

    # rin "I don't know what's wrong…"
    rin "我不知道出了什麼事……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1131
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_f080eb7f:

    # "A terrible silence falls upon the people gathered around Rin."
    "人們在琳周圍聚集，寂靜向四周蔓延開來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1133
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_2a09f94f:

    # "Everyone is petrified, not knowing how to react to her sudden… seizure, or something."
    "每個人都被石化了，不知該如何應對她突然間的……發作，算是發作吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1135
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_2e170a2d:

    # "She breathes with deep, trembling gasps as if she was running out of air, staring ahead of herself with hollow eyes."
    "她深深地吸著氣，發著顫，像是缺乏空氣一樣，用空洞的眼睛盯著前方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1154
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_3b57b7b5:

    # "Seeing that nobody does anything, I force myself to step to Rin and lift her up from the floor, letting her lean against me to keep standing."
    "我見沒人有任何行動，便逼著自己上前把琳從地上扶了起來，讓她靠著我站穩。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1156
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_b605b41d:

    # hi "Would you like some fresh air? OK, let's go outside for a bit."
    hi "你想出去透透氣嗎？來吧，我們去外面走走。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1158
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a01b4bc5:

    # "I don't even wait for her to answer before grasping her shoulder and pulling her past the stunned-looking Nomiya, Sae, Emi and guests."
    "我根本沒等她回答，直接抓住她的肩膀，把她帶過目瞪口呆的野宮，紗枝，笑美，還有所有的客人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1160
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5ae85c24:

    # hi "Excuse us."
    hi "麻煩讓一下。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1169
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_47ff5bf3:

    # "The cool evening breeze hits my face at the door."
    "清涼的夜風在門開後吹向了我的臉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1174
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_769ae004:

    # "I let go of Rin and she leans against the stone wall, trying to catch her breath."
    "我放開了琳，她靠在了石牆上，試圖穩定呼吸。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1176
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_dd0872f3:

    # hi "Are you all right?"
    hi "你還好嗎?"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1181
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_5d06bfbe:

    # rin "I couldn't say anything…"
    rin "我什麼都說不出……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1183
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_b64b1686:

    # "Rin is still not looking at me, so I look away too."
    "琳還是沒去看我，所以我也看向了一邊。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1187
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_16b8f65c:

    # "The streetlights and colored neon signs twist my vision into a blur of near-blindness, forcing me to look back."
    "街燈和色彩繽紛的霓虹標識扭曲了我的視野，將它變成一片耀目的模糊之光，讓我不得不移開視線。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1189
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_1a60359f:

    # "At least she talks, even if she's not directing her words to me."
    "至少她開口了，就算不是在朝我說話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1191
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_2ff399c8:

    # hi "What did you want to say?"
    hi "你想要說出什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1193
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_78de87e9:

    # "Maybe both of us can imagine that we are talking to an invisible friend."
    "可能我們兩人都能幻想自己正在和一個想像中的朋友談話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1198
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_4e7ade8d:

    # rin "I don't know."
    rin "我不知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1203
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_a1c846a2:

    # rin "Something that would have meant something."
    rin "一些能意味著一些東西的東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1205
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1207
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_7a537113:

    # "The silence lasts for a long time."
    "沉默持續了很長一段時間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1209
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_4eef4039:

    # "I don't feel comfortable being alone with Rin. I am not good at imagining things that don't exist, do… or that things that exist, don't."
    "我感覺和琳單獨待在一起很不自在。我一點也不擅長想像出不存在的事……或是把存在的事情想成不存在。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1211
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_28aa5a0b:

    # hi "We should go back in."
    hi "我們該回去了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1213
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_4b5021f3:

    # hi "The guests Sae invited are in there, they probably want to meet you and talk with you."
    hi "紗枝邀請的客人都在裡面，他們可能想要見見你，和你說話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1215
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_ccc3e9d3:

    # hi "You know, ask you questions and stuff. About those paintings you worked so hard for."
    hi "你明白的，問你問題之類的。問問那些你花了那麼大勁去畫的畫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1220
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_3304ddd5:

    # rin "I don't want them to ask me questions like that. I can never say the right things."
    rin "我不想讓他們問我那些問題。我從來就說不對話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1222
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_75fa03c0:

    # hi "What do you want then?"
    hi "那你想要什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1224
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1231
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_scene_ef00f851:

    # rin "That someone wouldn't have to ask questions from me." nointeract
    rin "一個不用問我問題的人。" nointeract

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1254
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1257
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_d72a268b:

    # n "{vspace=60}Vacation, huh?"
    n "{vspace=60}假期，對吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1259
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_329304f8:

    # n "Some people will stay at the school even over the holidays, some will go back to their families."
    n "有的人在假期裡也會留在學校，有的會回家。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1261
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_8784e275:

    # n "I probably should make the trip back home and report to my parents that I'm alive and well."
    n "我或許應該回趟家，告訴父母我還活著，過得不錯。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1263
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_a9ed5746:

    # n "{vspace=30}Not much to do at the school anyway, I suppose."
    n "{vspace=30}反正，在學校也沒什麼事做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1265
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_53975cd8:

    # n "Next trimester will be stressful. Everyone will have to seriously start thinking about what to do after graduation."
    n "下個學期壓力會很大的。每個人都必須嚴肅地為畢業後的將來考慮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1267
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_dc5d6e2d:

    # n "{vspace=60}Including me…"
    n "{vspace=60}包括我……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1271
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1277
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_ee4c3c2d:

    # "A look at my doodles convinces me to stop trying to salvage them. It's a mess of lifeless lines, a waste of paper if it wasn't the flip side of my exam."
    "我看了一眼自己的塗鴉，意識到應該放棄補救它們了。那只是一堆毫無聲息的亂線，假如作畫的地方不是我的試卷背面，那我還浪費了一張紙。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1281
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1284
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_7ea49f73:

    # n "{vspace=90}Maybe it's because I didn't really set out to draw anything in particular."
    n "{vspace=90}或許是因為我沒有挑什麼特別的東西去畫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1286
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_3a273586:

    # n "I just wanted to kill some time, so the drawing became exactly like I am."
    n "我只是想要耗耗時間而已，所以那些畫看上去就像我自己一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1288
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_fb104aa5:

    # n "Without a direction to go to."
    n "不知何去何從。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1290
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_bdb42e04:

    # n "{vspace=60}It'd be easier if I had some special talent, like Rin."
    n "{vspace=60}如果我有一些特殊的才華的話，會容易得多，就像琳那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1292
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_e6acf50c:

    # n "She has it easy."
    n "她畫得就那麼輕鬆。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1294
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_103f5a47:

    # n "It makes me kind of jealous."
    n "讓我有些嫉妒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1296
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_f33578dd:

    # n "It pisses me off that she herself can't seem to be happy about it."
    n "可她自己卻總是沒法滿足，我真是有些氣憤。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1300
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1307
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_0e057b53:

    # mu "Aaaand… time!"
    mu "啊~哈，時間到了！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1309
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_e5356afe:

    # "Mutou's call for the end of the exam draws groans of displeasure from half the class."
    "武藤宣佈考試結束，讓班上一半的人都發出了不滿的抱怨聲。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1311
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_3b0137b6:

    # "I don't blame them, the exam was kinda tricky."
    "我不怪他們，這次考試挺難的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1313
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_d8faab67:

    # "Mutou expects a lot from our class, even though he's not strict at all. I guess he'd like all of us to become scientists."
    "武藤對我們班的期望很大，雖然他一點也不嚴厲。我猜他希望我們所有人今後都能當科學家。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1318
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_9586a0ba:

    # mu "Put down your pencils and turn in your papers please."
    mu "麻煩大家把筆放下，交上試卷。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1320
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_1457f049:

    # "The biggest groan comes from the desk to my side."
    "最響亮的那聲抱怨來自我旁邊的桌子。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1334
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_eb0752fd:

    # "Misha's despair is almost tangible."
    "米莎的絕望幾乎可以被看見。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1336
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_a623fe97:

    # "The dark aura of lost hope emanating from her seat makes me simultaneously frightened of and sympathetic to her."
    "她的座位上散發著一種希望全無的黑暗氣氛，讓我同時對她產生了擔心和同情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1341
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_7a348718:

    # mu "Now then, there should be homeroom before you are free, but I only have a few announcements to make so this should be over quickly…"
    mu "現在，在你們解放前應該還有一次學生大會，不過我只有幾件事要交待，所以應該不會佔多少時間……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1343
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_91fd800a:

    # "His announcements are never important, so I listen to him only with one ear."
    "他交待的事從來不會是重要的，所以我聽得很心不在焉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1345
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_cb89b0f0:

    # "Misha seems to be too down in the dumps to even pretend attentiveness."
    "米莎似乎完全陷入了消極的心情裡，連專心聽都懶得裝了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1347
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_239b2154:

    # "She slumps her head against the desktop, looking stricken."
    "她把頭擱在了桌上，看上去奄奄一息。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1349
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_273b3860:

    # hi "Cheer up, Misha."
    hi "振作一點，米莎。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1351
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_5729ea2e:

    # hi "It's vacation! Don't worry about the test."
    hi "已經放假了！別擔心考試了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1356
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_f5ce562e:

    # mi "Thanks, Hicchan."
    mi "謝了，小久。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1358
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b6fb34fa:

    # "Her frown becomes a small smile, and a sparkle of excitement lights in her eyes."
    "她皺眉的表情變成了一個微弱的微笑，一點點激動的神色在眼中點亮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1363
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_6d2eb729:

    # mi "What're you going to do over your summer vacation, Hicchan?"
    mi "你暑假裡準備做什麼，小久？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1368
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_a16a5be9:

    # mi "I'm going to Shicchan's place, they have this awesome and super cool mansion! I'm so excited~!"
    mi "我要去小靜的家玩，他們有棟超級酷炫的宅邸！我超級興奮~！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1373
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_6b4afc3d:

    # mi "I'm sure it'll be the bestest summer vacation ever~!"
    mi "我肯定，這會是最爽的暑假的~！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1375
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_a1a6f5e9:

    # "She seems to have forgotten all about her misery in a few seconds and bounces up and down on her seat as if to pump up her excitement."
    "她似乎在幾秒鐘內就忘記了所有的苦悶，在座位上上下跳動，像是要為她的激動打氣一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1377
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b725356d:

    # hi "I don't really have any plans, I guess…"
    hi "我應該沒什麼打算吧，我猜……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1382
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_afb19d07:

    # mi "Is that so~? Maybe you should—"
    mi "真的嗎~？可能你應該——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1387
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_4c5bd624:

    # "A finger tapping her shoulder steals Misha's attention away from me."
    "一根手指碰了碰米莎的肩膀，把她的注意力轉移了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1392
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_9e779258:

    # "Shizune points to Mutou, who is expectantly looking back at the two of them."
    "靜音指了指武藤，他正期待地回視著她們兩人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1397
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b24d56ea:

    # mi "Oops! Sorry, Shicchan, I didn't notice teacher finished already, ehehe~."
    mi "噢！抱歉，靜音，我都沒注意到老師已經說完了，呵呵嘿~"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1399
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_6c3c9bf1:

    # "She clears her throat and takes a deep breath…"
    "她清了清嗓子，深吸一口氣……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1405
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_745cb1ff:

    # mi "Stand!"
    mi "起立！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1407
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_6fe3f787:

    # "I stand up with everyone."
    "我和大家一起站了起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1411
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1414
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_6cc7d4ef:

    # n "{vspace=60}Since I came here, I've always wondered about something."
    n "{vspace=60}自從我來這裡以後，就總是在琢磨一件事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1416
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_e7fa89db:

    # n "What do the wheelchair-bound students think about this daily tradition, being unable to do it 'properly?'"
    n "那些被固定在輪椅上的學生們會怎麼看待這種每日的慣例？他們可沒法“正確地”服從。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1418
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_26d00bbf:

    # n "Is it a faux pas to keep to this tradition in a place that bypasses many others for convenience?"
    n "這地方已經省略掉很多其他的傳統做法了，卻依然保持著這一種，難道不是有些失禮嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1420
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_19bacfc2:

    # n "Even though I never asked anyone, during these short weeks here I've come to the conclusion that they definitely are not insulted."
    n "雖然我從沒問過任何人，不過在這裡短暫的三週裡，我已經意識到他們一點也沒感覺自己受到了侮辱。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1422
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_c4785b31:

    # n "They understand."
    n "他們都理解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1424
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_ef0629f8:

    # n "That's what I like about this school. Nobody is too uptight about anything, everyone is so… considerate and understanding of each other."
    n "這正是我喜歡這學校的一點。沒人太神經過敏，每個人都那麼……理解對方，為對方考慮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1428
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_bd48d49c:

    # n "{vspace=60}I wish the whole world could be like this."
    n "{vspace=60}真希望整個世界都能如此。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1432
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1438
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_7b28a49b:

    # mi "Booooow!"
    mi "鞠~躬！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1446
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_6b23919b:

    # "I turn the page slowly, listening to the rustling sound the paper makes when my fingers grasp it."
    "我緩緩地翻著書頁，聽著書頁在手指間發出的沙沙聲。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1450
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_6:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1453
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_86da4edd:

    # n "{vspace=30}I'm restless."
    n "{vspace=30}我感覺焦躁不安。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1455
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_675b692c:

    # n "It's the summer vacation."
    n "已經是暑假了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1457
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_411e7189:

    # n "No class, no homework, no art club meetings. Just free time to spend however I want."
    n "沒有課，沒有作業，沒有藝術社團的聚會。全是由我自由處置的空閒時間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1459
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_d7334c86:

    # n "It doesn't feel like anything."
    n "但是卻讓人什麼感覺都沒有。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1461
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_04741731:

    # n "I tried to cheer up Misha, but I'm not feeling too cheery myself."
    n "我試圖讓米莎振作起來，可我自己卻不怎麼振作。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1463
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_bc409793:

    # n "To be honest, the free time is intimidating. It reminds me of the hospital and the long, meaningless days that had to be filled somehow."
    n "說實在的，這些空閒時間實在是有些嚇人。它們讓我想起了自己在醫院裡的日子，那些漫長，無意義的日和月，不得不想方設法地去把它們填滿。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1465
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_965a7f41:

    # n "The only difference is that there I was bound to the ward, guarded by the Cerberus-like nurses."
    n "唯一的區別是，在那裡我是被困在病房裡的，被地獄看門犬一般的校醫守著。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1467
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_12f67585:

    # n "Reading was a good solution back then, but the thought of spending my summer vacation reading books feels… nerdy."
    n "在那時，閱讀是個不錯的解決方法，不過一想到我要花整個暑假去讀書了，我就感覺……一股書呆子氣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1469
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_a98c4e1c:

    # n "That has nothing to do with the fact that I'm reading even now… I'm just killing time and trying to fight my anxiety."
    n "雖然我現在也在讀書，不過那不一樣……我現在只是在消耗時間，試圖抹去自己的焦慮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1471
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_ac10d3df:

    # n "Besides, my mind is on other matters, stretching in too many directions to make sense of any of them."
    n "再說，我正在想別的事，思緒向太多的方向延伸了，以至於什麼都想不清。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1475
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_7:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1478
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_8860c35a:

    # "Thus, the book I've been on since Tuesday is progressing s{w=0.3}l{w=0.3}o{w=0.3}w{w=0.3}l{w=0.3}y{w=0.3}."
    "所以，那本我從週二就開始讀的書真是顯得{w=0.3}漫{w=0.3}無{w=0.3}盡{w=0.3}頭{w=0.3}。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1480
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_4e28a1bf:

    # "It feels like this book is taking me longer to read than it took the author to write."
    "感覺我讀這本書的速度還沒有作者寫書的速度快。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1482
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_a1425505:

    # "I try to put it down for a while, then read some again, start all over from the beginning, read each page twice."
    "我試圖把書放下一段時間，然後再接著讀，從第一頁開始，每一頁都讀兩遍。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1484
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_779fba11:

    # "Nothing works, I have zero concentration."
    "不過沒什麼用，我一點注意力都集中不起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1486
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_3ab31011:

    # "Taking it with me just in case, I head out to get some fresh air and inspiration as to what to do."
    "以防萬一，我出去呼吸新鮮空氣時帶上了它，想找點事做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1491
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_f77d067f:

    # "I make my way to the quad, passing by students heading for the gates."
    "我經過一羣向大門湧去的學生，擠到了操場裡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1493
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_1e743d52:

    # "The hastiest ones are leaving for their homes already, judging from the luggage some are dragging with them."
    "從一些人拖著的行李看來，最著急的那一批已經開始回家了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1495
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_feb6c205:

    # "I guess that no matter how hospitable Yamaku is, home is still home. Still, I heard some people will be staying here over the vacation."
    "我猜不管山久高校有多親切，家也還是不可替代的。不過，我還是聽說有些人會留在這裡過暑假。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1497
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b8936b45:

    # "The quad is big enough for its center to be shadowless no matter how high or low the sun is."
    "操場足夠大，所以無論太陽有多高，它的中央都不會有陰影。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1499
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_61cf9b68:

    # "I stop in the middle and bask in the warmth."
    "我停在了中央，沐浴在暖意裡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1501
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_62b8076d:

    # "The brightness makes me squint my eyes when I look towards the main building."
    "當我看向主樓時，強光逼得我眯起了眼睛。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1503
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_56243082:

    # "It looks all but abandoned already."
    "它看起來像是已經被遺棄了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1505
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_ebb9ceb1:

    # "Yuuko wasn't at work today, so the next time I can get books from the school library is after vacation."
    "優子今天沒有上班，所以我只有在暑假後才能從學校圖書館借書了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1507
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_62d933f8:

    # "There is a public library somewhere, I'm sure, but I'm feeling too lethargic to find out where it is."
    "附近有所公共圖書館，我很確信，不過我覺得睡意太濃了，不想去找它在哪兒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1512
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b0a8f307:

    # "The hall is equally dead so I have to content myself with returning to the dorms, ending my leisurely walk sooner than I expected."
    "大廳也是同樣的一片死寂，所以我只得回宿舍，比預期更早地結束了散步。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1514
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_6b043fbf:

    # "Then again, I wasn't quite sure what I was expecting in the first place."
    "不過話說回來，我也不知道自己到底想要什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1519
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_460dd3b4:

    # "On a moment's impulse I enter the girls' dorm to see if Rin or Emi are there."
    "我一時心血來潮，走進了女生宿舍，想看看琳或笑美在不在。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1521
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_d9d89bdb:

    # "Neither is, so I go back to my own room to dwell on my lethargy."
    "但兩人都不在，於是我回到了房間裡，想借著昏沉的狀態想想東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1528
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_8:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1531
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_e38a9633:

    # n "{vspace=60}I should talk things through with Rin."
    n "{vspace=60}我真該和琳好好談談的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1533
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_4a5e72e3:

    # n "She really bothers me."
    n "她真的讓我很煩躁。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1535
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_809c916d:

    # n "{vspace=60}Defying the conceptual equivalent of gravity, she balances on the thin line zigzagging between insanity, incomprehensibility and instability."
    n "{vspace=60}她似乎在蔑視應該保持重心平衡的常識，東倒西歪地走在瘋狂、無法理喻和不穩定間的鋼絲上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1537
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_5aad4976:

    # n "Rin affects me too. She challenges me in ways that I didn't know… or more accurately, didn't hope existed."
    n "我也被琳影響了。她用我無法理解的方式去挑戰我……或者準確地說，是用那些我根本不知道存在的方式。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1539
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_5efc5572:

    # n "{vspace=60}I've started to wonder whether these feelings are really love, or I was just fooling myself."
    n "{vspace=60}我開始質疑那些感情是否真是愛了，或許我只是在自我欺騙。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1541
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_175d0cbc:

    # n "Surely, it would be insanity to consider that?"
    n "不過，那麼想肯定是瘋了吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1543
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_d46739d0:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}For the rest of the day, Rin, the hospital, Yamaku and vacation swirl through my head."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=60}這天剩下的時間裡，琳、醫院、山久高校，以及假期都輪流在我的頭腦裡旋轉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1547
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_f0f8a830:

    # n "{vspace=30}I can't concentrate even on concentrating."
    n "{vspace=30}我甚至沒法集中注意力，把注意力給集中起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1549
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_71457912:

    # n "{vspace=30}Thoughts seem to come and go haphazardly, fragmented into too-small pieces of cognition."
    n "{vspace=30}思緒總是在不經意間出現，又消失，碎成一小塊一小塊的認知碎片。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1551
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_58a290e8:

    # n "{vspace=30}I pick up the book and manage to read a hundred pages, but I'm sure by tomorrow I'll have no recollection of what happened in the story."
    n "{vspace=30}我拿起了書，讀了一百頁，不過我肯定到了明天，我對那故事就什麼也不記得了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1553
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_3a7fa6e0:

    # n "{vspace=30}I try to clean up my room, but even that proves to be too bothersome, too time-consuming and requiring too much attention to detail."
    n "{vspace=30}我試圖打掃房間，不過連這也開始讓我心煩，太耗費時間了，而且需要太多細節上的注意力。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1555
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_554e90c4:

    # n "It's usually like this. When you have 'nothing to do,' you do nothing even if you could."
    n "總是如此。當你“沒什麼要做”時，你就什麼也做不了了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1560
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_9:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1566
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_61247b6a:

    # "As expected, mom calls me and I end up promising to see if I can get a train ticket for tomorrow, or failing that, the day after."
    "如我所料，媽媽給我打了電話，讓我保證明天去看看能不能買張火車票，如果不行，後天再試一次。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1569
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_10:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1586
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_89cff40f:

    # n "{vspace=60}Maybe I'll go downtown tomorrow anyway. I could do some shopping or something."
    n "{vspace=60}或許明天我反正都要進城的。我可以買點東西，找點事做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1588
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b24c0736:

    # n "It's not that I need anything, but maybe there are summer sales, and I could pick up… something."
    n "我倒不需要什麼東西，不過有夏季的折扣，所以我可以買一些……東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1592
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_5e03b606:

    # n "{vspace=60}…Why am I trying to force myself?"
    n "{vspace=60}……我為什麼要逼自己？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1594
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_ae2b6e01:

    # n "Before, I was content with having nothing to do, save for kicking the ball every now and then at the field."
    n "先前，我還希望能無所事事，除了偶爾在球場上踢踢球外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1596
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b4d7f7eb:

    # n "Now it seems that I can't settle down at all."
    n "而如今，我像是根本沒法安穩下來一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1598
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_dce4c6f8:

    # n "{vspace=30}Is it because I have changed, or because my world has changed?"
    n "{vspace=30}是因為我變了，還是我的世界變了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1601
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_11:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1607
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_2d1d7ef9:

    # "By eleven, the darkness bids me to sleep."
    "十一點時，黑暗讓我不得不睡覺。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1625
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_d76e4f6d:

    # "The medication bottles are innocuously arranged on my night table, not at all beckoning, rather pointedly reminding me of the reality instead."
    "藥品無辜地擺放在我的床頭櫃上，看上去一點也不誘人，更像是在尖銳地提醒我現實是什麼樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1627
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_b9c7e988:

    # "It's evening so I have to open three bottles, extract one large oval-shaped one, two small round ones and one large flat that has to be cut into half, close the bottles and chug down the medications with a chaser of fresh tap water."
    "已經是晚上了，所以我打開了三個藥品，拿出了一顆橢圓形的大藥丸，兩顆小小的圓藥丸，還有一片扁扁的大藥片、必須要切成兩半。然後關上了藥瓶，藉著一杯新接的自來水把它們嚥了下去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1641
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_adcc9949:

    # "The water tastes metallic on my tongue."
    "水在我的舌頭上嚐起來像金屬。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1643
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_675cc894:

    # "I swallow it along with the pills anyway and head to the bathroom."
    "我把它連著藥片一起吞了進去，走進廁所。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1648
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_3e442dfc:

    # "The mindless job of brushing my teeth is fit for trying to sort my thoughts."
    "我心不在焉地刷著牙，正好能想想事情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1650
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_98aa888b:

    # "One emerges from the mass, clearly rising above the others."
    "在眾多思緒中，一個想法清晰地浮了出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1652
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_12:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1655
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_fe43f2c2:

    # n "{vspace=270}I want to see Rin."
    n "{vspace=270}我想要見琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1657
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_950439c0:

    # n "I can't let my outburst of anger be the last thing between us before the vacation."
    n "我不能讓自己發火時說的話變成假期前隔在我們間的最後一件事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1660
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_13:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1667
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_4215315d:

    # n "{vspace=240}I have to see her, tomorrow."
    n "{vspace=240}我明天必須去見她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1669
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_9f609591:

    # n "Sleep overcomes my confused mind with more ease than it should."
    n "睡意輕而易舉地淹沒了我迷茫的想法。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1672
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_14:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1692
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_8d8a2921:

    # "Rain is falling on my summer vacation like an uncountable number of small bad omens."
    "雨落在我的暑假裡，像是一個個數不勝數的噩兆。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1694
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d0255cc1:

    # "Luckily I'm not superstitious, but the bad weather makes me downcast too."
    "好在我並不迷信，不過這天氣也讓我有些消沉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1696
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_198a7d03:

    # "It's been like this since morning and there is no end in sight."
    "從早上開始，天氣就是這樣，似乎永遠都不會停。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1698
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_86398206:

    # "An impenetrable gray mass of clouds shadows the sky as much as it shadows my mood."
    "一團無法穿透的厚雲遮蔽的天空，同時也遮蔽了我的心情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1700
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_28e7b6ce:

    # "In a bout of defiance, I finished cleaning up this morning, but after that was done I ended up staring out of the window in hope of the weather clearing."
    "今天早上，在一陣蔑視般的衝動下，我打掃了房間，可那之後，我就開始盯著窗外，希望天能晴起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1702
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_39a3b2a9:

    # "The incessant drumming of rainfall against the roof and the pavement is mesmerizing, a droning background noise to lose your mind into."
    "雨滴接連不斷的墜落聲打在屋頂和人行道上，讓人像是被催眠了，讓神智迷失在那片單調的背景聲中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1704
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1706
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_604cb789:

    # "… …"
    "…… ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1713
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_96f490b9:

    # "This won't do, I have to get a move on."
    "這樣下去不行，我必須找點事做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1715
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_efd0c57f:

    # "Should I pack now, or later?"
    "我應該現在開始收東西嗎，還是過一會兒？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1722
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_0707f71c:

    # "I decide on the latter and make my way outside, pausing briefly at Kenji's door to listen to the odd clunking sounds from the other side."
    "我決定過會兒再收，然後出了門，在健二的門前短暫地停了一下，聽著另一邊傳來的古怪敲打聲。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1726
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_74a05ef3:

    # "I don't dare to knock, out of the fear of finding out what he is doing."
    "我不敢敲門，生怕看見他正在做的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1734
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_154c5f79:

    # "Braving the rain from under my trusty umbrella, I cross the space to the girls' dorm."
    "我迎著雨點打起了自己值得信賴的傘，穿過空地到了女生宿舍裡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1743
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_c939dd20:

    # "Knocking on Rin's door yields no answer, but the door behind me opens instead."
    "我敲了敲琳的門，毫無反應，倒是我背後的門開了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1758
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_69ba2711:

    # emi "Hisao? Hi!"
    emi "久夫？嗨！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1763
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_8fe0d634:

    # emi "Terrible weather. I even missed my morning jog."
    emi "天氣真糟。我都開始懷念我的晨跑了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1765
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_bec77409:

    # "She frowns, but I would be glad if I was her. Emi's morning jogs are anything but leisurely."
    "她皺著眉頭，不過如果我是她的話，會慶幸的。笑美的晨跑可一點也不輕鬆。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1767
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_46e17644:

    # hi "Oh, hi, I was—"
    hi "噢，嗨，我只是——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1772
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6c727612:

    # emi "If you're looking for Rin, I don't think she is there."
    emi "如果你是在找琳，我覺得她不在這兒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1774
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6c0eb2c4:

    # hi "Have you seen her recently?"
    hi "你最近看到她了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1779
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_7028b2c1:

    # emi "Yeah, just this morning when I woke her up."
    emi "看到了，今天早上我還叫她起床的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1781
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_db78729a:

    # "The mention of waking up makes Emi yawn like a cat, and makes me feel silly."
    "提到起床，笑美像只貓一樣打了個哈欠，讓我感覺自己有些蠢。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1783
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_45509f61:

    # "Of course she has seen Rin. Emi wakes her up and helps her get dressed on most mornings, even makes her lunch boxes every now and then."
    "她當然看見琳了。大多數早晨笑美都要幫她起床穿衣服，甚至時不時幫她帶午餐。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1785
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_cb6e2bc7:

    # "They are like sisters, even though they seem to have nothing in common."
    "她們就像是一對姐妹，雖然表面上沒有什麼共同點。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1788
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_78b4f0b5:

    # "I wonder which one is the elder sister? Probably Emi, against all odds."
    "不知道哪一個是姐姐？估計是笑美吧，雖然不太可能。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1790
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_7da774f5:

    # "She is really diligent, even though she gives the feeling of someone who would be a total airhead."
    "她真的很勤勉，雖然有時給人感覺像個沒腦子的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1792
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_2f5a5bea:

    # "Why does it feel odd that she is so dutiful under that cheery grin of hers?"
    "她總是那麼盡職，帶著愉快的笑容，可為什麼我感覺這麼古怪呢？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1797
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d064ef9b:

    # emi "She left for the gallery a few hours ago… hey, are you listening?"
    emi "她幾小時前去畫廊了……喂，你在聽沒？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1799
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_64dbce1d:

    # "Maybe I'm making a funny face or something, since Emi tilts her face quizzically, looking at me with her eyes round and inquisitive."
    "可能我的表情有些可笑，因為笑美疑惑地側起了頭，睜著圓圓的眼睛好奇地望著我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1804
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_19972527:

    # emi "Hmm?"
    emi "嗯？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1806
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_e13a2526:

    # "Her innocent face seems to request my attention."
    "她無辜的臉似乎是在要求我集中注意。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1808
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_58c0300f:

    # hi "Yeah, I'm listening…"
    hi "當然，我在聽……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1813
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_4f68b1dd:

    # emi "Can I ask you a question?"
    emi "我能問個問題嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1815
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_2541be0f:

    # hi "Yeah, of course."
    hi "行，當然可以。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1820
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_0ce6898f:

    # "She furrows her brow, licking her lips as if to prepare for something."
    "她皺起了眉頭，舔舔嘴脣，像是在為什麼做準備一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1825
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_9474eb39:

    # emi "Why do you care so much about Rin?"
    emi "你為什麼這麼關心琳？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1830
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_c748bc35:

    # emi "I mean, you probably hang around her more than I do, and we even slept in the same bed sometimes until, er, lately."
    emi "我是說，你和她在一起的時間可能比我還多，我們有時還會睡在一張床上呢，直到，呃，最近。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1832
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_1d3b01d3:

    # hi "After she banned you because you ravaged her hair?"
    hi "直到你蹂躪她的頭髮，讓她把你踢出去以後？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1837
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_3cea227a:

    # "A shock of horror widens Emi's eyes at least twofold, making them seem even more saucer-like than usual, while a healthy blush rises on her cheeks and ears."
    "一陣驚恐把笑美的眼睛至少擴大了兩倍，讓它們看起來比平常更像是盤子了，同時一抹健康的紅色染上了她的臉頰和耳朵。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1842
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_4814b0e8:

    # emi "She told?! Ohhh… I'm going to strangle that Rin or something other horrible…"
    emi "她說啦？！哦噢嚄……我要把那琳給掐死，得好好教訓……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1844
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_c0bbe1c9:

    # "I hold back my laughter, lest she direct her disdain at me."
    "我忍住了笑，害怕她把怒火發泄到我身上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1849
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_2f42f19e:

    # "Emi recuperates quickly from the embarrassment and seems to forgive Rin in the same instant, getting her focus back on me."
    "笑美很快就從尷尬中恢復了，似乎在同一瞬間就原諒了琳，把注意力重新轉回了我身上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1854
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_2d8d6cf8:

    # emi "Anyway, are you in love with her or something?"
    emi "總之，你是愛上她了還是怎麼回事？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1856
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d887d4a8:

    # "Uh oh. This really feels like an elder sister questioning a suitor. Emi is kinda nosy, and not in a good happy way, if there even is one to begin with."
    "糟了。現在感覺真的像是一個姐姐在質問求愛的人。笑美有點多管閒事的，而且不是那種好的多管閒事，假如真有好的多管閒事的話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1858
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_cc0d7719:

    # "She'd make a good partner for Misha, to be honest. The horror."
    "說實話，她可以做米莎的完美搭檔。想想都可怕。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1860
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6ce201a3:

    # hi "That's already your second question, so I don't think I have to answer."
    hi "已經是你的第二個問題了，所以我覺得我沒必要回答。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1862
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_1e558655:

    # "I try to conjure up a front made of pure, crystallized cool and uninvolvement."
    "我試圖戴上一個水晶般純潔冷靜、完全不為所動的面具。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1864
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_16e3c11f:

    # "I wonder whether I manage to fool even myself."
    "我懷疑我連自己都騙不過。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1869
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f8ba3511:

    # "At least Emi is waggling her eyebrows dangerously, with a nasty smirk on her lips."
    "至少笑美在危險地扭動她的眉毛，嘴角勾出一道險惡的傻笑。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1871
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5e48eea3:

    # emi "Is that a yes?"
    emi "這是肯定了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1873
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d5dfe2a6:

    # hi "No, it's not a yes."
    hi "沒，這不是肯定。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1878
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_9a9d7040:

    # "Obviously unsatisfied at my refusal to answer her way-too-intimate question, she has enough sense to back off."
    "她顯然對我拒絕回答這非常個人化的問題很不滿，不過還好她明白不該再問下去了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1883
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_37c97d73:

    # "Doesn't stop her from sticking out her tongue at me like a kid, and giggling again."
    "但她還是像小孩一樣對我伸出了舌頭，又開始咯咯笑起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1888
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_1c1021da:

    # emi "If that's your answer, I don't think I have to talk with you any more."
    emi "如果你要那麼回答，我覺得就沒必要和你再說下去了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1890
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_c3144138:

    # "It's easy to see that she's not really angry."
    "很明顯她沒有真生氣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1895
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a32de8d5:

    # emi "Besides, I have to go pack now. Mom will be worried if I miss my bus."
    emi "再說，我必須收東西了。如果我錯過公車，媽要罵我的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1897
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_23b8a84f:

    # emi "Seeya!"
    emi "再見啦！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1899
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_4f28c382:

    # hi "Yeah, bye."
    hi "嗯，再見。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1908
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_3fe99f78:

    # "She retreats back into her room, leaving me alone in the hallway."
    "她回到了自己的房間裡，留我一個人站在走廊上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1910
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_044d7110:

    # "What's between me and Rin is not her business, right?"
    "我和琳之間的事和她無關，對吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1912
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_7d0711e0:

    # "That's why I ended up not saying anything about our fight to Emi. Rin must have not said anything either."
    "所以我沒對笑美提起我們間的爭吵。琳一定也沒說。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1914
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_23e440a1:

    # "I guess… even though they are friends, there are things they don't talk about."
    "我猜……就算她們是朋友，有些話也是不會說的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1916
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1918
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5f51b53c:

    # "So, if Rin is at the gallery, I'd have to go all the way there."
    "那麼，既然琳正在畫廊，我就得去那兒了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1920
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5796dd87:

    # "Now that I managed to get out of my room, I suppose it's not that much of a bother to go downtown."
    "既然現在我已經出了房間，那再進趟城估計也沒什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1922
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_35d8f7e3:

    # "I could go get a ticket, but the train back home will have to wait, at least until tomorrow."
    "我可以去買張票，不過回家的火車必須等一等了，至少等到明天再說。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1924
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d5cfa695:

    # "No way I'm going to carry baggage to the train station in this rain, even if there's not that much of it."
    "我可不會在這種雨裡面拖著行李去車站，雖然雨其實不算太大。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1932
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6e23fb6d:

    # "Rain makes all outlines seem very unstable, as if they were fading away."
    "雨讓每一件東西的輪廓都變得朦朧，像是行將消逝一般。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1934
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6d9c9471:

    # "The townscape turns into a shapeless collection of various fuzzy tones of gray, instead of distinct forms of buildings and cars."
    "城市變成一片沒有形狀的灰霧，模糊不清，樓房和車輛不再具有形體。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1936
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_4cdb6f6a:

    # "Those poor souls who are forced into the downpour try to make as much haste as they possibly can, pitying each other for their shared misery."
    "那些可憐的人被困在了暴雨中，儘可能急切地走著，因為大家共同承受的苦難而互相同情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1942
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5e73aadb:

    # "I turn the final corner, the twenty-second corner so to say, and immediately feel stupid for being amused by my own pun."
    "我轉過了最後一個街角，也就是第二十二號街角，然後立刻感覺自己太傻，居然會被這種雙關逗笑。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1944
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_1e586a06:

    # "The door beckons me with promises of warmth."
    "大門召喚著我，煥發著暖意。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1953
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b1ffb743:

    # "The rainwater dripping from my umbrella makes interesting, almost artistic patterns on the floor."
    "雨水從我的傘上滴落，在地上匯聚成了有趣的圖案，幾乎顯得像是藝術。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1955
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_1a859d51:

    # "I am not wet, apart from my shoes that leave small puddles in my wake, completing the rainwater-artwork."
    "除了鞋以外，我沒有被淋溼，鞋在身後留下了一些小水灘，完成了那副雨水的畫作。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1961
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_976fb099:

    # "Nomiya is here too, chatting with Sae at the back of the gallery. Rin's nowhere to be seen, though."
    "野宮也在那裡，正在畫廊後和紗枝聊天。不過我看不到琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1963
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_e769e9e0:

    # "Maybe she's upstairs."
    "可能她在樓上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1965
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_39a5be74:

    # "There are no customers though, which figures, considering the bucketloads of water dropping on the neck of anyone daring to brave the weather today."
    "不過裡面沒有顧客，可以理解，因為外面的瓢潑大雨正傾瀉在每個膽敢冒險出門的人頭上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1970
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_477455a9:

    # sa "Welcome."
    sa "歡迎。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1972
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_dbbe0fc0:

    # hi "Hello. Sorry to interrupt…"
    hi "你好。抱歉打擾了……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1977
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_c387670f:

    # no "Ah, good afternoon Nakai."
    no "啊，下午好，中井。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1982
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a80d47c7:

    # no "Came all the way here for a visit?"
    no "跑這麼遠來拜訪？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1984
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f5c395b7:

    # hi "Ah… no, I think it was just an impulse. I was around the neighborhood, shopping, and decided to stop by."
    hi "啊……沒，我覺得只是心血來潮。我恰好在附近，買東西，所以就決定順便來看看了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1986
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_df253efd:

    # "My reflexive reaction is a white lie, which surprises myself."
    "我本能地撒了個無關痛癢的謊，讓我自己都有些吃驚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1988
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_99490866:

    # "Maybe I just don't want to say that I came specifically to see Rin, even though that much must be obvious."
    "或許我只是不想承認自己是專程來看琳的，雖然這肯定很明顯。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1993
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_58fbae9f:

    # sa "My, you chose a bad day for shopping. Would you like some tea to warm you up?"
    sa "老天，你真是選了個糟糕的日子出來買東西。你想喝點茶暖和一下嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1995
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5aaebf04:

    # hi "Thank you but I'm fine, really."
    hi "謝了，我沒事，真的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1997
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_e62c76ae:

    # hi "The weather could be better though. Rain on the first day of vacations is a bit depressing."
    hi "不過天氣倒是可以再好一點。放假的第一天就下雨，真有點沮喪。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2003
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f366b0d0:

    # no "Hahaha! Well, I'm sure it'll get better."
    no "哈哈哈！啊，我確信天氣會變好的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2005
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f924db9d:

    # "Nomiya offers his hearty laughter, bordering on abrasive."
    "野宮貢獻出了他熱心的大笑，已經快要接近研磨人耳了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2007
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f53e863a:

    # hi "Rain doesn't get you down, teacher?"
    hi "雨沒影響到你的心情嗎，老師？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2012
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_78963b55:

    # no "Well, I do prefer clear weather as well. I was actually leaving just now to meet someone, and I'd prefer not getting my jacket soaked. It's very expensive."
    no "這個嘛，我確實也更喜歡晴天。其實，我剛才正準備出去見一個人，不過不想把夾克打溼了。這衣服很貴的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2017
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a20af79a:

    # no "But of course I'm in a good mood!"
    no "不過當然，我心情不錯！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2022
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_60db5139:

    # no "What did you think about the exhibition? It was wonderful, wasn't it?"
    no "你覺得畫展怎麼樣？挺棒的，對吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2024
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d62d902f:

    # hi "Yeah, it was very fancy."
    hi "對，是挺不錯的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2026
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b9fa781d:

    # "My unenthusiastic answer only spurs him to carry on, walking around the gallery while blabbering about the opening."
    "我的回答不冷不熱，可依然激勵他說了下去，喋喋不休地說著關於開幕式的事，在畫廊裡走來走去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2028
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_bc0f5784:

    # "He talks more and louder when he is moving. It's something I noticed at the club meetings too."
    "當他走動時，說話聲音更大了，說得也更多。我在社團活動時也注意到這點了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2033
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_9a424440:

    # no "We got to talk with many good people and make valuable contacts."
    no "我們需要和很多好人談談，拉攏關係。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2038
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_53acf0d3:

    # no "One of Tezuka's paintings even got sold, to a collector from Osaka."
    no "手塚的一幅畫甚至被賣掉了，賣給了一個大阪的收藏家。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2045
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_39df7101:

    # "I follow his eyes to an empty space in the wall. I can't even remember which painting was hanging on that spot."
    "我隨著他的目光看到了牆上的一片空白處。我都記不清曾經掛在那裡的是哪幅畫了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2047
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a3764746:

    # "Well, it's gone now."
    "不論如何，現在它已經不在了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2055
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_46494bcb:

    # no "It was lucky that she was all right despite that dizzy spell."
    no "幸虧除了那點小眩暈以外，她安然無恙。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2060
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a500c4ec:

    # no "She got a little quiet though, so I told her to rest well. Then again she's always been pretty shy."
    no "不過她有點太安靜了，所以我叫她好好休息。不過話說回來，她一直就挺害羞的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2062
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_356770ba:

    # "Shy? Whatever, I just nod along with the teacher."
    "害羞？隨便吧，我只是附和著老師點點頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2067
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_e5ef1dfc:

    # no "The reception was very positive in general. I might be able to get one of my friends to write a little article on a magazine to—"
    no "總的來說，反響很不錯。我可能還可以讓我的一個朋友在雜誌上寫篇小文章來——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2069
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_701959b0:

    # sa "Shinichi, your meeting. You're making Mr. Takahashi wait."
    sa "信一，你的會議。高橋先生正在等你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2074
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_0cbb9e1a:

    # "Sae's remark makes him stop in his tracks and check his watch."
    "紗枝的話讓他停下來看了看錶。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2076
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_71e02f13:

    # "Nomiya frowns in displeasure at the interruption to his tirade."
    "長篇演說被打斷了，野宮不快地皺起了眉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2081
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_3515c2d3:

    # no "Oh, right. Yes, well, I'll be off then. We'll meet in September, Nakai."
    no "噢，對。沒錯，好吧，那我走了。九月再見，中井。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2083
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_361fdc97:

    # hi "Bye."
    hi "再見。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2091
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_68b1a74e:

    # "Wow. Teacher really doesn't hold back when it comes to Rin's budding artist career."
    "哇。老師對琳剛起步的藝術生涯真是義無反顧的支持。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2093
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_7b2cdcc7:

    # "I guess it takes a lot to succeed, but I suppose his job would be easier if Rin was more cooperative."
    "我猜成功的代價很大，不過假如琳更合作一點，他的工作也會更容易一些。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2098
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2101
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b2628fcf:

    # n "{vspace=30}She's too indecisive even though she's doing just fine. Like that 'dizzy spell' from the night before."
    n "{vspace=30}她太優柔寡斷了，哪怕她其實做的很好。就像那天晚上的“一點眩暈”一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2103
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_9f131eba:

    # n "She just got freaked out or something, and I didn't do anything to help her."
    n "她只是被嚇壞了而已，可我沒做些什麼去幫她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2105
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_aaa316ef:

    # n "{vspace=30}I sigh."
    n "{vspace=30}我嘆了口氣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2107
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_cbf6d502:

    # n "It feels like the gap between me and Rin is only widening."
    n "感覺我和琳之間的那道溝壑正變得越來越寬。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2109
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_05ebc2df:

    # n "She's going to become something great while I'm still feeling like I'm bogged down, despite promising myself to try and make something of my life."
    n "她正變得越來越好，與此同時我卻依舊感覺自己在止步不前，雖然我向自己保證要努力有所成就。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2111
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_899baf52:

    # n "On top of that, we had that fight and the longer we keep not talking, the harder the wounds become to heal."
    n "另外，我們又吵了一架，之後我們不說話的時間越久，傷口就越難癒合。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2113
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_1c9d389d:

    # n "If that even is what we want. I never found out what Rin felt, and now I'm not sure what I feel myself."
    n "如果癒合真的是我們想要的東西的話。我從來就猜不透琳在想些什麼，現在我連自己的想法也猜不透了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2115
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_038d7c50:

    # n "I wish I could understand her. But Rin is not very open for interpretation."
    n "我真希望自己能理解她，可是琳不是太容易被人理解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2117
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_456caa70:

    # n "Not that she's hiding anything, she just seems to defy my attempts at making sense of what she is talking about on any given day."
    n "不是說她在藏些什麼，她只是總對我試圖解讀她內心的嘗試不屑一顧而已，每天都一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2123
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2128
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_ef9162e6:

    # sa "Something on your mind?"
    sa "你有心事？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2130
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_19a1ba7c:

    # "I realize I've been spacing out in the middle of the gallery for who knows how long."
    "我意識到自己已經不知在畫廊中央站著發呆多久了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2132
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_fe9dc336:

    # hi "Ahh… nothing special…"
    hi "啊……沒什麼特別的……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2134
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_4b81de86:

    # "I pretend to study the closest paintings to distract her."
    "我假裝在看最近的那副畫，以轉移她的注意力。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2144
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6bbf3831:

    # "I've seen it before."
    "我見過那幅畫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2146
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_659d36c8:

    # "The now all-too-familiar strokes of color, twisting and melting into each other seemingly randomly still manage to feel like there is something happening behind the scenes, so to speak."
    "那些筆觸下的色彩現在實在是太熟悉了，互相之間融合、纏繞在一起，似乎毫無規律可循，然而依舊能讓人感到那色彩背後有東西正在發生。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2148
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6dd8e5bc:

    # "Rin's style is so much like her. Abstract, incomprehensible, colorful."
    "琳的風格真像她。抽象、不可理解，五彩繽紛。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2150
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_82eaf5c1:

    # "Mysterious."
    "詭祕莫測。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2152
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5b5ddb02:

    # "I wonder if to understand an artist, one must understand art?"
    "我想知道如果要理解一個藝術家，是不是要先理解藝術？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2159
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_57d5369c:

    # hi "Umm… I may have a question."
    hi "呃……我可能有個問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2164
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_cacde930:

    # sa "Oh?"
    sa "哦？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2166
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6abbb1d0:

    # "She looks up from the magazine she was idly leafing through, seeming delighted at my display of unspecified interest."
    "她從那本隨意翻閱的雜誌上抬起了頭，我顯露出的模糊興趣似乎讓她比較開心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2168
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_16f66972:

    # hi "How do you interpret art?"
    hi "你怎麼解讀藝術？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2173
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_c5a8be80:

    # sa "What do you mean?"
    sa "什麼意思？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2175
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b0c698ee:

    # "Her eyebrows rise high into questioning arcs, as if the question was too complicated to even begin to answer without clarification."
    "她的眉毛高高揚起，像是這問題實在是太複雜了，不進一步說明的話，根本無法解答。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2177
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b4f07c87:

    # hi "Sorry if I'm asking something stupid."
    hi "抱歉，好像問得挺蠢。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2179
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6547df5c:

    # hi "I don't think I really understand art like the pros do."
    hi "我只是覺得自己不能和專家一樣理解藝術。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2184
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_e0ce30d7:

    # sa "Oh, there's no trick to it."
    sa "哦，沒什麼技巧的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2186
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_af1350ce:

    # "Sae waves my question away with a simple but efficient flick of her wrist."
    "紗枝簡單又幹練地揮了揮手，把我的問題掃到了一邊。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2191
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5ce0787f:

    # sa "Everyone interprets art as they will, and interpretation is as much in the eye of the beholder as in the intentions of the creator."
    sa "每個人都在用自己的方式解讀藝術，觀眾的解讀和藝術家的創造有很多共同的地方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2193
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5875ce85:

    # sa "'Pros' have their own way, because there is this thing called art theory."
    sa "“專家”有自己的方法，因為有個叫藝術理論的東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2195
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_453cf356:

    # sa "There are patterns in art, just like in everything, and we assume that it's possible to draw some conclusions from observing those patterns."
    sa "藝術裡有規律，什麼東西都一樣，所以我們認為有可能從那些規律中得出結論。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2197
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6d031a38:

    # "Her voice is like a teacher's, lecturing and adding emphasis on random words to keep the listeners on their toes."
    "她的聲音像個老師，在一些特定的詞彙上加以強調，讓聽的人不至於被弄暈。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2202
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a6c2cfdd:

    # sa "In the end, I suppose it's pretty meaningless."
    sa "說到底，我猜都沒什麼意義。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2204
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_acf4c476:

    # "She moves to musing seemingly to herself, muttering loud enough for me to clearly hear."
    "她似乎陷入了沉思，只是在把想法以足夠讓我聽見的聲音說出來而已。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2206
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_31fa8ff4:

    # sa "A good piece of art will make you feel something and that's all there is to it."
    sa "好的藝術會讓你感到某種東西，僅此而已了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2208
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_7d678c9f:

    # sa "Feelings change and they affect the art we create and the art we see."
    sa "但感受是會變的，而且它們會影響到我們創造和欣賞的藝術品。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2210
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b91d705c:

    # hi "But…"
    hi "但是……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2215
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_aff67f9e:

    # sa "I'll tell you a story."
    sa "給你說個故事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2217
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_36500938:

    # hi "Do you have to? The last one was depressing…"
    hi "非要說嗎？上個故事有些讓人消沉……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2219
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_2c333e8c:

    # sa "It's important. Listen…"
    sa "很重要。聽著……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2221
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_67359d64:

    # sa "About a hundred years ago a little known painter got news that his friend, a man called Casagemas, had committed suicide."
    sa "大約一百年前，一個沒什麼名氣的畫家聽說自己的一個朋友自殺了，那朋友名叫卡薩吉瑪斯。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2223
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5414ed21:

    # sa "This happened while he was away and hadn't seen his friend for a while."
    sa "那件事發生時，他正在遠方，而且已經很久沒見過他的朋友了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2225
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_770733bf:

    # sa "So obviously he must have felt even more conflicted than you normally would after hearing of such a thing."
    sa "所以很明顯，他聽到這消息後比常人聽到這種事時更糾結。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2227
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a15d1905:

    # sa "For four years after that, our main character did nothing but monochromatic paintings because he was so deeply affected by the news."
    sa "那之後的四年裡，畫家都只用單色繪畫，沒有例外，因為他受那件事的影響太深了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2229
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_ecef6122:

    # sa "Whatever he did, he always kept returning to that same color until it let him out of its grasp."
    sa "不論他做什麼，都總是回到同樣的顏色裡，直到它放過他為止。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2231
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a4a66667:

    # "She takes a little pause to check whether I'm still following."
    "她停頓了片刻，想要弄清我是不是還在聽。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2233
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_69bf7d08:

    # "I am, to an extent, so I give her the prompt that storytellers seem to live for."
    "在一定程度上，我確實在聽，於是我給了她一點說書人似乎拼命渴求的激勵。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2235
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_c85221a4:

    # hi "So…"
    hi "然後……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2237
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d0a57d48:

    # "It's hard to continue from that, as I can't seem to come up with the question she wants me to come up with."
    "然後就很難接下去了，因為我想不出她想讓我想出的問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2239
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a646deae:

    # "Like a half-baked Socrates, she thought she laid out all the tools for revelation in front of me."
    "像是那個總是隻說一半的蘇格拉底，她認為自己已經把所有用來解答的工具都擺在了我面前。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2244
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_3f4eff04:

    # sa "Don't you see the point yet?"
    sa "你還沒看到重點嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2246
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_7da429ed:

    # "Only, her student proved to be too dense to get it."
    "只可惜，她的學徒笨得沒法理解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2251
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_92ae8521:

    # "She looks discontent at my slowness."
    "她看上去對我的遲緩很不滿。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2253
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_db9e06d8:

    # sa "Picasso's Blue Period is one of the most lauded in the history of art, but who knows what he felt when he worked on those masterpieces?"
    sa "畢加索的藍色時期是藝術史上最負盛名的幾件事之一，不過誰知道當他在創造那些傑作時，心中在想些什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2255
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b3ef9f66:

    # sa "Sadness? Longing? Regret?"
    sa "悲傷？渴望？悔恨？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2257
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_51a79c7c:

    # sa "Nobody can tell."
    sa "沒人知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2259
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_74a940f2:

    # sa "If you now see one of his Blue Period paintings, you'd probably interpret it differently from before you knew about Picasso's friend Casagemas."
    sa "現在你知道了畢加索的朋友卡薩吉瑪斯，如果你再去看一幅他在藍色時期的作品，你可能會有完全不同的解讀。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2264
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_3dcfcfb4:

    # sa "Experiencing art is always personal, only interactive by chance or circumstances."
    sa "體會藝術永遠是件個人的事，僅僅被機會和環境影響。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2266
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f4cd323a:

    # sa "There are a million explanations for any given piece of art, but it might be that none of them are what the creator intended."
    sa "任何一件藝術品都會有百萬種解讀的方式，可能其中任何一種都不是藝術家的初衷。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2271
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_2921a328:

    # sa "No man is an island, you know?"
    sa "沒有任何人是座孤島，你明白嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2273
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_0eba98cb:

    # "I nod without understanding what that last remark meant."
    "我點了點頭，沒弄清最後一句話是什麼意思。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2275
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_3baa71c1:

    # "What she said made sense otherwise, except for one thing."
    "她說的其他話倒是挺對的，就是這最後一句。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2277
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_aaf874d1:

    # "If art is communication like Rin said, but everyone is talking their own secret language like Sae said, what can anyone ever hope to communicate?"
    "假如藝術真像琳所說的那樣是一種交流，但每個人都如紗枝所說的那般，說著自己獨享的祕密語言，那還有誰能指望去交流？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2279
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_319d0dbd:

    # "It seems so futile, and pointless."
    "感覺真是徒勞又無意義。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2281
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_950ebfcb:

    # "Art really is not a thing for me."
    "藝術真的不適合我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2288
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_71ac2452:

    # "Sae returns to her art magazine, and I make a round in the gallery, trying to see what Rin can see in her own paintings."
    "紗枝又開始看她的藝術雜誌，我在畫廊裡走了一圈，試圖看出琳在自己的畫裡看見了什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2290
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_62b50f3a:

    # "A soothing mood takes hold of the gallery surrounded by the rainstorm, the big windows making the transparent isolation feel more comfortable."
    "暴雨中央的畫廊有一種撫慰的感覺，碩大的窗戶營造出一種透明的隔絕感，讓人更舒服了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2295
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_1a3f4747:

    # "A tinkle of the bell disrupts the tranquil mood."
    "一聲鈴響打破了寂靜的氣氛。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2305
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_da04f110:

    # "Rin pushes the door open with her shoulder and steps in."
    "琳用肩膀推開了門，走了進來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2307
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_addf6b79:

    # "I had almost forgotten that she was the reason why I came to the gallery in the first place."
    "我幾乎都忘了自己最開始是為了見她，才來畫廊的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2312
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_56f08f96:

    # rin "I think I'm ready—{w=0.3}{nw}"
    rin "我覺得我準備好了——{w=0.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2317
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_476b888f:

    # "She pauses mid-sentence, noticing my presence."
    "她在半途停住了，注意到了我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2319
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a43a6b46:

    # "The needle-dropping silence lasts for exactly one and a half seconds, not enough for either me or Sae to open our mouths, but enough for Rin to react."
    "能聽見落針的寂靜正好持續了一秒半，還不夠我和紗枝開口，但已經夠讓琳做出反應了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2324
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f2fc5ea0:

    # rin "I'm going for a walk."
    rin "我要去走走。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2331
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_fbb3c86c:

    # "Heading back outside with a reckless pace uncharacteristic of herself, Rin seems to forget that it's still raining."
    "琳的步伐焦躁，一點也不像她，她衝回了門外，似乎忘了外面正在下雨。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2333
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_b53d4867:

    # "Without giving it any real thought, I grab my umbrella and hurry after her."
    "我沒考慮，也沒猶豫，抓起雨傘追了上去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2343
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_bfa7b72c:

    # "I catch Rin around the corner, open the umbrella and lift it above the two of us while still having to almost run to keep up with her."
    "我在街角處追上了琳，撐開了傘，舉在我們的頭頂，同時依舊需要跑著才能跟上她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2345
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_0ea51acf:

    # "She doesn't protest me running after her nor me giving her shelter against the rain, eventually slowing her pace down so I can match it without an immediate danger of overexerting myself."
    "她沒有抗議我追上來，也沒反對我為她遮雨，終於，她放慢了腳步，讓我能不冒著過度操勞的險趕上她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2347
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_27ae3507:

    # "I relax from the rush, assessing the situation."
    "我休息了一下，掂量著現在的情況。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2349
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_bfa998d9:

    # "The last time I held my umbrella to guard both of us against the rain, I didn't think too much about it."
    "上一次我為我們兩人撐傘遮雨時，還沒怎麼去深想。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2351
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_d01cb9bb:

    # "But now, all the things that happened since then are gathering into a freezing cold ball around my stomach."
    "可現在，自那以後發生的一切都聚集在了我的胃裡，變成一個冰冷的大球。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2353
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_6a4cad7e:

    # "Being close to her makes me uncomfortable, and I feel myself flustering slightly."
    "離她這麼近，讓我很不舒服，而且我感覺自己有些臉紅。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2355
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_0252e53d:

    # "It's hard to get words out of my mouth, as it feels suddenly very, very dry."
    "我的嘴突然間說不出話了，感覺它非常，非常的乾燥。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2357
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_66523d72:

    # "Still, it's not like I can back off."
    "不過，我也無路可退。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2359
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_bf29b048:

    # hi "Why do you keep running away?"
    hi "為什麼你總是要跑開？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2364
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_27f8c077:

    # rin "I don't want to talk to you."
    rin "我不想和你說話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2366
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_3456971d:

    # hi "I want to talk to you."
    hi "我想和你說。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2371
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_4210074f:

    # rin "It hurts every time I do."
    rin "每次和你說話都好疼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2373
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_bc37a1a0:

    # hi "Sometimes it can't be helped."
    hi "有時這是沒法避免的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2378
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a992f22b:

    # rin "I don't want to hurt."
    rin "我不想疼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2380
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_434553cb:

    # hi "Fine. We don't have to talk."
    hi "好吧。我們不用說話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2385
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f9ed2b9a:

    # rin "What should we do?"
    rin "那我們該做什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2387
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_f01e297a:

    # hi "Let's just keep walking."
    hi "就繼續走吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2392
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_5f7e9809:

    # rin "Just walking?"
    rin "只是走？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2394
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_beb587ba:

    # hi "Just walking."
    hi "只是走。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2399
translate zh_hant a4_rin_blue_period_a61bcc4a:

    # rin "Okay."
    rin "好吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2420
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_332df450:

    # "Our footsteps go 'splish splash' in the shallow puddles forming on the streets as we walk through the rainfall."
    "我們走過雨幕，腳步在街上匯聚而成的淺水窪中發出“啪嗒，啪嗒”的聲音。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2422
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5e37c119:

    # "Rin, now walking beside me in her unhurried and relaxed manner, doesn't seem to be even a bit bothered by the fact that she is getting wet even though she needn't to."
    "琳在我身邊用她從容放鬆的方式走著，似乎一點也不在意自己被淋溼了，雖然她可以避開雨的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2424
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_55c8f7c2:

    # "She is partially out of the protective shelter of my umbrella, despite it being more than big enough for the two of us."
    "她有一半都在我雨傘的庇護之外，雖然那傘大得足夠為我們兩人遮雨。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2426
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4d73d9e1:

    # "It's as if she doesn't even notice the rain drenching her shirt."
    "像是她根本沒注意到雨水將襯衫浸溼了一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2428
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2430
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_292de573:

    # "Rin's demeanor always evokes mental images of meditative calm, even when she might be in inner turmoil."
    "琳的舉止總是讓人想起一種冥想般的平靜，哪怕她的內心可能波濤洶湧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2432
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_96895670:

    # "But I don't think that is meditation. That is just getting soaked in rain."
    "不過我可不認為那是冥想，只是在雨中浸溼罷了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2434
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fdb5b079:

    # "I wish I could be more calm too."
    "我希望自己也能更平靜一些。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2436
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b646bc5e:

    # "I've become too involved with Rin to retain my usual aloofness."
    "我已經太在乎琳了，沒法保持自己通常的冷漠。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2438
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_67633efc:

    # "It feels like I have become one of those people who fool themselves into thinking they are objective, only to find out they are the worst kind of liars."
    "感覺像是我成了那種一直欺騙自己、認定自己很客觀的人，結果卻只發現他們自己是最糟的騙子。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2440
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ae981667:

    # "Illusions to fool ourselves, what better way to make one feel like a good person?"
    "用幻象來欺騙我們自己，還有什麼讓我們感覺自己是好人的更好方法嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2442
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_62fa6d03:

    # "It might be better to lose that illusion."
    "可能最好還是拋下那幻象。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2449
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_81068593:

    # hi "I'll be going back home for some time so I thought I'd come to see you before that."
    hi "我要回家一段時間，所以我想，應該在那之前來看看你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2451
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5567e945:

    # "I could have thought of a better conversation opener, but Rin actively refusing to talk makes it hard."
    "我本來可以想到一個更好的開場白的，不過琳那麼固執地拒絕談話，讓它變得很難。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2453
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2a52ae42:

    # rin "That's good. I might have thought that you'd have been kidnapped otherwise."
    rin "真好。否則我還會以為你被綁架了的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2455
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_af1b1a87:

    # hi "You can't keep running away from everything. Not even from me trying to talk seriously."
    hi "你不能總是逃避一切，總是跑開。不能總是在我嚴肅說話的時候迴避我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2457
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_033e6652:

    # rin "I'm always serious. Also I seem to be running very slowly right now."
    rin "我一直都是嚴肅的。而且，我現在跑步也很慢了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2459
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_87c81773:

    # rin "Maybe I should take lessons from Emi."
    rin "可能我該讓笑美教教我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2461
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b88e0e80:

    # "It's futile. Like talking to a brick wall that randomly spouts sarcastic nonsense back at you."
    "根本沒用，像是在和一堵隨機吐出無意義嘲諷的牆談話一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2463
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6b4862b4:

    # hi "Think of your exhibition opening. What if you had run away?"
    hi "想想你的畫展開幕式吧，如果你逃跑的話，會怎麼樣？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2465
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_75f5f242:

    # "Rin doesn't answer to that, she just keeps walking. Or running slowly, escaping from me into her silence."
    "琳沒有回答，她只是繼續向前走著。或是在緩慢地跑，躲開我，藏進自己的沉默中去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2467
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_635773a9:

    # "She has a knack for being alone in company, I've noticed."
    "她很擅長在有人作伴時獨身一人的，我已經注意到了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2473
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_26f42f60:

    # "We head down the street, then turn left, then three times right, then left again."
    "我們沿著街走，然後左轉，右轉三次，接著再左轉一次。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2475
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_84bcf04d:

    # "It's like that night from some time ago, we keep choosing directions randomly because it doesn't matter where we are going."
    "像是先前的那個晚上一樣，我們不斷地隨機挑選方向，因為不論哪個方向都沒有意義。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2477
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f8daf5f7:

    # "All that matters is walking and the sound of raindrops drumming against the umbrella."
    "重要的是向前走，以及那些敲打在傘面上的雨點聲。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2479
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1cc7befa:

    # "Water flows down from the roofs of the buildings and into the storm drains in wide rivers."
    "雨水從樓房的屋檐邊流下，與瓢潑大雨匯在一起，流進了寬敞的水流中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2481
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_edfcc32c:

    # "Even though I try to step over them, my feet are getting wet through my shoes."
    "就算我試圖越過它們，我的鞋也溼透了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2483
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_076f37f9:

    # "We keep walking in silence that just begs to be broken again. I'm sure I am the only one feeling like this, though."
    "我們繼續無言地走著，寂靜乞求著能被再次打破。不過，我相信自己是唯一一個有這種感覺的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2490
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e76b0f07:

    # hi "Why did you have the exhibition?"
    hi "為什麼你要辦畫展？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2492
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_172269a2:

    # "Rin just shrugs sullenly and looks in the other direction. I give up at this point."
    "琳只是陰鬱地聳聳肩，看向了另一個方向。於是我放棄了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2500
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2503
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0dae1505:

    # n "{vspace=90}It's pointless."
    n "{vspace=90}真是徒勞。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2505
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5d37bd05:

    # n "{vspace=30}What did she want to accomplish? What she said at the night of the opening made me feel that there was something… something special she wanted."
    n "{vspace=30}她到底想要達成什麼？開幕的那天晚上，她說的話讓我感覺她想要某種東西……某種特別的東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2507
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9ffa0137:

    # n "It felt to me that Rin hoped for something unattainable."
    n "讓我感覺琳是在渴望某種無法取得的事物。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2509
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c78dd15e:

    # n "She set the bar high and inside her own head she failed, no matter how much people liked her works."
    n "她在腦海中把目標定得太高，然後失敗了，不論有多少人喜歡她的作品。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2511
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_60a233ec:

    # n "It's understandable to lack realism; most people do, even if not quite on the extreme level Rin takes it to."
    n "無法理解現實是可以理解的；大多數人都是如此，哪怕不像是琳那麼極端。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2513
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3b02dc03:

    # n "{vspace=30}But it's not a reason to live in your private world that accepts no visitors."
    n "{vspace=30}但這不是活在自己的世界中、不接受外界拜訪的理由。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2515
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_63cf5ae3:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=90}You can't bend the world to fit your twisted, megalomaniac cosmology where everything works just like you want."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=90}你不能把世界隨意塑造成自己希望的樣子，去符合你那扭曲、狂妄自大的世界觀。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2519
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_bdadc52d:

    # n "{vspace=30}That's what frustrates me the most in Rin."
    n "{vspace=30}這是琳身上最讓我感到挫敗的一點。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2521
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fe231760:

    # n "{vspace=30}She wants the world to live by her rules, disregarding everything that conflicts with those as irrelevant or unnecessary."
    n "{vspace=30}她想要整個世界都按照自己的規律去存在，忽視一切矛盾，認為那些是無關緊要，或是沒有必要的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2523
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ff42a06b:

    # n "I can't believe how anyone in Yamaku could not have the bare minimum perception to understand that the world can sometimes be very unfair."
    n "我無法理解，一個山久高校的學生怎麼會不理解這世界的不公。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2525
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1581ca86:

    # n "I'm sure she's not the only one who wishes some things were different, but we can at least grasp the facts as they are."
    n "我確信她不是唯一那個希望事情能不一樣的人，不過至少，我們應該接受現實。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2531
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2538
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_63d1a98c:

    # "I take a sideways glance at Rin, who is looking up at our dome-shaped cover. It is a poor replacement for a real sky in its monochrome bleakness."
    "我向旁邊瞟了琳一眼，她正抬頭看著我們穹頂式的傘。對於天空獨有的那種單色調的蕭瑟陰鬱來說，這傘是個糟糕的替代品。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2540
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_971cdcdf:

    # "The rain just keeps falling."
    "雨繼續向下落著。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2542
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_10b54f63:

    # "Just like the clouds today, Rin doesn't really give the feeling of wanting to be watched."
    "就像是今天的雲一樣，琳也讓人感覺不想被注視。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2544
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8f57b2d9:

    # "She sulks, in unison with the sky that she loves so."
    "她在生悶氣，就像她深愛的天空一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2546
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_548676a9:

    # "I shouldn't have come. Her presence only reminds me of how angry I got because of these exact same reasons, and how those reasons probably can't ever change."
    "我不該來的。她只讓我想起了自己先前是如何因為同樣的原因發怒的，而那些原因恐怕是永遠都無法改變了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2548
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4a4dd5a6:

    # "Even though I want to say I'm sorry, even though I don't want us to break apart, I can't bring myself to say either of these things."
    "就算我想要道歉，就算我不希望我們分別，也沒法把它們說出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2554
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f49fa71d:

    # "We keep measuring the rain-drenched streets one step at a time."
    "我們繼續用自己的腳步去丈量被雨水浸溼的街道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2556
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3a3b6a41:

    # "Often, when you walk with someone else, your steps become synchronized as if through some weird subconscious pact."
    "通常，當你和別人一起走時，你們的腳步會漸漸變得同步，就像是潛意識中有某種古怪的協定一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2558
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6f47e9df:

    # "I noticed that ours never do."
    "我注意到我們從不會那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2567
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b5c742e3:

    # "Time passes, and the strikes against the drumskin of my umbrella fade as the clouds above slowly disperse to reveal a cerulean blue."
    "時間流逝，我雨傘表面的擊打聲緩緩消褪，烏雲漸漸散去，露出了一抹蔚藍的天。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2575
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_aa6eb418:

    # "Eventually the rain yields enough for me to close the umbrella, shaking the excess water off before I do."
    "終於，雨小到了讓我把傘收起的地步，我抖掉了傘上多餘的雨水。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2577
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c18ccb2a:

    # "While I wrestle with the mechanism, Rin stops so abruptly that I take five steps before realizing that she's not with me any more."
    "當我和那個機械裝置搏鬥時，琳猛地停住了，那麼突然，以至於我向前走了五步，才意識到她已經不在我身邊了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2579
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_caaac72a:

    # "Stupid umbrella seems to be jammed."
    "那蠢傘好像被卡住了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2589
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e1cde282:

    # "When I turn around, I find her staring at me with an impassive face."
    "當我轉身時，發現她那張漠無表情的臉正瞪著我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2591
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1450add9:

    # rin "I wanted someone to say 'I understand how you feel.'"
    rin "我想要一個說“我明白你的感受”的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2593
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cbf075eb:

    # rin "Wouldn't that be great?"
    rin "那不是很好嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2595
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_59e0e773:

    # "Is that an answer to the question from before? I'm not sure."
    "這是在回答我先前的問題嗎？我不知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2597
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_23d487a5:

    # hi "Yeah… but why is it so important?"
    hi "是啊……但是，這有那麼重要嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2602
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0217691a:

    # rin "Because otherwise… I don't know if I can bear this."
    rin "因為否則……我就不知道自己能不能忍受下去了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2604
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ed14fd34:

    # "I was still in the middle of folding my umbrella so I just answered something to get the conversation going, but what she says now freezes my blood."
    "我依然在試圖把傘收起來，所以只是回答了一句讓談話繼續下去的話，不過她的回應讓我的血都冷了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2609
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6f762f3c:

    # rin "If someone says a joke and laughs, you laugh with them, right? Because a joy doubled is a joy tripled, right?"
    rin "如果有人說了個笑話，然後笑起來，你就要和他們一起笑，對吧？因為翻倍的快樂就有三倍多了，對吧？（“分享的快樂有兩倍多”的錯用）"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2614
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_909981a6:

    # rin "If someone is hurt and sad, you comfort and hug them, right? Because that way—"
    rin "如果有人受傷了，而且很悲傷，你就應該抱他們，對吧？因為那樣的話——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2616
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_879b98dc:

    # rin "…"
    rin "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2618
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_83b047f4:

    # "She pauses, her mouth still halfway open, then remembers to close it."
    "她打住了，嘴依然半張著，然後想起來應該把它閉上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2623
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ca93fe8c:

    # "A gloom sets on her face and simultaneously on my heart."
    "一道陰影落在她的臉上，同時沉進我心中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2625
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7b710278:

    # rin "I don't know why the right words never come out."
    rin "我不知道為什麼正確的詞從來就出不來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2627
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_581f7d8b:

    # rin "I don't know why I can laugh only when I make myself."
    rin "我不知道為什麼我只有在逼自己的時候才能笑出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2629
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_95a2d745:

    # rin "I don't know why everything stays only inside me, even when it feels like I'm going to burst."
    rin "我不知道為什麼所有的東西都只留在我裡面，有的時候我感覺自己都要爆了，可還是一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2631
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_66bf3f0f:

    # "Her flat, expressionless face does not waver even when she says that."
    "就算當她這麼說時，她平淡的臉依舊面無表情，沒一點動靜。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2633
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_18875c04:

    # "Her usual steady voice becomes only slightly quieter than normal."
    "她通常平穩的聲音只是比平常稍微小聲了一點而已。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2635
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_09d03f68:

    # rin "But who… who would ever want to feel like that?"
    rin "誰……誰有可能想要有那種感覺？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2637
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cec8cfbb:

    # "Rin looks at me and I imagine the sadness reflecting from her eyes, whether it really is there or not."
    "琳望著我，我幻想著她眼中折射出的悲傷，不論那到底是不是真的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2639
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ae6f824c:

    # rin "I don't."
    rin "我不想。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2641
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4998265c:

    # rin "I don't want to feel like that."
    rin "我不想有那種感覺。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2643
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_56438df9:

    # "We stay silent for a little while after that."
    "那之後，我們又沉默了一會兒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2645
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c2d35d33:

    # "Rin because she said all she has to say at once, I because I have no clue how to process what she just said."
    "琳是因為她已經把要說的都說完了，我則是因為不知該怎麼處理她剛才說的話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2647
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a87c8b78:

    # "I don't understand what Rin is saying. Or I do, but I don't want to."
    "我不理解琳在說什麼。或許我理解，只是不願去承認。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2649
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_464ca93e:

    # "For the first time both of these things happen, and it has to be simultaneously."
    "這是我第一次產生這兩種感覺，它們卻偏偏要同時發生。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2651
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4027b135:

    # "The irony is not lost on me."
    "真是諷刺。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2653
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_05baf856:

    # hi "I… think everyone wants to be understood. That's universal."
    hi "我……覺得每個人都希望被理解的。這很正常。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2655
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_10eb878c:

    # hi "But… that is impossible. Not only for me, but for anyone."
    hi "但是……那是不可能的。不止是對我，每個人都一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2657
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c85f7b29:

    # hi "Sae said so too."
    hi "紗枝也這麼說了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2659
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_43f6713f:

    # hi "You affect other people and are affected by them, but in the end, you see everything the way only you do."
    hi "你影響其他人，也被他們影響，但到了最後，你都只會用自己的眼光去看世事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2661
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7a83d220:

    # hi "All people… are alone. We just use each other to alleviate that loneliness."
    hi "所有的人……都是孤獨的。我們只是在利用對方罷了，去緩解孤獨。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2663
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7bfeda32:

    # "I wonder why I put it like that. It just felt that what Sae told me rang true, as if I had always thought like that without knowing it."
    "我不知道自己為什麼要這麼說。只是感覺紗枝告訴我的話變得越來越真，像是我一直就是這麼認為一樣，只是不知道而已。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2665
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e08edf7e:

    # "It feels like she articulated my thoughts in clear, simple words and that stupid story about Picasso."
    "就像她用簡單的話和關於畢加索的蠢故事把我的思想勾勒出來了，。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2670
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_32776b4f:

    # "Rin droops her head like a withering flower, letting her bangs fall in front of her eyes so that I can't see them."
    "琳低下了頭，像是凋謝的花，她讓劉海垂下，我看不見她被蓋住的雙眼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2672
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8462cffb:

    # rin "Why do you say that when you made me feel otherwise?"
    rin "為什麼你要那麼說？如果你讓我感覺到的是完全相反的……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2674
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cb976a1a:

    # rin "It's unfair."
    rin "這不公平。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2676
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5fdefa48:

    # "The shaky voice that says those words does not belong to Rin."
    "說出這話的顫抖聲音似乎不屬於琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2681
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5f2f6129:

    # rin "I really thought you could be different. That I wouldn't have to be alone."
    rin "我真的以為你會不一樣。我以為我不會是一個人了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2683
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1da80edf:

    # "It's a bitter voice of disappointment, spoken through clenched teeth and a quivering chest."
    "那是種失望的苦澀聲音，從顫抖的胸膛裡傳出，擠過咬著的牙。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2685
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6000cd34:

    # hi "I'm sorry…"
    hi "對不起……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2687
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_48be6363:

    # rin "If you are, why do you say something unfair like that?"
    rin "如果你真對不起，為什麼還要說那種不公平的話？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2689
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_40e2a175:

    # "Her demanding tone invokes no particular feeling in me, apart from sadness that has been there since yesterday evening."
    "她質問的語氣沒讓我產生任何感覺，除了那種昨晚開始就一直纏著我的悲傷以外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2691
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8cfc03b3:

    # "She doesn't intimidate me at all. Not any more."
    "她一點也不能脅迫我了。再也不可能。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2693
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_69772e59:

    # "Rin is not a prodigal art genius, nor an unpredictable idiot savant who could tear the logic lobe of my brain into shreds whenever she opened her mouth."
    "琳既不是一個藝術天才，也不是一個無法預料的殘智奇才，只要一開口，就把我腦葉裡的邏輯撕成碎片。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2695
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_80eff952:

    # "She is just a girl that I thought I loved, a loved one who wanted to be my friend, a friend whom I let down."
    "她只是一個我以為自己愛過的女孩而已，一個被愛的人，想要做我的朋友，卻因為我而失望了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2697
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_dc671011:

    # hi "I say that, because saying otherwise would feel like lying."
    hi "我那麼說，是因為其他的話都像是在說謊。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2702
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d66e33b2:

    # rin "Why?"
    rin "為什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2704
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7b9192bc:

    # "Simple questions are the hardest ones. I have to close my eyes so I can focus my thoughts enough to answer her."
    "最簡單的問題是最難的。我不得不閉上眼睛，強迫自己思考該怎麼回答。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2706
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_30c0befa:

    # hi "I'm no artist. I can never be on the same level with you."
    hi "我不是藝術家。我永遠都不可能和你站在同樣的高度的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2708
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0030f0a3:

    # hi "There is a world only you can see, and to be part of it I would have to become you."
    hi "你有一個只有自己能看見的世界，如果要變成它的一部分，我就必須先變成你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2710
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_bdb58370:

    # hi "That's something I can't do, no matter how much you wish me to."
    hi "但我做不到，不論你多想讓我做到。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2712
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_32e19661:

    # "Rin takes in my explanation without batting an eyelash."
    "琳聽見了我的解釋，連眼都沒眨。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2714
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_70c4d36e:

    # rin "I'm not a real artist either."
    rin "我也不是真的藝術家。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2716
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_29cb1b16:

    # rin "I just paint because it makes me feel like I can really feel something."
    rin "我畫畫只是因為那樣能讓我真正的感到一些東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2721
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a2ea179c:

    # "She holds her breath for a while before releasing it in a long, sigh-like flow."
    "她屏住呼吸，然後將它長長地一口氣呼出。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2726
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a06d90bb:

    # rin "That's why I'll do it."
    rin "所以我答應了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2728
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9f0de06c:

    # rin "I have decided. I'll do it. If even Hisao says that, then that's what I will do."
    rin "我已經決定了。我要答應。如果就連久夫都那麼說了，那我就要那麼做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2730
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f0418c62:

    # hi "Do what?"
    hi "答應什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2732
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce5fbd43:

    # "Rin starting a little shows that she had regressed into talking to herself again, but I'm glad I can snap her back even now."
    "琳稍稍驚了一跳，看來她剛才又陷入與自己的對話中了，不過我很慶幸自己能在這時把她扇醒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2737
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cdb6b300:

    # rin "Teacher and Sae have talked with someone who is a very important person. I got a scholarship for a big art school in Tokyo."
    rin "老師和紗枝和一個非常重要的人談過話了。我得到了東京一所大藝術學校的獎學金。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2739
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3af27008:

    # rin "He said I could transfer there and start after the summer is over, if I wanted to."
    rin "他說只要我願意，就能轉學到那兒，在夏天結束後開始上課。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2741
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_222b7f04:

    # rin "I don't really get why—"
    rin "我不知道為什麼——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2745
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5ccc20ae:

    # hi "Hold on, what? Why didn't you tell?"
    hi "慢著，啥？為什麼你不說？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2750
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_89ac8615:

    # rin "I just did. You are the first one I told because I decided it just now."
    rin "但我已經說了。你是我告訴的第一個人，因為我剛才才作出決定。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2752
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d43185c5:

    # "She keeps her cool, looking only mildly surprised at my shocked interjection."
    "她保持著那冷靜的表情，我的震驚只讓她稍稍有些意外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2754
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b75b8aa9:

    # "It's ridiculous how easily she can say something so life-changing."
    "真是荒唐，她竟然可以把如此重大的決策這麼輕易地說出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2756
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1353e44e:

    # "I can't believe it. After what happened in February, I have had enough change for this year."
    "我無法相信。自從二月以來，我今年已經受夠劇變了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2758
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_bf32c6bd:

    # "Even if things are going badly right now, I don't want everything to change."
    "就算事情現在開始惡化，我也不想再有任何改變。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2760
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_63297b3a:

    # hi "But what about Yamaku? Don't you want to graduate with everyone?"
    hi "但是山久高校怎麼辦？你不想和大家一起畢業嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2762
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_dd3fd004:

    # "My plea evokes no emotion."
    "我的懇求沒激起一絲感情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2764
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6339218e:

    # rin "Everyone who?"
    rin "誰是大家？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2766
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5b83c79a:

    # hi "Emi, me, everyone!"
    hi "笑美，我，大家！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2768
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fc9d34f8:

    # "I feel my pulse rising unnervingly, and my breathing becomes fast and shallow."
    "我感覺自己的脈搏開始危險地加速，同時呼吸變得又快又淺。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2770
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6d5053e2:

    # "I don't want this to happen."
    "我不想讓這事發生。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2772
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9475602e:

    # rin "Their life is not mine."
    rin "他們的生活不是我的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2774
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8fd58498:

    # rin "You just said that everyone is alone."
    rin "你剛才才說過，每個人都是孤獨的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2776
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6111e161:

    # hi "I didn't mean it like that—"
    hi "我不是那個意思——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2778
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_72a13a46:

    # rin "You always said that you'd have to seize the day and start living your life."
    rin "你總是說應該抓緊時間，體會生活。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2780
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5dcb8c2f:

    # rin "I have to live my life too."
    rin "我也必須體會自己的生活。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2782
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_960ce380:

    # "Rin is twisting my words to justify running away again. It makes me angry."
    "琳又開始扭曲我的話，用來為自己開脫，然後溜走了。真讓我惱怒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2784
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_443f95fc:

    # "Her ease, finality and seriousness in announcing this is unacceptable."
    "她顯出的平靜，嚴肅和不可動搖都像在宣告這是不可接受的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2786
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c7f719b2:

    # "As if changing your life is something you can do on a moment's whim! No!"
    "像是你可以一時心血來潮就改變自己的生命一樣！不可能！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2788
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_47f0411b:

    # hi "How can you say that? Why don't you even try to belong?"
    hi "你怎麼能這麼說？為什麼你連找個歸宿都從不試一下？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2790
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_db625628:

    # "The desperate accusation has no effect. It feels like I am once again out of weapons, that I can't reach through to her no matter what I try."
    "這道絕望的指責一點用也沒有。我感覺猶如再一次彈盡糧絕，不論我怎麼嘗試，都沒法觸到她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2792
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a0eaae9b:

    # "Rin is so frustratingly absolute in her own judgment that it might make me hate her if I didn't love her, even though I don't know which way I am feeling any more."
    "琳對自己的決定的堅持是那麼讓人挫敗，如果我不愛她的話，一定會恨她的，雖然我已經沒法分清自己的感受到底是什麼了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2797
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d5e62c37:

    # rin "Maybe I am that kind of a person. The kind that belongs only to herself."
    rin "或許我就是那樣的人。那種只屬於自己的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2799
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_53beb146:

    # hi "I won't accept that."
    hi "我沒法接受這個。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2801
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8a5624cd:

    # "Her nonchalant eyes do not seem to care whether I accept her decision or not."
    "她的眼睛漠不關心，似乎不在乎我接不接受她的決定。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2803
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2805
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_40b7767e:

    # "The pause lets me cool down, to find my sensibilities."
    "這道停頓讓我冷靜下來了，找回了自己的認知能力。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2807
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9a6da514:

    # "While I do, the parting rainclouds reveal a setting sun that still has time to shine its last few warming rays before calling it a day."
    "與此同時，消散中的雨雲顯露出了一輪垂陽，尚且留有一些時間，還足夠讓它將自己最後的暖光照過大地，將一天的帷幕拉下。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2809
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_eb76af50:

    # "A mosaic of light and shadow spreads on the walls of the buildings, on the street and the fence circling a park on the other side of the street."
    "一片光和影的馬賽克鑲嵌畫在樓房的牆面上鋪散開來，蔓延過街道和街對面環繞公園的柵欄。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2811
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_57201433:

    # "Rin's shadow is long enough to reach my feet."
    "琳的影子長得足夠能觸到我的腳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2813
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_254a5629:

    # "It's like one of those western movies, with two cowboys staring each other down, ready to sling their guns at each other."
    "像是那些西部電影，兩個牛仔互相對峙，隨時準備朝對方拔槍射擊。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2815
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_75bc3df4:

    # "The one who loses his nerve will eat lead."
    "失去勇氣的一方就會挨槍子。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2817
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7e45710c:

    # "I realize I would have the disadvantage because the sun is behind Rin, stinging my eyes."
    "我意識到自己是處於劣勢的，因為夕陽正在琳的身後下垂，刺疼了我的眼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2822
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_956ad423:

    # rin "Do you hate me?"
    rin "你恨我嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2824
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_11bdbe9f:

    # "She draws first and I have no counter."
    "她先拔槍了，而我無法回擊。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2826
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3b1d8348:

    # hi "I don't know."
    hi "我不知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2828
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ad8b8b19:

    # "Did I lose?"
    "我輸了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2830
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5a5c0a67:

    # hi "Even if I did, what would it matter?"
    hi "就算我恨，又有什麼意義？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2832
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4f4e1a70:

    # "I scramble for words, words that could salvage this. I find none."
    "我狼狽地找著回答的話，那些能挽救這一切的詞。但我什麼也找不到。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2834
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fb7e1ba6:

    # hi "You are my friend, I promised you that. I am not the kind of guy who forgets about promises."
    hi "你是我的朋友，我向你保證過。我不是那種違反諾言的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2836
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_707e1298:

    # hi "I think that is the most important thing. We could try to—"
    hi "我覺得那才是最重要的事。我們可以試著——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2841
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2edda4e4:

    # rin "Don't say it."
    rin "別說了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2848
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3623627b:

    # "Predicting what I was going to say, Rin throws herself into my arms, pressing her body against mine."
    "琳料到了我要說什麼，撲進了我的懷抱裡，把她的身體緊緊地貼向我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2850
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2736a4f0:

    # "I feel her rising to her tiptoes to match my height and snuggle closer."
    "我感覺她踮起了腳尖，縮短我們間的高度差，然後依偎著，靠向更近。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2852
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a4f3b77f:

    # "The scent of her hair is that of rain and paint thinner. Her body feels as cold as always. Her breathing against my neck is as hot as always."
    "她髮間的清香像是稀薄的雨和顏料。她的身體一如既往的冰冷。拂過我脖頸邊的呼吸則一如既往的火熱。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2854
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a0af7b9d:

    # "It's funny how all of those feel so familiar even though Rin, as a whole, does not."
    "真是可笑，所有的這些都感覺如此熟悉，可以琳作為一個整體卻是那麼陌生。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2859
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a334318d:

    # rin "Are you sure you can't hate me?"
    rin "你確定你不會恨我嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2861
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e54d1688:

    # "Rin whispers into my ear so close I can feel the movements of her lips against my earlobe."
    "琳對我耳語道，她捱得是那麼近，以至於我都可以感到觸在我耳垂上的脣，挪動著。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2863
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d1a66320:

    # "It's teasing, taunting. If this was some other kind of situation I'm sure it would tickle tantalizingly and I would giggle even though I'm a guy."
    "這感覺撩人又嘲諷。如果這是在別的情況下，我相信自己會被撓癢的，忍不住咯咯笑出來，哪怕我是個男人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2865
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7a4aa9a5:

    # rin "It would be easier if you did."
    rin "如果你恨的話，會容易得多。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2867
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fbe64de4:

    # hi "Dunno. It's pretty hard when you are hugging me like that."
    hi "不知道。你這麼抱著我的時候恨起來很難。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2872
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b9eaea40:

    # "I wonder if it's because of my sullen voice, but she takes a step back, looking wistfully at her short arms."
    "我不知道是不是因為自己慍怒的語氣，不過她向後退了一步，憂愁地看著自己短短的手臂。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2874
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4b12741f:

    # "I wish she hadn't done that."
    "我真希望她沒這麼做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2876
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_658b4d83:

    # rin "I can't hug anyone, Hisao."
    rin "我沒法抱任何人，久夫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2878
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7d52b351:

    # rin "I'm a bad person like that."
    rin "我就是個那樣的糟糕人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2883
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_29e24d1e:

    # rin "That's why I have to go."
    rin "所以我才必須走。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2885
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f2da7cf9:

    # "She disarms me completely with three simple sentences, rendering me unable to argue any more."
    "她用三句話就讓我徹底繳械了，讓我無法再爭執下去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2887
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d92b597d:

    # "And since I can't, Rin is free to continue as she wills, shifting her weight from one foot to the other before she does."
    "既然我沒法回覆，琳便繼續說了下去，把重心從一隻腳挪到另一隻。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2892
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c14dd8d3:

    # rin "I will learn to hug people in my own way."
    rin "我要學著用自己的方式去抱別人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2894
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5a5e600a:

    # rin "I'm sure I can become a real artist."
    rin "我相信自己能變成真的藝術家的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2896
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f734e332:

    # rin "But if I do… I might not be able to be me any more."
    rin "但如果我成功了……我可能就再也不能做自己了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2898
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_56bd51cc:

    # "The hint of a smile on her lips is a betrayal, a false sign of self-confidence in a future that even Rin can't foresee."
    "她脣間隱現的微笑背叛了她，那是一種虛假的自信，存在於一個就連琳也無法預料的未來中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2900
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0aa77a3c:

    # "I'd want to interpret it as a sign of hope, but I know better."
    "我想把它解讀成一個希望的跡象，但我清楚事實是什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2902
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_984cd297:

    # "Rin just keeps smiling that awkward, forced smile of hers."
    "琳只是繼續掛著那個尷尬，強迫的微笑。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2904
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_35c122ed:

    # rin "That's why… please forget about me, and I will forget about you too."
    rin "這就是為什麼……忘了我吧，我也會忘了你的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2906
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c893b703:

    # rin "I'm sure that—{w=0.5}{nw}"
    rin "我肯定——{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2911
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_766706de:

    # "She chokes in the middle of saying something I would never come to hear."
    "她說到一半時噎住了，我再也不可能知道她要說什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2913
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c663fefa:

    # "I don't think I'd wanted to hear it anyway."
    "但我也不覺得自己想要知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2915
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_268c61ba:

    # "This is not fair."
    "這不公平。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2917
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1054418b:

    # "Rin is not joking. Rin is always serious. But I can't accept it, I can't."
    "琳沒在開玩笑。琳從來都是嚴肅的。但我無法接受，我不能接受。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2919
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b1787844:

    # "Forget about you? How could I ever…?"
    "忘了你？我怎麼可能……？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2921
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_af6e097f:

    # "That's what I'd like to say. But I don't know how I would continue. I can't come up with anything good to say, so I have to challenge her."
    "這就是我想說的話。但是我不知該如何繼續下去。我不知道該說什麼才好，所以我只有挑戰她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2923
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8ec01e7b:

    # hi "How can you say such a thing?"
    hi "你怎麼能這麼說？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2928
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e068ae10:

    # "Rin raises her eyes to meet mine, they are serious and deep, a perfect image of the uncharted territory I always thought they were."
    "琳抬起了眼，對上了我的目光，它們嚴肅又深不可測，完美地驗證了我之前的想法，那是一片從未被涉足的水域。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2930
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8dd10a61:

    # "Even now, I can't read her emotions from those unblinking, jade irises that never could reflect what they saw."
    "就算此刻，我也沒法從那雙從不眨動的眼中讀出任何情感，那兩道翡翠色的虹膜從不會反射出它們看到的事物。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2932
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0f93dbe1:

    # rin "It's easy. After all, I am good at forgetting things."
    rin "很容易的。畢竟，我很擅長忘掉東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2934
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2936
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fc924da8:

    # "Her unfairness is choking my throat, but I manage to utter the question burning my mind."
    "她不公的話語在扼住我的喉嚨，不過我還是問出了那個一直在炙烤著我的問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2938
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_edab4dd5:

    # hi "So, is this it? Is this goodbye?"
    hi "那就是這樣？這就是再見了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2940
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2942
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_445a5121:

    # "Rin kept looking at me gently, without answering my question."
    "琳繼續溫柔地看著我，沒有回答。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2944
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d9c22d49:

    # "From her eyes I could see that she didn't even need to say anything."
    "從她的目光看來，我明白她已經不用說任何話了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2946
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c9799485:

    # "There were no more words for us."
    "我們之間已經無話可說。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2953
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9324cd77:

    # "She turned around and walked off without looking back."
    "她轉身走了，沒再回頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2955
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_91ab4a5f:

    # "All around me, the world kept changing, little by little, but I was left standing there."
    "在我周身，世界不停變幻，一點一點地改變，但我卻依舊站在這裡，被留下。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2960
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6c80a6b7:

    # "The sun dropped below the horizon, casting long and thin shadows across the street."
    "夕陽陷入了地平線下，把又長又瘦的陰影伸過街頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2962
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_55bcdcc7:

    # "In the waning light, Rin's distancing back seemed to be like from a faraway dream."
    "在那消逝中的光中，琳越來越遠的背影像是來自一個遙遠的夢境。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2964
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_09b6a8a5:

    # "The gap between us grew slowly."
    "慢慢的，那道溝壑在我們之間蔓延。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2966
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2b6ec8f5:

    # "The ripples on the puddles she stepped on expanded until they met the limits of their tiny existence and disappeared without a trace."
    "她踩過的水灘裡動起了漣漪，一層層向外盪漾，直到觸及它們渺小存在的邊緣，然後消失，不留一絲痕跡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2968
translate zh_hant a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f4d5e348:

    # "Her words stayed frozen deep inside my heart."
    "她的話語留在了我的心裡，被深深地凍結成了冰。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2980
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2983
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_e96c8674:

    # n "{vspace=30}Vacation, huh?"
    n "{vspace=30}假期，對吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2985
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_329304f8:

    # n "Some people will stay at the school even over the holidays, some will go back to their families."
    n "有的人在假期裡也會留在學校，有的會回家。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2987
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_77de5f7d:

    # n "I don't know what to do. I should go buy a train ticket for my trip back home, but I can't bring myself to do it."
    n "我不知道該做什麼。我應該買張回家的票的，可又下不了那麼做的決心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2989
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_64e8f2ca:

    # n "I bet I'm going to get a call from home again. Mom's going to pester me about when I'm coming back, and I'm not going to know what to answer."
    n "我打賭自己又要接到家裡打來的電話了。媽媽肯定又要糾纏，問我什麼時候回家，我不知道該怎麼回答。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2991
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_8e72648f:

    # n "{vspace=30}This is really lousy. In the current state of things with Rin, it feels like I can't just bail out of here and pretend we are through."
    n "{vspace=30}真的很煩人。尤其是現在和琳的情況變成這樣，感覺像我就是沒法逃離，假裝我們之間已經沒問題了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2993
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_cbef346b:

    # n "{vspace=30}And now, she has other problems of her own. I thought that the exhibition opening would give her a breather, but I was sorely mistaken."
    n "{vspace=30}如今，她也有了其它需要頭疼的事。我還以為畫展會讓她有時間喘喘氣，真是大錯特錯。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2995
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_a734eb67:

    # n "{vspace=60}The tangle just seems to thicken."
    n "{vspace=60}亂子似乎變得更糾結了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2999
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3004
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_bbc8465f:

    # "A sharp knock on the door interrupts the quiet but frantic mood of the last 15 minutes of the exam."
    "一陣銳利的敲門聲打破了安靜又狂亂的氣氛，考試只剩下最後十五分鐘了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3011
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_0de9b330:

    # mu "Come in."
    mu "進來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3024
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_0583d852:

    # "The opening door reveals the art teacher, who steps in with his jacket swirling around him as though in a gust of wind."
    "門開了，美術老師走了進來，他的夾克在他周圍扇動著，像是有風一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3026
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_1589bc1c:

    # "He glances at Mutou, who glances back at him."
    "他瞪著武藤，武藤也瞪著他。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3034
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_c1fcfe89:

    # "A frown spreads simultaneously on both of their faces as the men measure each other with their gazes."
    "兩者臉上同時都出現了皺起的眉頭，兩個男人用目光丈量著對方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3036
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_4f63ba5a:

    # no "Excuse me, could I borrow Mr. Nakai for a moment?"
    no "打擾了，我能不能和中井先生談下話？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3038
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_d060c84f:

    # mu "Excuse {b}me{/b}, Mr. Nomiya, but we are in the middle of an exam here."
    mu "真讓{b}我{/b}難辦，野宮先生，不過我們現在正在考試。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3040
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_b0ffeef2:

    # "A chilly atmosphere suddenly spreads in the middle of the summer afternoon as the two men try to stare each other down."
    "一陣冷冷的氣氛突然飄過夏季的午後，兩人都試圖把對方給瞪趴下。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3045
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_909b80ce:

    # no "This is urgent, and it seems that Nakai has already finished."
    no "事情緊急，而且看起來中井已經做完題了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3047
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_de5f031f:

    # "Both men turn to look at me, staring at me like a pair of basilisks trying to petrify a tasty snack."
    "兩個男人同時轉向我，像是兩個打算要把美味的獵物給石化的蛇怪一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3049
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_93f0744a:

    # "It's true that I've been idle for a good while now, so Nomiya is right, but…"
    "確實，我已經有一段時間沒事做了，所以野宮沒說錯，不過……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3054
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_2ce8ee7f:

    # mu "Nakai, would you like to check your answers one more time?"
    mu "中井，你想要再覈對一遍答案嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3056
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_df9ba85a:

    # "Mutou speaks with an odd intonation, weighting certain words as if trying to send a message."
    "武藤帶著一種奇怪的語調說，在某些詞上加了重音，像是在傳遞某種訊息。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3058
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_9f6ddf1d:

    # "The pressure from their stares makes me rapidly shake my head, which is apparently interpreted as an answer of some sort."
    "他們目光的壓力讓我迅速搖了搖頭，很顯然，這動作被解讀成了某種回答。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3065
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_7b8ebea7:

    # mu "Very well. Nakai, go with Mr. Nomiya, if you please."
    mu "好吧。中井，和野宮先生走吧，如果你不介意的話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3067
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_b7850a7f:

    # mu "Take your bag with you and bring your test paper to my desk."
    mu "帶上你的包，把試卷拿到我的桌上來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3072
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_2ea5b16f:

    # mu "You have a nice vacation."
    mu "假期愉快。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3074
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_3d7834a3:

    # hi "Umm. Er, you too, teacher."
    hi "嗯。呃，你也一樣，老師。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3076
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_a6dff9e2:

    # "The entire world… well, at least the classroom seems to hold its breath just for me, putting the exam on hold until I stand up, collect my stuff and walk to the door."
    "整個世界……啊，至少整個教室似乎都在因為我屏住呼吸，一直在暫停考試，直到我站起身，收起東西走到門口。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3078
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_35f58f7c:

    # "I can feel the stares in the back of my neck. My classmates probably think I'm in for some detention or something, on the last day of the school before summer vacation."
    "我能感到瞪在脖頸上的目光。我的同學可能還以為我要在暑假前的最後一天被拘留了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3080
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_e767c37c:

    # "I don't know what the teacher wants from me, but I can guess it probably is not detention and also that it probably has something to do with Rin again."
    "我不知道老師想要和我說什麼，不過我猜應該不是拘留，而且，應該又和琳有關。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3090
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_9f1852b3:

    # "Nomiya doesn't take me anywhere, contenting himself with the hallway as it's completely abandoned."
    "野宮沒帶我到別的地方去，對他而言，走廊就夠了，像是那裡已經被徹底遺棄一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3097
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_1e354d89:

    # no "Do you know where Tezuka is?"
    no "你知道手塚哪兒去了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3099
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_8c4ea6f8:

    # "So she is trying to avoid the teacher… par for the course, probably."
    "所以，她在試圖躲著老師……意料之中，可能吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3101
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_566d2aa5:

    # "I wonder if she realizes that she can't avoid dealing with this indefinitely."
    "我不知道她有沒有意識到自己不能無限期地把這事推遲下去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3103
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_2d914b5b:

    # hi "I have no idea."
    hi "不知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3105
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_f3678e70:

    # hi "You have probably asked in her homeroom next door."
    hi "你可能應該去隔壁她的班問的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3110
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_389fb581:

    # no "Of course I have! I have searched every nook and cranny of this blasted school and the girls' dorm."
    no "我當然問過了！我已經把這鬼學校和女生寢室翻了個遍。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3112
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_7f306d19:

    # no "You are the last one to see her since yesterday and you are her friend."
    no "你是昨天最後一個看到她的人，而且你是她朋友。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3117
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_82fbee90:

    # no "Work with me here. Aren't you worried?"
    no "配合一下我。難道你不擔心嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3119
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_cc663513:

    # "I am, but I don't know what I could do."
    "我確實擔心，但也不知道能做什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3121
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_502ebbdf:

    # "Rin did something incomprehensible yesterday, even for her."
    "琳昨天做了一些無法理解的事，哪怕對她來說也無法理解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3123
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_7a68094c:

    # "She seemed really confused."
    "她看上去真的非常困惑。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3125
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_15b583f7:

    # hi "Maybe she just wants some time to think then. I got the feeling that she had second thoughts about having that exhibition."
    hi "可能她只是想要些思考的時間。我覺得，她對那畫展改變看法了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3127
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_0a4398c3:

    # "Or something. She really didn't explain what was wrong."
    "或者是類似的情況。她真的沒解釋是什麼出了問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3132
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_a6fe6193:

    # no "What second thoughts?"
    no "改變什麼看法？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3134
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_6e9b4029:

    # hi "I dunno. Just got that feeling."
    hi "我不知道。只是有那種感覺而已。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3136
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_7956358e:

    # "I am being a little dishonest with the teacher, but this is not something I should be meddling with."
    "我沒完全對那老師說實話，不過這不是我能插手的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3138
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_e7e1c948:

    # "He came to me… yes, why? Maybe he thinks I'm some kind of confidant of Rin's, but I don't think I can help with this matter."
    "他來找我……沒錯，但為什麼？可能他認為我是琳的知己，不過我不覺得我能幫他。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3143
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_67914ac7:

    # "The teacher huffs and scratches his head in confusion."
    "老師惱怒地噴口氣，困擾地撓撓頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3145
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_bc4932fe:

    # no "What's up with that girl? This is so unlike her, she's always been so goal-driven."
    no "那姑娘是出了什麼問題？真是一點都不像她，她一直那麼胸懷大志。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3147
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_a698630c:

    # "'Goal-driven?' Those don't really strike me as words to describe Rin with."
    "”胸懷大志？“這詞聽起來一點也不像是用來形容琳的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3149
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_aae2da5f:

    # "To me, she always felt obsessive at best."
    "對我來說，她頂多是著魔了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3151
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_b7db4b12:

    # hi "Er, I don't mean to be rude, but wasn't it you who pushed Rin to that direction in the first place?"
    hi "呃，我不是要無禮，但最開始莫非不是你把琳向這個方向推的嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3156
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_5a0efb0a:

    # no "Her goal is my goal. That is a mentor's job."
    no "她的目標就是我的目標。這是導師的責任。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3158
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_c9e6b5c1:

    # hi "I guess so. I just don't know if painting can make her happy."
    hi "我猜是吧。我只是不覺得畫畫會讓她開心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3163
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_88a7d18b:

    # no "That's pretty preposterous of you to say, Nakai."
    no "你這話說得真可笑，中井。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3165
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_d223337e:

    # "He suddenly sounds pretty irate. Did I say something stupid?"
    "他突然間變得挺生氣。我說了什麼蠢話嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3170
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_c6fd24d7:

    # no "You don't understand, do you? It is not a question of happiness. For every gain there is a sacrifice to be made."
    no "你根本不懂，是吧？這和快樂無關。對每件事而言，都要代價要付。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3175
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_458c5978:

    # no "There is no free lunch, but could I… would I let that girl waste away her talent if she has a moment of doubt? Never!"
    no "天下沒有免費的午餐，但我怎麼能……我怎麼會讓那姑娘有片刻猶豫，揮霍自己的才華？不可能！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3177
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_cc053d13:

    # no "Painting is work just like any other. Tezuka might make it look like child's play to you, but she works hard every day to make her art."
    no "畫畫和別的工作一樣。可能手塚讓你覺得那是小孩子玩的東西，不過她每天都努力工作，才能畫出那些畫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3179
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_de48fc4a:

    # no "To become extraordinary, one has to make an extraordinary effort."
    no "想要變得非凡，一個人就必須做出非凡的努力。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3181
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_5600875c:

    # "The more the teacher talks, the more I feel that Rin doesn't think like that, even though I have no idea how she thinks."
    "老師說得越多，我越覺得琳不是那麼想的，雖然我也不知道她到底在想些什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3186
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_7a9b4bba:

    # no "I can very well understand why she would sacrifice her summer vacation and make up for the lost classes and exams to get a chance at showing her art."
    no "我非常能理解她為什麼要犧牲暑假，來補上錯過的課，就是為了一個展現自己畫作的機會。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3188
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_cbba8f9c:

    # no "This is the path she has taken, and to go all the way, that's not easy."
    no "這就是她選的路，要一路走下去，不容易。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3190
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_c59dea95:

    # no "I know she is young, and things are hard for her just like for all the kids here in this school, but that's no excuse."
    no "我知道她還年輕，和這所學校裡的其他孩子一樣，生活不容易，但這不是理由。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3192
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_80f7a08f:

    # "He is finished."
    "他說完了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3194
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_f2449dda:

    # hi "But—"
    hi "但——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3199
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_24d8a14e:

    # no "Do you have anything like what art is to Tezuka?"
    no "你和手塚一樣有藝術那麼重要的東西嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3201
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_0f269d05:

    # hi "No…"
    hi "沒有……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3203
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_0191c814:

    # "That's right. I have only vague ideas of my future, no goal to shoot for, no dream to blindly reach for."
    "確實。我對未來只有很模糊的想法，沒有奮鬥的目標，沒有盲目追尋的夢想。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3205
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_68bd3fa5:

    # "I joined the art club in search of something I could be interested in, to get inspired by."
    "我加入藝術社團是為了找出自己感興趣的事，找到靈感。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3207
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_c57ea0ce:

    # "Did I find something like that?"
    "我找到了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3209
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_c61de6a1:

    # "All I found in the end… was Rin."
    "到了最後，我唯一找到的……就是琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3211
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_4f4dbaab:

    # hi "No, I don't have a passion like that."
    hi "沒有，我沒有那種激情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3216
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_98ac8d70:

    # no "Then you can't understand."
    no "那你就不會明白。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3218
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_cd6fc25f:

    # "His flat statement allows no counterargument."
    "他平白的陳述讓我沒法反駁。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3220
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_01af5b29:

    # hi "But… she might not understand even herself."
    hi "不過……她可能自己都不明白。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3222
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_69301cc8:

    # "Still, I carry on arguing, out of spite if for nothing else."
    "可是依然，我卻繼續爭執著，可能只是為了刁難。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3227
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_3b9a8234:

    # no "How could she not? She's been at it so hard for the past few weeks that she put off even coming to school, not to say anything about attending class. Don't be ridiculous."
    no "她怎麼可能不明白？她之前的幾個星期裡那麼努力，甚至輟了學，更別提上課的事。別可笑了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3229
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_87e84184:

    # "I don't think I'm being ridiculous, but as I have no rebuttal, Nomiya seems to consider this one his win."
    "我不覺得自己有什麼可笑，不過既然我不知道該說什麼反駁，野宮就認為是自己贏得這場爭執了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3234
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_7901202f:

    # no "At any rate, the opening was quite successful despite Tezuka hardly showing up."
    no "總之，開幕式非常成功，雖然手塚幾乎沒露面。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3236
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_0c222304:

    # no "Many people were interested in her work and one piece was even sold for a reasonable price."
    no "很多人都對她的畫感興趣，一幅畫甚至賣了個不錯的價錢。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3238
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_cb9cf776:

    # hi "Well, that's nice isn't it?"
    hi "啊，真好，對吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3243
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_d9a29ef8:

    # no "Yes, it's fantastic news! I hoped that Tezuka would come to her senses when she heard about this, but…"
    no "當然，簡直美妙至極！我希望琳聽到這事後會找回點理智，不過……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3245
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_b33e402c:

    # "He sighs and takes off his glasses, cleaning them against his jacket before putting them on his nose again."
    "他嘆一口氣，脫下了眼鏡，用夾克擦了一下，然後重新戴回鼻子上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3250
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_0477d0e4:

    # no "At any rate, I should be going. There is this mess to be settled with Sae and everyone."
    no "總之，我要走了。紗枝和大家那裡還有亂子要收拾。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3252
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_439f3294:

    # no "If you see Tezuka, please ask her to come see me. Otherwise, have a nice vacation."
    no "如果你遇到手塚，麻煩讓她來見我。還有，假期愉快。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3254
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_e5c8fee6:

    # hi "Thanks…"
    hi "謝了……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3263
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_d10cffe6:

    # "After he has disappeared around the corner, I ponder where Rin could really be."
    "當他消失在廊角後，我思忖著琳可能去了哪兒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3265
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_a985ab63:

    # "It feels like she has not one, but at least half a dozen of these 'secret places.'"
    "感覺她好像不是有一個那種“祕密地點”，而是有至少一打。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3267
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_a915d233:

    # "I balance between the desire to solve this tangle and to drop it for good."
    "我權衡了一下是否該把這亂子給解開，然後徹底放下它。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3269
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_337552a9:

    # "The disused classroom is just a few feet away."
    "那間廢棄不用的教室就在幾尺之外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3271
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_da38e87f:

    # "What to do?"
    "該做什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3273
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3281
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_4a9e5232:

    # "As I push open the door, only the shadows greet me from the inside."
    "當我推開門後，迎面而來的只有室內的陰影。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3283
translate zh_hant a4_rin_desperate_glory_f957c2b7:

    # hi "Hey there."
    hi "嗨。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3296
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ee3f73f1:

    # "She's standing in the middle of the sunlit room, peering through the gaps of the curtains out into the yard."
    "她正站在沐浴陽光的房間中央，透過窗簾間的縫隙望向操場。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3298
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8c7aaa2e:

    # "Like so often before, she doesn't start or jump, just calmly waits for me to make the first move."
    "和從前一樣，她既沒被嚇著，也沒吃驚，只是平靜地等我邁出第一步。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3300
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_03a649fa:

    # "It's as if she is trying to become a permanent part of the furniture."
    "像是她正在試圖變成傢俱的一個固定部件。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3302
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d59819a9:

    # hi "The teacher is looking for you."
    hi "老師在找你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3304
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_96f6b750:

    # "A blank look over her shoulder is all I get, accompanied by a cryptic nonexpression on her face."
    "我得到的唯一回應是她越過肩膀的空洞目光，同時她的臉龐毫無表情，難以解讀。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3306
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_85c360b3:

    # rin "Are you looking for me too?"
    rin "你也在找我嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3308
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_3642d3bc:

    # hi "Nah, I already found you, didn't I?"
    hi "沒，我已經找到你了，不是嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3310
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6edd8a73:

    # rin "Did you?"
    rin "真的嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3315
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b7f14a11:

    # "She furrows her brow, looking so puzzled that it makes me wonder if the question was asked in all seriousness."
    "她皺起了眉頭，看起來異常困惑，我不禁好奇這是不是個嚴肅的問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3317
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_fcda1a5e:

    # "Maybe it was."
    "或許是的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3319
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c077d5b0:

    # hi "Are you talking metaphorically now?"
    hi "你在打比喻嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3324
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a3aa92a4:

    # rin "Do you mean like eels, caves and dark, stormy nights?"
    rin "你是說像是鰻魚、洞穴和漆黑的暴風雨夜那種？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3329
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8adb383e:

    # rin "I am bad at talking like that."
    rin "我很不擅長那麼說話的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3331
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3335
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0ec3e92f:

    # "The abruptly-ended greetings give me the chance to close the door behind me and sit down on a dust-covered desktop."
    "問候戛然而止，讓我有機會關上身後的門，坐到了一張鋪滿塵埃的桌上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3340
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e6a49020:

    # "Rin stays standing, but at least she turns around."
    "琳依舊站著，不過至少她轉身了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3342
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_046e264a:

    # "I soon wish she didn't though, so oppressive is her expectant stare."
    "我立刻希望她沒那麼做，那道期待中的目光實在是太咄咄逼人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3344
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_755ef64b:

    # "This is her place and I'm an intruder, although a tolerated one. Despite that, she still waits for me to say something."
    "這裡是她的地盤，我是個闖入者，雖然是個被接納的闖入者。除此以外，她依舊在等著我開口。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3346
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_3b3ea37a:

    # "If I only knew what."
    "要是我知道該說什麼就好了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3348
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3350
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_04a59135:

    # "The sunlit silence presses me towards decisions."
    "沉默被暖陽點亮，逼迫我做出決策。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3352
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_672af16b:

    # "I came here without really thinking what I would do, apart from delivering Nomiya's short message in case Rin was here."
    "我來這之前其實沒怎麼考慮自己該做什麼，除了如果琳在這兒的話，為野宮傳個口信外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3354
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4150f5aa:

    # "She was, and now I don't know what else I want to say… what else I should say?"
    "她確實在這兒，現在我不知道自己還想說什麼了……我還該說什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3356
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5d122f4b:

    # "I hover between my two options for a moment."
    "我琢磨了一下僅有的兩個選擇。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3358
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e9d74956:

    # "Rin being troubled troubles me too. It's a surprising revelation, almost as big as realizing that she really is troubled was."
    "琳在擔憂時，我也會擔憂。意識到這一點讓我感到意外，幾乎像是意識到她會擔憂時一樣意外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3360
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_9ef1978c:

    # "Nothing I can do would probably help, and I might be partially to blame too."
    "我做什麼可能都沒用，而且還有一部分錯在我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3362
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_33817fb1:

    # "Does it mean I should just wash my hands of her?"
    "也就是說，我應該就放手讓她走開？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3364
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_801d9523:

    # "Didn't think so."
    "我不覺得。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3366
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c7124952:

    # hi "So… what's wrong?"
    hi "那……出了什麼問題？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3368
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3373
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_be162ee9:

    # rin "Nothing."
    rin "沒什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3375
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_66076e58:

    # "She starts to turn away again, as if trying to physically exit a conversation she doesn't want to have."
    "她又轉身了，似乎是想要真的走出一場她不願繼續下去的談話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3377
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8a4478d7:

    # hi "Rin, stop trying to dodge me or I'll leave."
    hi "琳，別再躲我了，否則我會走的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3382
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a61bcc4a:

    # rin "Okay."
    rin "好吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3384
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b3376472:

    # hi "Do you want me to leave?"
    hi "你想讓我走嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3389
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7a4f3897:

    # rin "Are you still angry?"
    rin "你還在生氣嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3391
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_9f1fab98:

    # "It took us - or was it only me? - ten seconds to swamp the conversation into this."
    "我們只用了——或者只是我？——十分鐘就把對話引到了這一步。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3393
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1bf70863:

    # "I wish we could erase the past, or failing that, forget all about it."
    "我真希望我們能抹去過去，或者至少能忘記。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3395
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a5e21d72:

    # "I've wished for that more than once in the last few months."
    "在最近的幾個月裡，我已經不止一次地這麼希望了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3397
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8e367d4b:

    # hi "Let's put that aside for the time being, all right?"
    hi "我們暫時別提那個了，好嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3402
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e787f564:

    # rin "If you say so."
    rin "如果你想的話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3404
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1fc2aff8:

    # hi "I do. So… what's wrong?"
    hi "我想。所以……出什麼問題了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3406
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_f071e6cb:

    # hi "Sae and Nomiya were not too happy that you just ran off yesterday."
    hi "紗枝和野宮對你昨天跑掉的事不是太開心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3408
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b7034cb6:

    # hi "You left them in quite a pinch, and I suppose the teacher wants some kind of an explanation."
    hi "你離開的時候挺匆忙的，我猜老師想要個解釋什麼的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3410
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b87a1272:

    # hi "It seemed like you just threw out everything you had worked for. And I don't get why."
    hi "像是你把先前努力的一切都拋下了。我也搞不懂為什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3415
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_bcc87ff2:

    # rin "Did I make a mistake?"
    rin "我做錯了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3417
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b5b2603f:

    # "My reprimanding and her flat answer go so much against the usual expectations and presumed interactions that it might just as well be somebody else talking."
    "我的指責和她平白的回答顯得那麼矛盾，錯開了常識和期望，以至於它們顯得像是別的人在談話一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3419
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_23734b94:

    # "Neither of us is like we used to be, this stiff, constricting feeling I get every time I look at Rin nowadays seems to be mirrored in her own behavior."
    "我們都不像從前那樣了，每次我看琳時，那種僵硬，受束縛的感受也似乎開始在她的身上顯現出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3421
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_db9eab9c:

    # "I hate things that go irreparably wrong. Ever since February, I have hated them."
    "我討厭那些變成不可挽回錯誤的事。自從二月之後，我就開始恨它們了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3423
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_edbaad66:

    # "What can I say?"
    "我還能說什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3425
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1456a0d8:

    # "Her question is trailed by a compelling, quizzical stare that makes me sigh and frown."
    "她的問題之後還拖曳著一道逼迫般的疑惑目光，讓我不禁皺眉嘆氣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3427
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_57d59b05:

    # "Conversations nobody wants to have are the worst."
    "誰都不想繼續下去的那種談話是最糟的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3429
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8dc8cb6d:

    # hi "I don't know. I mean, it's not the end of the world but it probably was pretty stupid."
    hi "我不知道。我意思是，倒不是說這是世界末日什麼的，不過可能是挺蠢的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3434
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_23b82067:

    # "She responds with a sigh of her own, although hers is not nearly as heavy as mine was."
    "她用一聲自己的嘆息作了回答，雖然那聲嘆息不像我的那麼沉重。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3439
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_41f678a6:

    # rin "I just couldn't do it."
    rin "我就是做不了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3441
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d773584d:

    # hi "But… why? What's wrong?"
    hi "但是……為什麼？出什麼問題了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3446
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d5db3a09:

    # "A pause, a furrowed brow, a quiet voice."
    "她頓了頓，皺起眉頭，聲音很輕。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3448
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_813fbe53:

    # rin "Let it be, Hisao."
    rin "就讓它這樣吧，久夫，別問了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3450
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_db6d9338:

    # rin "I don't think I can really explain it in a way that would make sense."
    rin "我覺得我沒法用能讓人聽懂的方式解釋。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3452
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_03f39121:

    # "Yeah, Rin doesn't want to have this conversation either. That may be for the better."
    "沒錯，琳也不想進行這次對話。可能這樣最好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3454
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7e09a6bb:

    # "But how rare of her, to admit that even she has some kind of limits."
    "但是她竟然也承認自己是有極限的了，真是少見。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3456
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6e18c75e:

    # "I always thought Rin was all but ignorant of her tendency to get distracted, so much that she inadvertently obfuscates everything she says."
    "我還以為琳完全不知道自己容易被分神的毛病，所以她總是在不經意間就把那些她說出的話變得晦澀難懂。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3458
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3460
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_646a5472:

    # hi "You never explain {b}anything{/b} in a way that would make sense."
    hi "你從來沒用能讓人聽懂的話解釋過{b}任何事{/b}的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3465
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6e44563b:

    # rin "Nobody else has ever asked me to."
    rin "從來都沒人讓我那麼做過。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3469
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3472
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_cafeb753:

    # n "I guess that's how it is."
    n "我猜事實就是這樣，沒法改變。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3474
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_23323e1b:

    # n "But I always wanted to make sense of you, to find out who you are."
    n "但我總是想要聽懂你，想要弄清你到底是誰。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3476
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c243b672:

    # n "I still want to, can't you see?"
    n "我現在依然如此，你看不出來嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3478
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_eabec665:

    # n "…"
    n "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3480
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5256755c:

    # n "I know you can't."
    n "我知道你看不出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3482
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6625e57c:

    # n "But I do."
    n "但是我能。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3484
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_545e50c4:

    # n "Is that why I keep this up? It pains you as much as it pains me. It's unlikely to be of any use to either."
    n "這就是我一直繼續下去的原因嗎？但它傷你像傷我那樣深，或許這也是徒勞的"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3486
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_300fc010:

    # n "We did things and said things that can't be undone."
    n "我們總是去說、去做那些沒法被完成的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3488
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5c30b55f:

    # n "It's as if… you and me being close to each other just hurts us both, but we still deliberately keep doing it."
    n "就像是……我和你互相接近，只是為了傷害對方一樣，但我們卻依舊刻意去繼續那麼做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3490
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7d209e62:

    # n "Isn't that silly?"
    n "很蠢吧？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3492
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_2c4bc0a6:

    # n "Even now, I can see how you force yourself to respond even though you owe me nothing."
    n "就連現在，我也能看出你在逼迫自己回答，哪怕你什麼都不欠我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3494
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_2e0c4c6a:

    # n "Even if it's hard to talk about things like this."
    n "哪怕談論這樣的事非常痛苦。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3496
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_651e1241:

    # n "Why?"
    n "為什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3501
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_28de4337:

    # nvl clear
    # hi "Why is it that you paint?"
    nvl clear
    hi "你為什麼要畫畫？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3508
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0bb0fa31:

    # rin "I… because I don't know what else I could do."
    rin "我……因為我不知道自己還能做什麼了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3510
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_800cc3cb:

    # rin "It's like this feeling that there is no choice, that it's the only possibility."
    rin "像是感覺我沒有別的選擇，這是唯一的可能性。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3515
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0bf234f7:

    # rin "Like when there are only watermelon-flavored popsicles left in the store but you need to eat a popsicle."
    rin "像是商店裡只有西瓜味的棒冰了，但是你又想要吃棒冰。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3517
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_2ee37a8f:

    # "Her poor metaphor aside, she didn't really answer anything. If possible, this makes even less sense than not knowing."
    "除開那個糟糕的比喻之外，她沒有真正回答什麼。如果可能的話，那這比一無所知更讓人困惑"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3519
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_aaa5eb21:

    # hi "But… if you don't want to paint…"
    hi "但是……如果你不想畫畫……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3524
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1c175781:

    # rin "Not like that. You had to come to this school even though you probably didn't want to have a heart attack."
    rin "不是那樣的。你也必須來學校，雖然你之前可能不想心臟病發作。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3529
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_611f9eb6:

    # "She pauses, frowning as if something in what she said didn't please her."
    "她停下了，皺起了眉頭，像是自己的話中有東西讓她不高興了一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3534
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6c42b26d:

    # rin "At least I think you wouldn't."
    rin "至少，我覺得你不會。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3536
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8e545a1e:

    # "Her careful follow-up is followed in turn by another, shorter pause with another, smaller frown."
    "她小心翼翼地補上一句，接下來又是一個短暫的停頓，又是一次微微皺起的眉頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3541
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_3973e3e4:

    # rin "Would you like to have a heart attack?"
    rin "你會想要心臟病發作嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3543
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_aa41265d:

    # hi "No, I wouldn't and I didn't want to."
    hi "不，我不會，而且我確實不想。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3548
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_75127094:

    # rin "But you're doing fine, aren't you? Or are you still sad about it?"
    rin "但是你現在很好啊，不是嗎？還是你還是很傷心？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3550
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_291d8cab:

    # "Rin's question makes me realize that I haven't really thought about my illness for weeks."
    "琳的問題讓我意識到我已經很多個星期沒去想自己的病了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3552
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_fab79964:

    # "Aside from chugging down my medication every day there has been no need to concern myself with my broken heart, which I'm only thankful for, really."
    "除了每天把我的藥吞下去以外，我沒必要去操心自己的心臟，對此我真的很慶幸。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3554
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_f7e0cd3b:

    # "Getting to know new people, a new school, a new town… a new life, it all has caught me and made the past fade away."
    "接觸新的人，新的學校，新的城鎮……一個新的生命，所有的這些都讓我忙碌不堪，以至於過去漸漸消失了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3556
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_dfc88b52:

    # hi "No… heh, I guess even I can't dwell on the past indefinitely."
    hi "沒有……嗯，可能就算是我也不能永遠抓著過去不放。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3561
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_10596138:

    # rin "See? Even watermelon doesn't really taste bad if you have to eat it."
    rin "看到了嗎？如果你必須去吃的話，就算是西瓜嚐起來也不壞的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3563
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_88845d6c:

    # "Her half-nonsensical closure seems to put an end to the subject in Rin's mind, so I just nod in uncertain confirmation."
    "琳半不可理喻的總結似乎讓這個話題在她的腦袋中結束了，所以我也只有不確定地點了點頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3565
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_4:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3567
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_5:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3569
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7225b402:

    # "There are two kinds of silences: awkward ones that you want to break, and comfortable ones that you don't mind."
    "有兩種沉默：那種你必須打破的尷尬沉默，還有那些你不介意的愜意沉默。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3571
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1d71e413:

    # "The first kind is bad, because it makes your thoughts go awry. Like mine do, now."
    "第一種很糟糕，因為它會讓你的思路走入歧途。就像我現在這樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3573
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d1bf587e:

    # "Looking at Rin makes me feel bad."
    "看著琳，我感覺很糟。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3577
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3580
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7a3f251e:

    # n "{vspace=30}I don't want to feel like this."
    n "{vspace=30}我不想這樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3582
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c0d056e5:

    # n "Looking at Rin makes me feel… exhausted. I really tried my best, she tried to… I have no idea."
    n "看著琳時，我感覺……精疲力竭。我真的已經盡力了，她想要……我不知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3584
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_da93884c:

    # n "But we ended up like this, and she ended up screwing up her exhibition opening."
    n "但我們卻變成今天這樣，她還弄砸了自己的畫展開幕式。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3586
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_fa1ac8c6:

    # n "It feels like we are at a dead end."
    n "感覺像是我們已經走投無路。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3588
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4d95f641:

    # n "There is no direction to continue to."
    n "前方沒有新的方向了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3590
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a609c6da:

    # n "I reached out for her yesterday, thinking it would be the last time."
    n "昨天我試圖去和她溝通，心想那會是最後一次。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3592
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_24374079:

    # n "She walked away."
    n "但她轉身走了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3594
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_60bcbc14:

    # n "'I want to be me.'"
    n "我想做我自己。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3596
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_eebff0d0:

    # n "What the heck does that even mean? Rin, if anyone, is most definitely herself."
    n "但那到底是什麼鬼意思？在所有人中，琳是最像她自己的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3598
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e3a9b01f:

    # n "I feel kinda relieved that I am not the one to blame, but this still grates on my mind."
    n "我不是那個該被怪罪的人，這讓我有些鬆了口氣，不過還是有些頭疼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3600
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7455413a:

    # n "Why did she run away? It didn't make sense yesterday. It doesn't make sense today."
    n "為什麼她要跑走？昨天的事真是讓人匪夷所思，今天的事也一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3602
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_87aefa77:

    # n "The things she said feel like they should make sense but they just don't, to me."
    n "她說的那些話讓人感覺像是有道理的，可我就是沒法理解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3607
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6dacf797:

    # nvl clear
    # hi "You know, about that thing you just said…"
    nvl clear
    hi "知道嗎，那些你剛說的事……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3614
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_14826801:

    # rin "Which one of them?"
    rin "哪一個？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3616
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_20b7af2e:

    # hi "Umm… painting… Sae said something like that to me before… that a true artist does not paint because she wants to, but because she {b}must{/b}."
    hi "呃……畫畫……紗枝從前對我說過類似的話……她說一個真正的藝術家不是因為想要畫畫才去作畫的，是因為她{b}必須{/b}去那麼做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3618
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a4b67d9f:

    # hi "And I've been wondering about what she said. Why do artists {b}have{/b} to paint?"
    hi "我一直在想她為什麼要那麼說。為什麼藝術家們{b}必須{/b}去畫畫？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3620
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_18296262:

    # "My question is probably pretty stupid. At least Rin looks at me in the blank way that seems to say so."
    "我的問題可能聽上去挺蠢的，至少琳看著我的那種茫然方式似乎證明了這一點。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3625
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_195bf102:

    # rin "I don't know. Am I an artist?"
    rin "我不知道。我是個藝術家嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3627
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_fa95ba56:

    # hi "Well, you paint stuff and you have an exhibition too. I'd say you qualify."
    hi "這個嘛，你畫東西，還有個畫展。我覺得應該算。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3632
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c4aaa318:

    # rin "I think I still don't know, but okay."
    rin "我覺得我還是不確定，不過好吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3634
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_77d41dff:

    # "The thinking pause that follows seems to last for half an eternity."
    "她接下來思考時的停頓讓人感覺似乎延續了半個世紀。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3636
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d21be6f0:

    # "Unlike most people, Rin doesn't flavor her thinking pauses by body language or saying 'like' or 'umm' or anything."
    "和大多數人不一樣，琳不會用肢體語言，或是”像是“，”呃“之類的東西去裝點自己思考時的沉默。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3638
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_74ece31c:

    # "I've noticed that I might prefer her way. The usual way even annoys me, as if people were so infatuated by the sound of their own voice they just have to keep making some noise even when they are just thinking what they could say next."
    "我發現自己可能更喜歡她這種方式。通常的那種方式常讓我厭煩，就像人們是如此迷戀自己的聲音，以至於他們在思考接下來該說些什麼時，也必須要發出點聲音。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3640
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0715462c:

    # "Rin just… comes to a full stop while she is thinking. It's disconcerting, because reacting to people spacing out is always hard, but she comes off as less obnoxious."
    "而琳……琳思考的時候總是徹底停止運轉了。有些讓人窘迫，因為應對發呆的人總是很難，不過她那麼做時不是很煩人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3645
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ee0f3b45:

    # rin "I think I want someone to see what's inside me. Not the way doctors and serial killers do."
    rin "我覺得我是希望有人能看到我的身體裡面。不是像醫生和連環殺手那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3650
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4ceaf127:

    # rin "The way that doesn't make me feel lonely."
    rin "像是能讓我感覺不再孤獨的那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3655
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_10d8b645:

    # rin "This is what you call metaphorical, you see."
    rin "你看，這就是你說的那種打比喻。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3657
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_083951c2:

    # hi "Please don't lecture me about self-evident things."
    hi "拜託不要教訓我這麼不言而喻的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3662
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_14f860e5:

    # rin "It's not self-evident that this is self-evident."
    rin "這事的不言而喻不是不言而喻的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3664
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a097d013:

    # hi "So, you present a painting to someone and expect him to magically see a glimpse of your soul?"
    hi "意思是，你想給一個人看一幅畫，然後指望他能神奇地瞥見你的靈魂？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3669
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_dde8910c:

    # rin "It's not like that. It's just a little like that but not really. Don't you understand?"
    rin "不是那樣的。有一點點像那樣，不過不是。你不明白嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3671
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5e864c48:

    # hi "I do… and I don't."
    hi "我明白……也不明白。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3673
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e9f88ef6:

    # hi "You know, I feel a little bit of despair every time you ask that question."
    hi "知道嗎，每次你問那問題的時候，我都變得更絕望一些了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3678
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_aba56c2b:

    # rin "What question?"
    rin "什麼問題？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3680
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4317b1d6:

    # hi "About whether I understand you or not."
    hi "我理不理解你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3682
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_513f47b2:

    # "She seems almost surprised at my clarification."
    "我的回答似乎讓她吃了一驚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3687
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_386e0709:

    # rin "Oh, it's not really a question. It's one of those kind that you don't have to answer."
    rin "噢，那其實不是個問題。是那種你不用去回答的問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3689
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1096c39f:

    # hi "Rhetorical."
    hi "修飾性疑問。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3694
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_bebbe0dc:

    # rin "Yeah, that's the word, a question that is not a question is a rhetorical question. How nice."
    rin "對，就是那個詞，一個不是問題的問題就是修飾性疑問。真好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3696
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4fab62b6:

    # rin "That reminds me, it doesn't really make sense. What kind of a question is one that isn't a question?"
    rin "我突然想起來，那其實是矛盾的。什麼樣的問題會不是問題啊？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3698
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4490b910:

    # hi "A rhetorical one."
    hi "修飾性疑問。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3700
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_843b5534:

    # rin "What kind of an answer is an answer that doesn't answer anything?"
    rin "什麼樣的回答是一個什麼也回答不了的回答？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3702
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e023ff8d:

    # hi "Is that a rhetorical question?"
    hi "這是個修飾性疑問嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3707
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_92a01500:

    # rin "You are not funny."
    rin "你一點都不好笑。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3712
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_eed4370b:

    # rin "But if you don't like it, would you like me to say something else instead?"
    rin "不過，如果你不喜歡聽的話，想要我換句其他的話說嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3717
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_66c7fa1d:

    # rin "I don't have any good ones though. How about… 'Your pants are on fire?'"
    rin "但是我沒什麼好東西可說的。想想……”你的褲子著火了“怎麼樣？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3722
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_bda4e8c8:

    # rin "This can be our secret language."
    rin "它可以做我們之間的祕密話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3724
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7682797e:

    # "Rin's honest-to-goodness silliness, made twice more ridiculous by the fact that I know she is dead serious, derails me like it always does."
    "琳那種誠實至極的傻，然而事實是她是完全嚴肅的，這讓我的荒謬感翻了倍，像往常一樣讓我的思想脫了軌。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3726
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_dba20ae4:

    # "It's like some kind of a safety lock to prevent me from becoming too much of a worrywart, dragging even my own thoughts off the ground where they should be."
    "就如同一個防止我變得太杞人憂天的安全鎖，把我的思想從著實的地面上提了起來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3728
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_05a783f6:

    # "It makes me smile confusedly, but only on the inside."
    "我在內心裡困惑地笑了，不過沒有表現出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3730
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4de286af:

    # "Even though the corners of my mouth are not drawing into a grin, I'm still impressed by her ease of wrecking any attempt at being too serious."
    "雖然我沒有笑，但還是被她防止事情變得太嚴肅的能力折服了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3732
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7881bdf2:

    # "Could she (should she will so) forget and ignore things that bug her, things that bother her?"
    "她能忘掉、忽視掉那些煩擾她的事嗎（如果她願意的話）？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3734
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0e0e5e33:

    # "Could she (should she will so) be free of whatever burden being her means?"
    "她能擺脫一切做她自己帶來的壓力嗎（如果她願意的話）？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3736
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_37e75b58:

    # "Or am I the only one who feels burdened by being myself?"
    "還是我才是唯一那個因為做自己而感到壓力的人？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3738
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5d7bd46a:

    # hi "No thanks."
    hi "不了，多謝。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3740
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_213b0650:

    # hi "But still, the times when I feel that I am on the same page as you are pretty rare."
    hi "不過，我很少感覺自己和你在同一頁上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3742
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b4eb455a:

    # hi "It feels like… there is this huge gap and sometimes you just go to the other side, and I don't… have any way to reach to you from where I am."
    hi "感覺像是……有一道很寬的溝壑，有的時候你就邁到了另一邊，但是我沒法……沒有任何從我站著的地方去觸到你的辦法。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3744
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_222dda68:

    # hi "It's like you are in some completely different place at times."
    hi "像是有時你在一些完全不同的地方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3746
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d2a3094c:

    # hi "Even though you are right here."
    hi "哪怕你其實就在這兒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3748
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_112ac131:

    # "That's right."
    "沒錯。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3750
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_13d325fb:

    # "There is an insurmountable discontinuity, an imaginary glass wall that blocks comprehension from happening."
    "總是有一道無法逾越的斷層，一道想像中的玻璃牆，阻擋了一切理解她的嘗試。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3752
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_18f58ea5:

    # "There might be such a gap between any two people, but with Rin, it feels more tangible."
    "或許任何兩個人之間都有一道這樣的溝壑，可對於琳而言，那溝壑似乎是一個實體。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3754
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6a8ac072:

    # "Rin does not react to my thoughts, not to the ones I uttered aloud nor the ones I did not."
    "琳沒有對我的想法做出回應，不論是那些我說出來的，還是沒說出的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3756
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_fba2ac6a:

    # hi "It's even worse with art."
    hi "藝術就更糟了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3758
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_588ba655:

    # hi "I'm not very good at art, I admit it."
    hi "我不是很擅長畫畫，我承認。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3760
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_9359a0b9:

    # hi "I joined the art club 'cause I thought it could be interesting."
    hi "我加入藝術社團是因為我以為會有意思。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3762
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_07a3eee5:

    # hi "And I guess it is. I like art, I like your art too, but just like with you, I can't comprehend it."
    hi "可能確實如此。我喜歡藝術，也喜歡你的畫，但就像是你一樣，我沒法理解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3764
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a90459f9:

    # hi "And I'm pretty sure nobody really can."
    hi "而且我很肯定其實沒人能真正理解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3769
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_63627b63:

    # "This seems to worry her slightly."
    "這似乎讓她有些擔心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3771
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b1e4b14a:

    # rin "Do you think so?"
    rin "你真這麼想嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3773
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ec0c608c:

    # hi "Yeah. I guess that art is meant to be interpreted, not understood. That's how I'd put it."
    hi "對。我猜藝術應該是被解讀的，不是被理解。至少我是這麼想的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3778
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_892c793d:

    # rin "That's a sad thought."
    rin "這想法好悲傷。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3780
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_63321a7e:

    # hi "I guess it might feel like one."
    hi "我猜也是的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3782
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_178e1309:

    # hi "Does it make you feel sad for yourself?"
    hi "讓你為自己傷心了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3787
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0db8c15b:

    # "Rin thinks about this for a while, and then shakes her head surprisingly vehemently."
    "琳想了一會兒，然後搖了搖頭，出人意料地猛烈。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3792
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e3bbb7e3:

    # "The first thing she focuses her eyes on afterward is me."
    "那之後，她第一眼去看的東西就是我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3794
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_931bfb86:

    # "Both of these things make me glad, and relieved."
    "這兩件事都讓我有些開心，而且鬆了口氣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3796
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_bd15c7c3:

    # hi "That's good, isn't it? Anyway, you should go see the teacher and apologize properly."
    hi "這是好事，對吧？總之，你應該去見見老師，好好道個歉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3798
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1f693936:

    # hi "I think he is worried about you."
    hi "我覺得他在為你擔心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3800
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_61ea2e1f:

    # hi "Can you do that?"
    hi "可以嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3805
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a07805c3:

    # "This time, she nods her head."
    "這一次，她點了點頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3809
translate zh_hant a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8f5ac796:

    # "Only, it's not as vehement."
    "只是，沒那麼激烈了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3819
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_0a716e6b:

    # "The hallway is empty, almost intimidating."
    "走廊裡空蕩蕩的，幾乎有些嚇人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3821
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1bacdced:

    # "Nomiya's 'office' is the art classroom at the other end of the third floor hallway."
    "野宮的“辦公室”就是三樓過道盡頭的藝術教室。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3826
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_125fc35a:

    # "Our steps echo disturbingly. The atmosphere is unlike on a normal afternoon. It feels like the school knows that nobody will be coming back for a month, too."
    "我們的腳步聲令人不安地迴盪著。今天的氣氛不像是個通常的午後，彷彿連學校也知道今後的一個月裡沒人會回來了一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3828
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_dbce099b:

    # "The door is open, but not very inviting."
    "門開著，不過沒有多少歡迎的感覺。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3830
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_6aff6df4:

    # hi "I'll… um, wait outside."
    hi "我就……呃，在外面等著好了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3843
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_6dc07af5:

    # "Nodding barely noticeably, Rin strides in without stopping, and naturally, without knocking."
    "琳難以察覺地點點頭，直接走了進去，和往常一樣沒敲門。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3845
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_86657f4b:

    # "Maybe that's why it takes a few seconds before I hear the teacher's voice from inside."
    "可能這就是為什麼我過了幾秒鐘後才聽見老師的聲音從裡面傳來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3847
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_fc6734c8:

    # no "There you are!"
    no "你總算來了！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3849
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "你好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3851
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_2e34d48b:

    # "A conflict arises: should I stay here or go somewhere else?"
    "我內心一陣糾結：我該待在這裡，還是去別的地方？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3853
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5a13c96e:

    # "I'm not sure if I even want to eavesdrop on them."
    "我不覺得自己想要偷聽他們的談話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3855
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3861
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e426c925:

    # "Manners lose to curiosity, and so I stay close enough to listen in."
    "我的禮節向好奇心屈服了，所以離得近了一些，好聽聽裡面在說什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3863
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_4a190024:

    # "Their voices echo in the hallway, but no matter."
    "他們的聲音迴盪在走廊裡，不過沒關係。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3865
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a48f9e1d:

    # "There is nobody around, save for me."
    "附近除了我以外，沒一個人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3869
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_7c75511a:

    # no "Dear girl, what on Earth were you thinking, leaving like that on the big night?"
    no "好姑娘吶，你到底在想些啥，在這麼重要的晚上像那樣給走了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3871
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ba978e60:

    # rin "I couldn't say anything."
    rin "我什麼都說不出來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3873
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_de7a30cd:

    # "Compared to Nomiya's scolding tone, Rin sounds awfully quiet and withdrawn."
    "與野宮叱責的語氣相比，琳的聲音聽起來非常安靜，有些畏縮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3875
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_bced366c:

    # "Her words seem to drown under his."
    "她的聲音似乎要在他的聲音下溺死了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3877
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c5162c6d:

    # no "I have to say, I am very disappointed in you, Tezuka."
    no "我得說，我對你非常失望，手塚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3879
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e3306e7d:

    # rin "It was no good at all."
    rin "那事一點也不好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3881
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_35f4098e:

    # no "Never mind all the things I did for you, but what about Sae? What about all the guests who wanted to meet you?"
    no "都別提我為你做的那些事了，你為紗枝想過嗎？還有那些想要見你的客人？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3883
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_f107b085:

    # rin "There was nobody. Even Hisao…"
    rin "根本就沒人。就連久夫……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3885
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_04098c4e:

    # no "You have embarrassed us very badly, Tezuka."
    no "你可讓我們丟大了，手塚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3887
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1ccaed51:

    # no "Reputation is what counts, surely you know that?"
    no "名聲才是最重要的，你肯定也知道吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3889
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1a57d6f6:

    # rin "It's all right. I don't need it."
    rin "沒關係。我不需要的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3891
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_f52bc1ca:

    # no "'Don't need!' What do you think you know?"
    no "”不需要！“你以為自己知道什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3893
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_94db79fe:

    # "Rin's replies only seem to agitate the teacher more, his voice rising with every sentence."
    "琳的回答似乎僅僅讓老師更憤怒了，他的音量隨著每一句話上升。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3895
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_3a0f219c:

    # no "The path of an artist is a thorny one, I'll tell you that! Thorny!"
    no "藝術家的道路充滿艱難險阻，我給你說！艱難險阻！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3897
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_60478bcc:

    # no "You have to see the big picture! There will be bad times and good times!"
    no "你必須要有長遠的目光！有壞的時候，也有好的時候！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3899
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e566c382:

    # rin "Things are like they are. It'll be all right even—"
    rin "事情就是它們本來是的樣子。不會有事的，就算——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3901
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_254659b4:

    # no "You might now think that it's oh so wonderful and easy, but how far would you have gotten without me?"
    no "你現在可能覺得噢，好棒好容易，但如果沒我的幫助，你以為自己能走多遠？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3903
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_acbc9b1f:

    # no "I won't always be there for you!"
    no "我不會一直在這幫你的！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3905
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5eb00a09:

    # no "When you lie on the floor of your minuscule room, your rent three weeks late, your mind blank for the fourth week straight, then you will wish that you had listened to old Nomiya a bit more."
    no "當你躺在小房間的地板上，房租遲交了三個星期，第四個星期裡腦海一片空白時，你就會希望自己當初多聽些聽老野宮的話了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3907
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_0378543b:

    # no "When you keep measuring how the shadow of your chair becomes longer over the spring because that's all your lethargy allows, maybe that's when you will start caring about your career!"
    no "當你睡不著覺，只有瞪著椅子，看那影子在春天慢慢變長時，可能你就會開始考慮自己的事業了！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3909
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_f1bae754:

    # rin "That doesn't matter."
    rin "沒關係。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3911
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_4de65275:

    # no "Your resolve is not enough."
    no "你的決心還不夠。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3913
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_42cfea3b:

    # rin "I am not a resolved person."
    rin "我不是個有決心的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3915
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_29e17732:

    # no "You are not a resolved person…"
    no "你不是個有決心的人……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3920
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_7ae46f04:

    # no "Then tell me, why… why… WHY DID WE GO THROUGH ALL THIS TROUBLE IF IT AMOUNTS TO A MOSQUITO'S SHIT?"
    no "那告訴我，為什麼……為什麼……為什麼我們要弄出這麼多麻煩，如果這些都只不過是坨蚊子屎的話！？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3922
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_edfbf6aa:

    # "Oh dear, the teacher blew a fuse."
    "噢，糟糕，老師爆炸了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3924
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_56a2d361:

    # "Him yelling at Rin makes me feel bystander's guilt. If I had gone with her, maybe he wouldn't have gotten so angry."
    "他對著琳怒吼，讓我感覺有種旁觀者的愧疚。像是如果我和她一起進去的話，可能他就不會這麼生氣了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3926
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a5adb09f:

    # "If I had not let her run away, he wouldn't have gotten angry in the first place."
    "如果我沒讓她跑走，他可能一開始就根本不會生氣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3928
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1e75dc9d:

    # "I still could go and save her… I don't think I can."
    "我還是可以進去救她……但我不覺得自己真的可以。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3930
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_713fbfe8:

    # "I was the same. I yelled at Rin too, and I'm feeling all the more embarrassed about it now."
    "我也是一樣的。我也曾對著琳大吼過，現在我感覺更加愧疚了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3932
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5687b0c3:

    # "I felt justified to vent my anger at her face just because… just because I felt it was her fault that I was so frustrated."
    "我覺得自己朝她發泄怒火是天經地義的，只是因為……因為我以為那是她的錯，而且我那時是那麼挫敗。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3934
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_35f8da37:

    # "I was no more justified than the teacher is."
    "我並不比老師更有理由。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3936
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3938
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_44dea617:

    # "A terrible silence sets upon the hallway."
    "一陣可怕的沉默蓋過走廊。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3940
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_2c47ca41:

    # "Rin does not have anything to say to Nomiya."
    "琳什麼話也沒對野宮說。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3942
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a79943d3:

    # "Whether she has run out of answers or she knows that arguing would only make him angrier is anyone's guess."
    "到底是因為她已經沒了回答的話，還是她明白爭論只會讓他更加憤怒，就沒人知道了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3944
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_0862d794:

    # "The teacher has nothing more to say either, it seems, or maybe he just ran out of breath."
    "聽上去，老師也無話可說了，或許只是因為他喘不過氣來了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3946
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a51bbc4a:

    # "For a moment, I imagine the two of them just staring at each other, one full of red-hot anger, the other full of… yes, what?"
    "有那麼一刻，我想像著他們兩人瞪著對方的樣子，一個怒髮衝冠，另一個……是啊，另一個怎樣？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3948
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_54a036f9:

    # "I can't tell how Rin feels, not before, not now."
    "我沒法想像琳的感受，從前不行，現在也一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3950
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_4f0fb537:

    # "Teacher seems to expect Rin to say something too, but since she doesn't he finally continues in a quieter, but not less angry voice."
    "老師似乎也在指望琳能說些什麼，可既然她沒有，他終於用一種安靜一些，卻同樣惱怒的聲音說話了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3952
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_3e8f651d:

    # no "What worth is there in doing so much work if the outcome is… nothing?"
    no "如果結果只是……什麼都不是，那做那麼多還有什麼意義？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3954
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_cc6452f4:

    # "Still, Rin will not say anything."
    "依然，琳一句話也不說。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3956
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_fd187c3a:

    # no "I'm sorry. I shouldn't have gotten so excited."
    no "抱歉，我不該那麼激動的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3958
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_b4229233:

    # "He does not sound sorry at all. Rather, his tone is cold and sharp, like he was spitting the words out of his mouth."
    "他聽上去一點也不抱歉。相反，他的語調冰冷又尖銳，像是在把詞從嘴裡啐出來一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3960
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_55965a48:

    # no "It seems that I was expecting too much. You are not an artist after all."
    no "看來我的期望太高了，你畢竟不是個藝術家。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3962
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_927c5f46:

    # "Yeah, not sorry at all."
    "沒錯，一點也不抱歉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3980
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e79fa0b3:

    # "He storms out of the club room and down the stairs without noticing me."
    "他氣勢洶洶地衝出了社團教室，下了樓梯，看也不看我一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3982
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_faf1ce19:

    # "After he is gone, I peek carefully inside the classroom."
    "他走後，我小心地看了教室裡一眼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3988
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ebabbe35:

    # "Rin is left standing there, in front of the teacher's desk."
    "琳還在那兒，站在老師的桌前。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3993
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c880ca0d:

    # rin "I couldn't say I am sorry."
    rin "我沒法道歉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3995
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c43e5a6e:

    # "She says it into the humid air of the classroom, not to me."
    "她是對著教室裡潮溼的空氣說的，不是對我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3997
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_311ce79f:

    # "But since the room won't answer her, I will have to."
    "不過既然教室不會回答她，我只有開口了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3999
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_cf06bdb3:

    # hi "That was unfair of him… He was angry, but still…"
    hi "他太不公平了……雖然他很生氣，但是……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4001
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5f883ced:

    # "I can't decide how to end my sentence. Disdaining the teacher feels like disdaining my own behavior from two days ago."
    "我不知該如何把句子說完。蔑視那老師，就像是在蔑視我兩天前的行為一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4003
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_b2363998:

    # "Stupid, but correct in hindsight."
    "愚蠢，但事後看來卻是正確的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4008
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e87bad7e:

    # "Rin won't answer, staying petrified where she stands, so I walk up to her."
    "琳不願回答，石化一般地站在那裡，於是我走上前去。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4010
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_040a94e2:

    # "She stood up for herself. In a way. I didn't expect that."
    "她維持了自己的立場。從某種意義上說來，我沒有料到。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4012
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_01114343:

    # "I can't determine whether it's unbecoming or not, but either way, she did it."
    "我不知道這是不是有些不妥，不過不論如何，她都那麼做了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4014
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c7fc8fb0:

    # "Against me, she never did."
    "但她從來沒對我那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4016
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_98782b07:

    # "I sort of wish she had, maybe I would not feel this bad then."
    "我卻有些希望她那樣做過，或許那樣一來，我就不會感覺像現在這樣糟糕。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4018
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ac23e748:

    # "Lately, it really seems that I've been wishing for all kinds of things."
    "最近，我真的總在希望各種各樣的事情發生。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4020
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_79b8b7de:

    # hi "Rin?"
    hi "琳？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4025
translate zh_hant a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1149e5d6:

    # rin "Go away."
    rin "走開。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4036
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a86f8847:

    # hi "Why… what are you saying?"
    hi "為什麼……你說什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4041
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_328e6f5e:

    # rin "You're angry with me too, right?"
    rin "你也生我的氣了，對不對？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4043
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_17a09b54:

    # rin "I thought you were my friend. I thought he was, too."
    rin "我還以為你是我的朋友。我以為他也是。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4045
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_10398a35:

    # "Her voice is unlike I've ever heard it, it's bitter, sharp like needles, and she keeps staring pointedly at her toes."
    "我從沒聽過她用現在的聲音說話，苦澀，而且尖得像針，同時她一直盯著自己的腳趾。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4047
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_33b1994b:

    # hi "I don't think it's about that."
    hi "我不覺得是那個意思。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4049
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a68d17f2:

    # hi "He wanted you to be something you are not. And…"
    hi "他是想讓你變成你不是的東西。而且……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4054
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_b76c58e4:

    # "I take a deep breath and finally catch her eyes in my own, locking our gazes."
    "我深吸一口氣，她的目光終於對上了我的，鎖在了一起。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4056
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8581e44e:

    # hi "…I'm sorry. I wanted us to be something else too… more than friends."
    hi "……對不起。我也想讓我們變成另外的……比朋友更多。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4058
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_af8ee4ad:

    # hi "Maybe that's why I couldn't contain myself and became so frustrated, just like the teacher did."
    hi "可能就是因為這個，我才一直不滿足，變得那麼沮喪，就像是老師那樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4063
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6e9f3c4c:

    # rin "What more? There is nothing more to me than me, that's all I am. I don't understand that."
    rin "什麼更多？我只有我，沒有更多了，我只有這些。我不明白。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4065
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_2f5449fc:

    # "Well… the answer should be obvious, right?"
    "嗯……答案應該是很明顯的，不對嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4067
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_eb839590:

    # "I remember myself, thinking of the purpose of friendship. To put up with everything and anything, to be there for your friend."
    "我還記得自己曾思考友情的意義。去面對和應付任何事，去和你的朋友站在一起。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4069
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_aed08c9f:

    # "Did I fail as a friend, thinking it could be a stepping stone for something else?"
    "我做朋友的嘗試是失敗了嗎，因為我以為它會成為另一種東西的墊腳石？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4071
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d7849ebe:

    # "Maybe because of those thoughts, I didn't manage to put up with things, to keep it together."
    "或許就是因為這些想法，我才沒法面對和應對這些，沒法撐住不倒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4073
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d8455860:

    # "As outrageous as Rin is and was, I shouldn't have let myself get caught into that, especially when I started feeling the way I did towards her."
    "雖然琳曾經是、現在也是令人難以忍受的，但我不該被那影響，尤其是當我已經開始對她產生那樣的感情後。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4075
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_451e526f:

    # "So, did I fail?"
    "所以，我是失敗了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4077
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3e4b8c69:

    # "That's what her eyes seem to ask."
    "她的眼睛似乎也在問同樣的問題。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4079
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4081
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_4edfc2ce:

    # hi "I'm sorry, Rin."
    hi "對不起，琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4083
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_77849431:

    # hi "I might not be able to be your friend."
    hi "我可能沒法做你的朋友。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4085
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_fb09bfa5:

    # hi "I don't think I could ever be a good friend to you."
    hi "我不覺得我對你來說有可能當一個夠格的朋友。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4087
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_45f8c1f5:

    # "I say these things because they are true, not because one of us would like to hear them."
    "我把這些話說出來了，因為它們是真的，不是因為我們兩人中有一個想要聽它們。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4089
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_08731ab3:

    # "But they are something that must be said."
    "但它們是必須被說出的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4091
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_71028a93:

    # "The finality of my words creates a shaking silence, for what could either of us add to that?"
    "我的話語創造出了一陣搖搖欲墜的沉默，那樣的話，讓我們怎麼可能接下去？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4093
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4098
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_898bc629:

    # rin "Why? Why does all this happen?"
    rin "為什麼？為什麼要發生這些事？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4103
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0015c967:

    # rin "People are doing things I don't ask for and don't want and everyone keeps getting angry at me, I have no idea what is going on any more and can't stop feeling like I want to run away from everything…"
    rin "人們總是做我沒要求而且不想要的事，而且每個人都不停生我的氣，我已經沒法搞懂發生什麼了，總是覺得想從所有這些東西面前逃走……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4108
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8a8d11ae:

    # "She shuts her eyes tight and breathes out deeply, calmly."
    "她緊緊閉上了雙眼，平靜地深呼出一口氣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4113
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_9e0b5f21:

    # "When the eyelids open, all I can see is dark green desperation."
    "當她的眼瞼睜開時，我只能看見深深的綠色絕望。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4115
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_f56118e1:

    # rin "{b}I have no idea what's wrong with me!{/b}"
    rin "{b}我不知道自己出了什麼問題！{/b}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4117
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a9fa7df7:

    # "Her frenetic outburst stupefies me for a moment, and for a heartbeat we just gaze into each other's face."
    "她突然的狂亂髮作讓我呆了片刻，一聲心跳掠過，我們什麼都沒做，只是看著對方的眼睛。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4119
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6dd64e05:

    # "Seeing her confused eyes desperately looking for answers from mine only makes me sad, because I know I have none."
    "她困惑的雙瞳不顧一切地想要從我的眼睛裡搜索出答案，讓我感到悲哀，因為我知道自己是什麼答案也沒有的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4121
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6bb4f611:

    # hi "I don't know either."
    hi "我也不知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4123
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d7caf8fa:

    # hi "But you know, you yourself said that things are not right nor wrong."
    hi "但是，你自己也說了，事情是沒有對和錯的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4125
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_400d49b1:

    # hi "They just are."
    hi "它們只是它們本來的樣子而已。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4127
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_02a828c3:

    # hi "You either accept them, work to change them or give up."
    hi "你要麼接受它們，試圖改變它們，要麼放棄。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4129
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_c0932a9f:

    # hi "It's not that I hate you, or that teacher Nomiya does."
    hi "不是因為我恨你，野宮老師也一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4131
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8aaa5d46:

    # hi "I just… think that I am the kind of person who gives up when he feels he can't go on."
    hi "我只是……以為我是那種感覺自己沒法再繼續下去、就會放棄的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4133
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3c2a5195:

    # hi "And even if you hate it, this… this is… how things are."
    hi "就算你恨它，這也是……這是……事情就是這樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4135
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_29d2ca31:

    # "I'm saying pretty cruel things but I can't stop myself, the words keep rolling off my tongue with slow, hard certainty."
    "我正在說出一些很殘酷的事，但我沒法停止，詞和句不斷從我的舌頭上滾落，緩慢，而又堅定不移。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4140
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_9cdb683d:

    # "I can see them hitting Rin almost like physical blows."
    "我可以看出它們像是真正的拳頭一樣打在了琳的身上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4142
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_f8ae645e:

    # "As the wetness gathers into the corners of her eyes, they are still wide with the shock of rejection."
    "一道溼意在她的眼角聚集，但那雙眼睛依舊大大睜著，滿是拒絕和震驚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4147
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ee8600d6:

    # "As the tears start rolling down her pale cheeks, she does nothing to stop them."
    "當眼淚從她蒼白的臉頰滾落時，她沒有去阻止它們。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4149
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_11c5de7b:

    # "As they fall down on the floor one by one, she stands still, staring at me with a gaze full of hollow disbelief."
    "它們一滴滴地落在地面上，而她依然站著，望著我，無法相信的目光裡空洞無光。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4151
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_879b98dc:

    # rin "…"
    rin "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4153
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_1e44f061:

    # "But reality catches up."
    "但是終於，現實闖了進來。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4163
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d303f825:

    # "Rin slumps forward as if she was deflating, and buries her face as deep in my shirt as she can."
    "琳向前倒向我，像是泄氣了一般，她把臉貼在我的襯衫上，儘可能地埋向深處。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4165
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_05d6787e:

    # "Rin is heavy and featherlight when I support her weight."
    "我支撐著琳的身體，她輕如羽毛，同時又非常重。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4167
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_4eaad8de:

    # "She doesn't really sob or bawl, just leans against me, letting her tears burn through my shirt into the skin underneath."
    "她沒有啜泣或慟哭，僅僅是靠著我而已，讓她的眼淚灼燒過我的襯衫，直接滲進下面的皮膚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4169
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_20566d5f:

    # "And I let her, bringing my hand around her shoulders in a clumsy hug that does no good to comfort her."
    "我任她那麼做，用手環繞住她的肩膀，形成了一個笨拙的擁抱，沒法安慰她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4171
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_71466c97:

    # "I can feel Rin's vertebrae against my fingertips, like hard and jagged reminders of how messed up things are."
    "我的指尖能感到她的脊椎，顯得堅硬又凹凸不平，像是在提醒我們事情糟成了什麼樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4173
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e97643b3:

    # "Her slim shoulder quivering against my palm is a pitiable sight, and the hopelessness of being part of the cause for Rin's sadness keeps shredding my heart."
    "她纖細的肩膀顫抖著，貼向我的手掌，令人憐憫，我卻是讓琳變成這樣的一個原因，這是沒法擺脫的事實，一點一點地撕著我的心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4177
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4180
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d368b86c:

    # n "{vspace=120}To make a girl cry is the most despicable thing to do."
    n "{vspace=120}讓一個女孩流淚恐怕是最卑劣的事了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4182
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_aba60d25:

    # n "{vspace=30}Even Rin. Especially Rin."
    n "{vspace=30}哪怕是琳。尤其是琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4184
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_4a1d6033:

    # n "{vspace=30}Behind that veil of aloofness, Rin is just a human being too."
    n "{vspace=30}在那層曾經冷漠超然的面紗下，琳也只是人類而已。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4186
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_cad5f2ab:

    # n "Just as confused, scared and lost as any of us is."
    n "和我們中的任何一個一樣惘然、害怕和迷茫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4188
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_687c3d91:

    # n "Most of the time it seems that there is no rhyme or reason for what Rin does and says, but for once, I think I really understand how she feels."
    n "大多數時候，琳的話、還有她做的事，似乎沒有節奏也沒有原因，但是這一次，我想我真正了解她的感受了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4190
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_b4ed80bb:

    # n "{vspace=60}But no words can express it, and no words can make it better."
    n "{vspace=60}可是卻沒有話語能將它表達出來，也沒有話語能讓它變得好一些。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4194
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4203
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d0080779:

    # n "{vspace=150}So wordless we stay, quietly waiting for her tears to run out."
    n "{vspace=150}所以我們繼續無言地留在這裡，靜靜地等她的眼淚流盡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4205
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_024094a7:

    # n "Time passes agonizingly slowly, even the lazy specks of dust floating in the air seem to pause into a standstill."
    n "時間的流逝緩慢得讓人痛苦，哪怕那些倦怠地飄浮在空氣中的塵埃似乎也凝固了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4207
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_2254b4a9:

    # n "The obligatory wall clock is ticking distractingly from above the door."
    n "門上的鐘義不容辭地滴答走著，讓人不禁分神。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4209
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e7e72875:

    # n "I decide against counting the seconds, because it would make them feel longer."
    n "我不再去數秒了，因為那隻會讓它們變得越來越慢。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4211
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_16d51601:

    # n "{vspace=60}…"
    n "{vspace=60}……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4216
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4221
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_b60b0732:

    # "Eventually Rin stirs a little and still smothering herself against my chest, mutters into my shirt."
    "終於，琳有了一點動靜，雖然她依然把自己悶在我的胸前，對著我的襯衫咕噥著。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4223
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ed876ef2:

    # rin "Let me be here for a while."
    rin "讓我再在這待一會兒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4228
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_351c6e6c:

    # rin "Please, Hisao."
    rin "求你了，久夫。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4230
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a31911cf:

    # rin "Just give me a little while."
    rin "就給我一點時間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4232
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6fef3343:

    # "A soothing deluge spreads into my consciousness, the knowledge that while being here for Rin is all I can do for her, that's all she wants right now, even after all we've gone through."
    "一條撫慰人心的河流漫進了我的意識中。雖然我能做的只是為了琳站在這兒，但我卻突然意識到，在此刻，她需要的也只有這些，就算我們已經經歷了所有的那些事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4234
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_21ce94c5:

    # hi "Sure."
    hi "當然可以。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4236
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3af3c03c:

    # "So she stays there."
    "於是她留在了這裡。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4238
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_f04f3643:

    # "But I still can't bring myself to draw her closer so I could embrace her properly."
    "可我還是沒法讓自己把她拉得更近，讓我能好好地抱她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4240
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_93c1815a:

    # "It's because doing it would just make me so sad that I don't know if I could bear it."
    "因為那麼做一定會讓我非常悲傷的，我不知道自己能不能忍受。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4244
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4247
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_2b137976:

    # n "{vspace=60}The realization that we might never really be able to become what we want to be for the other crystallizes into my mind as a diamond-hard enlightenment."
    n "{vspace=60}我意識到我們或許永遠也沒法真正成為對方想讓我們成為的人，這想法在我的腦海中結成了冰晶，變成了一道鑽石一般堅硬的覺悟。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4249
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_dc129c07:

    # n "A pang surges through my heart like an electric shock."
    n "一陣痛苦像電流一樣傳過了我的心臟。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4251
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_1ea11879:

    # n "It's painful."
    n "讓我難以忍受。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4253
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0804e70b:

    # n "This clarity… hurts."
    n "這種清晰真是……很疼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4255
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ecb7b8b8:

    # n "What can we be for each other? What meaning is there for us to desperately cling to each other even though it seems so futile?"
    n "我們能為對方成為什麼？這一切到底有什麼意義，為什麼我們要這麼絕望地握住對方不放，就算徒勞無用？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4257
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_81c3655e:

    # n "What should I say to Rin? How can I make her feel better?"
    n "我能對琳說什麼？怎麼才能讓她感覺好些？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4259
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0493a82f:

    # n "I do not know any of those things, and I fear knowing them would only hurt more."
    n "這些問題，我沒有一個答案，而且我感覺知道它們只會讓我被傷得更深。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4261
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_f8b35533:

    # n "Forcefully, I push all of that out of my mind because I don't want to be thinking of hurtful truths."
    n "我用力把所有的這些都推出了自己的腦海，因為我不願再去想令人痛苦的事實了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4263
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3a4b7b00:

    # n "My thoughts calm down soon enough, the sadness disperses until all that is left is me and Rin and the tender feeling of her warmth and softness against my chest."
    n "很快，我就平靜下來，悲傷漸漸消散，直到最後只剩下了我和琳，還有她的溫暖和柔軟貼在我胸前的溫柔感受。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4265
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d938d1c3:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}When did I fall in love with her?"
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=60}我什麼時候愛上她的？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4269
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_64f7d26f:

    # n "I can't remember, but I'm certain it was way before the warm touch of her lips on my own, on that orange-colored afternoon when she was sick with cold and I went to see her because of unclear reasons."
    n "我記不清了，但我能肯定，那是在她把溫暖的脣貼上我的嘴之前，很久之前。那天下午一片橘色，她因為感冒而臥床了，我因為說不清的原因去探望了她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4271
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6f5c9eeb:

    # n "Her carefree attitude, the air of otherness around her, all the things that make Rin herself… those things captured me with irresistible force."
    n "她無憂無慮的態度，那種特立獨行的氣質，所有的一切都讓琳成為了她自己……這些東西以一種不可抗拒之力捕獲了我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4273
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3238220f:

    # n "The way she could take in anything and everything giving it only the value she herself placed, weighing all things fairly and without prejudice, seeing the world as she wanted."
    n "她有那種吸收一切事物、並把它們冠以她自己所定價值的能力，能不含偏見地評判任何事，以自己的眼光去看世界。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4275
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_31a9f0ec:

    # n "This is something I could never do, and Rin was probably more of a muse to me than anything ever was to her."
    n "這些都是我永遠都做不到的，琳或許沒有掌控靈感的詩神，但對我來說，她可能就是我的繆斯。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4277
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_cd935f1e:

    # n "She seemed so free to me, truly a free spirit. While I, constantly worrying about everything, seemed so inhibited that it was almost embarrassing."
    n "在我眼中，她是如此自由，一個無拘無束的靈魂。而我卻總是擔心著每件事，都快成了一個習慣，幾乎讓我感到尷尬。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4279
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0e32f4d7:

    # n "Maybe that's why I latched so tightly on to Rin, trying to get inside her world that was so different from my own bleak life."
    n "或許這就是為什麼琳如此吸引我，我想要走進她的世界，那個和我荒涼的生活如此不同的地方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4281
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e5657d2b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}Before I noticed it, that irresistible force had pulled me dangerously close to her, but it turned out to be way too alien for me."
    nvl clear
    n "{vspace=60}還沒等我回過神來，那種無法抵抗的力量就把我拽向了她，近得危險，結果我發現那個世界對我來說太陌生了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4285
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_792d39a9:

    # n "And I had forgotten Newton, of all things."
    n "我偏偏忘了牛頓。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4287
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_23d2f7d9:

    # n "The gravitational force is inversely proportional to the square of the distance between the objects…"
    n "引力是和物體間距離的平方成反比的……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4289
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e04bb72e:

    # n "So if two people feel something for each other…"
    n "所以說，假如兩個人相互之間產生了某種感情……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4291
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ceccb846:

    # n "Heh."
    n "呵。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4293
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_770c0e91:

    # n "Even though feelings are not governed by the constants of the universe, I can't help thinking that for some time now I've been a satellite to Rin's brightly shining planet."
    n "就算情感不受宇宙間萬物理論的束縛，我也忍不住有這想法一段時間了：我成了一顆衛星，圍繞著琳光彩溢目的星球旋轉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4295
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6e1b8abb:

    # n "{vspace=30}Planet Rin."
    n "{vspace=30}琳之星。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4297
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_c32b9b24:

    # n "{vspace=30}The thought makes me almost laugh, she really does seem to be from another planet at times, minus green skin and possibly some tentacles."
    n "{vspace=30}這想法幾乎讓我笑出聲來，她有時真的像是來自另一顆星球一樣，淺綠色的皮膚，可能還有一些觸手。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4302
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4307
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_5955a6a7:

    # "Perhaps because of my stifled laughter, Rin pulls away and I let her go, feeling the cold when her warmth goes away, and slight embarrassment for letting my thoughts run wild like that."
    "或許是因為我被悶住的笑聲，琳離開我的懷抱了，我也放了手，感到冷氣開始在她的溫度消失後入侵，同時還有一點尷尬，我剛才竟像那樣胡思亂想。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4309
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_9a30057f:

    # "I credit that as Rin being a bad influence on me, while being glad at the same time that she can't read thoughts for real."
    "這得怪琳，她對我產生了不好的影響，我很慶幸她沒有真正的讀心能力。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4311
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_19219675:

    # "Rin's bitter tears have dried up, and she looks a little more like herself again."
    "琳苦澀的眼淚已經幹了，她看起來又像是她自己了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4316
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_12e51051:

    # "The lost look in her eyes is still there though. Her gaze wanders around restlessly before stopping at me."
    "雖然那種迷失的眼神依然在她的眼裡。她的目光躁動不安地四下搜尋著，最後落在了我身上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4318
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_adacdb45:

    # rin "What happened just now?"
    rin "剛才發生什麼了？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4320
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0223cbca:

    # rin "Can you tell me?"
    rin "你能告訴我嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4322
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_87c4a6de:

    # hi "What? What do you mean?"
    hi "什麼？你指什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4327
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a8947010:

    # rin "I cried."
    rin "我哭了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4329
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ad8f6622:

    # "She says that hesitantly, as if not believing it herself."
    "她猶豫地說道，像是自己都不相信一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4331
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8a2b55c1:

    # hi "Yes…"
    hi "沒錯……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4333
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4335
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_cfc1f971:

    # "She keeps staring at me, as if pleading guidance so that she wouldn't have to feel so lost."
    "她繼續望著我，猶如在渴求得到指導，這樣她就不會如此迷惘了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4337
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4342
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d66e33b2:

    # rin "Why?"
    rin "為什麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4344
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_349e3329:

    # hi "You were sad."
    hi "你在傷心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4346
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3f88c33e:

    # hi "Is that what you want me to say? But isn't that obvious?"
    hi "你是想要我說這個嗎？但，那不是很明顯麼？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4351
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_be7c1a33:

    # rin "I don't know. It feels weird to cry."
    rin "我不知道。哭的感覺好怪。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4353
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_bf4cb129:

    # hi "What? I don't believe it. I mean, everyone does that. It's nor—"
    hi "什麼？不敢相信。我是說，每個人都會這樣。這很正——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4355
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_52d15ee0:

    # "I bite my tongue before I finish my argument about normality."
    "我住了口，沒把這句關於正常的話說完。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4357
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_bf6a1b2a:

    # "Norms do not apply to the person I'm talking to."
    "正常是不能用來形容這個我正在與之對話的人的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4362
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_db33f92d:

    # rin "It always felt so wrong, different from what is in me. Like I couldn't really tell what I felt."
    rin "但它一直都感覺弄錯了，和我身體裡的東西不一樣。像是我沒法形容自己的感受。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4364
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8bf039d1:

    # rin "So I started thinking that maybe I don't know what I'm feeling. Maybe it's me who is wrong—"
    rin "所以我開始想，也許我不知道自己有什麼感受。可能是我自己錯了——"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4366
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_f27b9343:

    # rin "I thought those kinds of things."
    rin "有時我會這樣想的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4371
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_c406ac59:

    # rin "I thought… that painting was enough because it felt that I did at least that right."
    rin "我以為……畫畫已經夠了，因為我覺得自己至少把它做對了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4373
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_4b28f38d:

    # rin "That all that is inside me could become a picture if I tried really hard. And it could."
    rin "我還以為我身體裡的所有東西都會變成一幅畫，只要我非常用勁地去試就行。它們確實可以的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4375
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8c7a520e:

    # rin "But it doesn't feel like it's enough any more. Because if nobody else can see that, I will still be alone."
    rin "但現在我感覺它們不夠了。因為如果沒人能看到它們，那我就還是孤獨一人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4380
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_b6c80e2a:

    # rin "Was it wrong to try? Everyone got really angry at me for that."
    rin "去試一試是錯的嗎？每個人都因為這個對我生氣了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4384
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8095eb63:

    # "I've rarely heard Rin say this much at once before."
    "我之前很少聽見琳一下子說那麼多話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4386
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_29fdde40:

    # "Once she finishes, she simply shuts up, looking so neutral that it's hard to believe she just said what she did."
    "她剛說完，就簡單地不吭聲了，看上去非常中立，讓人難以相信她剛才才說過那些話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4388
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a444f39f:

    # "I don't know what to think."
    "我不知道該怎麼想了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4390
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_4:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4392
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d23c6534:

    # "Rin was desperate for someone to look at her paintings, and somehow see right through them into her soul, to understand her feelings…"
    "琳絕望地想要別人去看她的畫，能以某種方式穿透它們，直接看進她的靈魂裡，理解她的感受……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4394
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_953b2b5c:

    # "Because… she felt she could not express them in any other way?"
    "因為……她感覺自己沒法用任何其他方式去表達它們？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4396
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_c0ba05f9:

    # "How can one say whether that is right or wrong?"
    "你怎麼能說這是對還是錯的？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4398
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_dd6ad7cf:

    # "Could it be that all this time she's been trying to reach out to me like I've tried to reach out to her?"
    "有可能一直以來，她都在試圖觸到我，就像是我在試圖觸到她一樣嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4400
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_5:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4402
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_04c6ce66:

    # "I sit down on a desk to think, and to rest my legs that kept us both standing for a long while."
    "我坐到了一張桌子上，思考著，順便休息一下自己的腿，剛才它們一直在支撐我們兩個人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4406
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_2c896449:

    # hi "You know, when I read a good book or look at a starry sky or whatever, sometimes I too feel something… profound, like a… shoot, I don't know how to describe it."
    hi "這個，當我讀一本好書，或者看星空之類的東西的時候，有時我也會感到一種東西……深不可測，像是……哎，我不知道該怎麼形容。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4408
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6a9a2fd2:

    # hi "But the instant I try to put it into words I feel that I lose something, it doesn't feel as real, as true as it did inside my head."
    hi "但一旦我想要把它說出來，我就感覺有東西被弄丟了，它變得不像是真的一樣，不像是在我腦袋裡那樣真實。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4410
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_48a460c2:

    # hi "It feels a bit phony. Damn, even what I just said felt phony."
    hi "感覺有些假。該死，就連我正在說的東西都感覺像是假的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4412
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e682e6a2:

    # "I offer a smile that is meant to be between funny and self-deprecating, but Rin doesn't react."
    "我笑了笑，本來是為了自嘲和開玩笑，但琳沒有回應。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4414
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_b054bfeb:

    # hi "Anyway…"
    hi "總之……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4416
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_107c4e75:

    # hi "It might be that nobody can ever express their true feelings so that others understand."
    hi "可能從來就沒人能表達出自己真實的感情，讓別人理解過。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4418
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_9b1b6d9c:

    # hi "Reality has no chance of living up to what someone has inside their head."
    hi "現實是不可能和一個人腦海裡存在的東西比的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4420
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6a9bf8c7:

    # hi "Nothing can match that. Not even your paintings, except maybe for you."
    hi "沒什麼可以和它比。哪怕是你的畫，除非是對你自己而言。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4422
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_34fe76fc:

    # hi "But I suppose you can't keep everything inside, you'd explode for real then."
    hi "但我猜，你也不可能把一切都藏在心裡，那樣的話，你真的會爆炸的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4424
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ee6be804:

    # hi "What I'm trying to say is… I don't think it's wrong to express your feelings, even if you use painting as your conduit."
    hi "我想說的是……我不覺得表達你的感受有什麼錯，哪怕你是在用畫畫作為中介。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4426
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ef735d30:

    # hi "You just can't expect people to understand you any better than they would if you did it any other way."
    hi "你只是不能指望人們會更加了解你而已，不會比你用其他的方式更容易讓人了解。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4428
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8a82649e:

    # hi "In fact, you can't expect people to understand you at all."
    hi "事實上，你可能根本就不能指望人們會理解你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4430
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_02f41c2d:

    # hi "It's because everything is so subjective. You see the world the way you do, but it's different from everyone else."
    hi "因為所有事都是客觀的。你以自己的方式去看世界，和其他所有人都不同。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4435
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6448d5be:

    # rin "But isn't that terrible?"
    rin "但是，那不是很可怕嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4437
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d7aeaf20:

    # hi "I guess it is, in a way."
    hi "我覺得，從某種意義上來說是的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4439
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_6:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4444
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3e9cf840:

    # "She frowns, looking probably as stricken as she can. Which is not much, but it's enough for me to understand that Rin is not particularly happy."
    "她皺起了眉，做出了一幅可能是她最受打擊的模樣。也就是說，不怎麼明顯，不過已經夠讓我明白琳不是很開心了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4446
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e87bd7d2:

    # rin "I think it might make me sad after all."
    rin "我覺得這還是會讓我感覺悲傷的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4448
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6845161a:

    # hi "Yeah. I know."
    hi "是啊，我知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4450
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6c4db884:

    # hi "I wish I could do something to help it."
    hi "我也希望我能做些什麼幫你。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4452
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_413175ba:

    # "I don't think I sound bitter, even though I am, a little."
    "我不認為自己聽上去苦澀，雖然我確實如此，有一點點。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4454
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8bee9134:

    # "This is my problem. I cannot be what Rin wants for her. And for the same reason, she can't do the same for me either."
    "這就是我的問題，我沒法成為琳想讓我成為的人。出於同樣的原因，她也沒法為我做一樣的事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4456
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_7:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4461
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3b349d31:

    # "She makes a difficult face, carefully trying to pick the words she wants to say."
    "她做出了一幅費力的表情，小心地試著挑出自己想要說的話。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4463
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d42dc0de:

    # "So Rin has times when it's hard to say anything, too."
    "那看來，琳也會有找不到話說的時候。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4468
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_87c9fe2f:

    # rin "It can't be helped, I think."
    rin "我覺得，那是沒人能幫得了的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4473
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_99177fda:

    # rin "…but… if you say that…"
    rin "……但是……如果你那麼說……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4478
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_dd4a67b1:

    # rin "It makes me feel a little better."
    rin "讓我感覺稍稍好一些了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4480
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_8:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4482
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_019de7b4:

    # "It's funny how some seemingly irrelevant things are the most significant ones at times like this."
    "真是好笑，在這種時候，那些貌似無關緊要的事卻變成最重要的了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4484
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a64f84b7:

    # "Like how Rin's voice is very very small, barely audible when she says that."
    "例如當她說那話時，聲音有多微弱，幾乎輕不可聞。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4486
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a2c417aa:

    # "And how even her short bangs can cover her eyes when she looks downwards."
    "還有她向下看時，那短短的劉海遮住她眼睛的方式。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4491
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_5751c244:

    # "And how they can't cover the deep red color rising on her cheeks and all the way to the tips of her ears."
    "它們沒法遮住她臉頰上泛起的深深紅暈，一直染到了她的耳朵尖。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4493
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_59a25684:

    # "They turn into a very interesting shade of red."
    "變成了一道非常有趣的紅色陰影。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4495
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_549bdf94:

    # "A deafening silence follows."
    "隨後，是一陣讓聽覺麻木的寂靜。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4497
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_3d3c20fc:

    # "It's very awkward, as if I saw something that wasn't meant to be seen, even if it wasn't on purpose."
    "感覺非常尷尬，像是我看到了某種不該被看見的東西一樣，雖然我完全是無意的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4499
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_c6c92ca9:

    # "I don't know what to say to that, but I keep feeling like I should know."
    "我不知該說些什麼，可又一直覺得，我應該是知道的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4501
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_c0e8f418:

    # "She doesn't either."
    "她也不知道。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4503
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_1038150c:

    # "Still, it feels like there is no momentum to lose even if we keep silent."
    "不過，就算我們保持沉默，我們間的空間也沒有失去一點動能。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4505
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_52d28473:

    # "Like we have some weird, wordless connection that would hold even so."
    "就如同我們之間有了一種古怪的無言聯繫，就算如此，也不會斷裂。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4510
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_557cc958:

    # "Rin keeps shifting her weight from one foot to the other restlessly, looking everywhere around the room except at me."
    "琳不斷把重心從一隻腳轉到另一隻，看向房間裡的每一處，除了我。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4512
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0a7e78aa:

    # "She is the one who finally breaks the spell."
    "最終打破沉默的人是她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4517
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0b2a8ec0:

    # rin "Can we go? I don't want to stay here."
    rin "我們可以走了嗎？我不想再留在這兒了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4519
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_1f756dac:

    # hi "Oh, yeah, of course. Where?"
    hi "噢，行，當然可以。去哪？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4521
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_53ce0290:

    # "My reply is covering my nervousness as badly as her question is covering hers."
    "我的回答根本沒法掩飾自己的緊張，就像是她的問題沒法掩飾她的緊張一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4526
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0218adc5:

    # rin "You can go wherever you like. I want to sleep. I haven't really slept for a few weeks."
    rin "你想去哪裡都可以。我想要睡覺。我已經幾個星期沒好好睡過了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4531
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_73997863:

    # rin "It feels like there is a flock of light blue butterflies inside my head. It makes it hard to think properly."
    rin "感覺像是有一羣淺藍色的蝴蝶在我的腦袋裡一樣。讓我很難好好想事情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4536
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_b2ffe712:

    # rin "The kind that you think is too blue to really exist, like Emi's panties this morning."
    rin "那種你覺得藍得不可能存在的蝴蝶，就像笑美今天早上的內褲一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4562
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_476897b1:

    # "She shakes her head, and I almost expect a couple of ultramarine-colored Morphos to pop out of her ears."
    "她搖了搖頭，我幾乎要盼著看到幾隻海藍色的大閃蝶從她的耳朵裡撲騰出來了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4567
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_1ed49f2d:

    # "A small smile tugs upwards the corners of her mouth."
    "她的嘴角勾起了一個小小的微笑。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4569
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_2350ff9c:

    # rin "That reminds me. The blue, not the panties."
    rin "想起來了。我是說那藍色，不是內褲。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4574
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_38a3db9d:

    # rin "The word for a flock of butterflies is a swarm. I looked it up."
    rin "說很多蝴蝶的那個詞是蝶羣。我去查了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4576
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_4ed50446:

    # "That makes my eyebrow rise into a questioning arch."
    "這話讓我疑惑地揚起了眉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4578
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e18b1573:

    # hi "Why don't you use it then?"
    hi "那為什麼你不用它？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4583
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_dd415c81:

    # rin "I like the other word better."
    rin "我更喜歡另一個詞。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4585
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_28e0f0ee:

    # "Why look it up in the first place, then?"
    "那為什麼還要去查它？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4587
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8fa37f5c:

    # hi "Then you should use it, right?"
    hi "那你就應該用它，不是嗎?"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4592
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_0a07eb38:

    # "She nods and falls silent, her gaze escaping mine to the side, attracted by the dark orange sunlight refracting from the windows."
    "她點點頭，陷入了沉默，目光向一邊逃去，被窗戶上反射的深橘色陽光吸引了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4594
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_4ff98111:

    # "We stay like that for a little while: me silently looking at her silently looking out of the window."
    "我們像這樣保持了一會兒：她不出聲地望向窗外，我默默地看著她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4596
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a3c26168:

    # hi "Hey… you all right now?"
    hi "嗨……你現在好些了嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4601
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_cfdd5168:

    # "She glances at me from the corner of her eye, looking wistful again. The sunlight's reflection doesn't betray any more of her inner feelings."
    "她從眼角看向我，又露出了那種憂思的神情。反射過來的陽光沒揭露多少她內心的情感。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4603
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_5e2df80d:

    # rin "I'll need to think about that."
    rin "我要想一想。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4605
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_e5b3dad1:

    # "I want to continue this conversation, grasping at those straws that she finally revealed to even exist."
    "我想把這談話繼續下去，抓住那些她終於顯露出來的稻草。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4610
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_4b4035a8:

    # "But Rin is looking out of the window so absentmindedly that I know she won't be responsive in any way that would make sense."
    "但琳看向窗外的模樣顯得如此心不在焉，以至於我深知她是不會以任何合理的方式去回答我的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4612
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_029ac659:

    # "It's like some kind of defense mechanism of hers, to avoid being sensible."
    "這就像是她的某種防禦機構，防止她變得通曉事理。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4614
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d2c707f8:

    # "Her mind is like a butterfly in itself, always fluttering somewhere away whenever it's stirred."
    "她的頭腦本來就像只蝴蝶，總是一被驚動，就飛走了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4616
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_8e04dc58:

    # "Just when I thought I could see behind her veil, she jumps out of my reach again."
    "我剛以為自己能看到面紗後的她，她就又消失了在我碰不到的地方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4618
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_f7df2706:

    # "Maybe that's just how Rin is."
    "或許琳就是這樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4620
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_84b3b28c:

    # "Maybe that's something I should just accept to get some peace of mind."
    "可能我應該接受這一點，換取一點內心的平靜。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4622
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "好吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4624
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_5ff982ec:

    # hi "I'll walk you back to the dorms then."
    hi "那我送你回宿舍吧。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4629
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_a0d0eacd:

    # rin "Thanks."
    rin "謝謝。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4634
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_d88922f3:

    # rin "Really."
    rin "真的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4641
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6c3b0809:

    # "The empty hallways of the school devoid of its students feel very lonely."
    "教學樓的走廊裡空無一人，顯得非常寂寞。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4643
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6000513c:

    # "Less than one hour after the summer vacation began, the building seems to be deserted, and all that intrudes on the stillness of the hallways are our footsteps."
    "離暑假開始還不到一小時，整棟樓似乎就被遺棄了，只有我們的腳步聲在擾亂沉寂的走廊。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4645
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_6905c3de:

    # "The change is sudden, but it shows how the building is just an empty shell, dead without its students and teachers."
    "變化是突然而來的，讓人意識到教學樓不過是一個空殼而已，沒有了學生和老師，也就沒有了生機。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4647
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_adbfa89c:

    # "It's as though the school has become a private world for only the two of us, a desolate place filled with silence and chalk dust."
    "學校似乎已經變成了一個只屬於我們兩人的世界，遺世獨立，飄蕩著寂靜和粉筆的粉塵。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4653
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_28b47659:

    # rin "I think I have to change."
    rin "我覺得我必須改變。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4655
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_c8a91802:

    # "She says it out of the blue while we walk down the staircase from the third floor, still managing to feel like she is mirroring what I was thinking just before."
    "她忽然間這麼說，我們正從三樓的樓梯走下，依然讓人感覺她是在反映我剛才的想法。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4657
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_72471f0d:

    # hi "That's what people must do, sometimes."
    hi "有的時候人必須那麼做。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4659
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4662
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_ae118e0e:

    # n "{vspace=240}That's the last thing we say to each other that day, even though there would be so much to talk about."
    n "{vspace=240}那是我們那天向對方說的最後一句話，雖然其實我們還有千言萬語可以談論。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4664
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_dfb8e2b0:

    # n "And even those words drown in the all-encompassing silence, disappearing into the stagnant air as if they were never said."
    n "而且就連那幾個詞也被包裹一切的沉默淹沒了，消失在凝滯的空氣之中，如同從未存在過一般。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4666
translate zh_hant a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_6:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4686
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c1dc1f90:

    # "The first day of summer vacation is a disappointment."
    "暑假的第一天讓人失望。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4688
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_83c1e36f:

    # "I woke up. Water came down from the leaden sky in Biblical proportions."
    "我醒來後，只見雨水從鉛灰色的天空中傾盆而下，猶如聖經裡的大洪水。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4690
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_02317591:

    # "I was optimistic at the time."
    "我在那時還是挺樂觀的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4692
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b9437469:

    # "A quick summer shower, I thought. Torrents of rain for a few minutes, then it's gone."
    "不過是一次夏季的短雨罷了，我想。讓雨水泄幾分鐘的洪，然後它就會停了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4694
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ed6bb294:

    # "No such luck."
    "當然沒那麼好運。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4703
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_be4e215c:

    # "Rainwater is relentlessly pouring down from the blue-gray sky outside, streaming down the glass of my window in small brooks and rivers and gathering together to form miniature ponds on the walkways."
    "雨水間歇不斷地從室外灰藍色的天穹塌落，在我的窗玻璃上匯聚成了溪流，一路向下，在過道上形成了小水灘。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4705
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0167ac62:

    # "Just like it has done for the past two and a half hours."
    "已經這樣下了兩個半小時了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4712
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d88ef36c:

    # "So I've been half-assedly cleaning up in between half-assedly reading a book, packing my stuff on the side when I get bored of the first two."
    "於是，我便心不在焉地一會兒打掃一下房間，一會兒讀讀書，當我厭倦了這兩者後，就收拾一下東西。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4714
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_df831c42:

    # "The weather drags my spirits pretty down too, making it harder to do anything properly."
    "天氣讓我的心情也變得低落了，沒法好好地做任何事。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4718
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_22b52622:

    # "Something bumping quite loudly against my door rouses me from my apathy."
    "但是突然間，有東西大聲地撞在了我的門上，把我從漠然之中驚醒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4720
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c552a4ad:

    # "I hope it's not Kenji and his crazy indoors bowling alley."
    "我希望這不是健二和他的瘋狂室內保齡球。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4722
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4724
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b844a4f7:

    # "I hear no more sounds from the corridor until I walk to the door and open it."
    "一直到我走到門前打開它時，那走廊裡的聲音都沒再響起。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4734
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e1d2edbf:

    # "Rin."
    "琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4736
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ab3de4e6:

    # "I wish seeing her would evoke some more emotion in me, but for one, I'm too surprised that she came to see me and for two, she is soaking wet."
    "我希望她的身影能激起我內心的某些感情，不過首先，我太驚訝她竟會來看我了，而且，她渾身溼得一塌糊塗。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4738
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1c628974:

    # "Her uniform shirt is drenched and she is standing in a self-created puddle."
    "她的校服襯衫溼透了，讓她站在了一灘她創造出的水灘中。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4740
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a4ac716a:

    # "Droplets of rainwater are dripping from her short bangs and sliding down her nose until they fall down from the tip."
    "一滴滴雨水從她短短的劉海間落下，滑過鼻子，從鼻尖掉落。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4742
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d3ae6300:

    # "One.{w=0.7} By.{w=0.7} One."
    "一滴。{w=0.7}接。{w=0.7}一滴。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4744
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9abb5df8:

    # hi "Umm… hi."
    hi "呃……嗨。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4746
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c65cf440:

    # hi "How are you feeling?"
    hi "你感覺怎樣？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4751
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_79478467:

    # rin "Medium normal."
    rin "一般普通。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4755
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bc7af2e4:

    # "The relative questionability of her statement aside, she sure doesn't look too good."
    "撇開她有點讓人摸不著頭腦的回答不說，她看起來一點也不怎麼好。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4757
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4451b91a:

    # hi "You're all wet."
    hi "你溼透了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4762
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8de3af21:

    # rin "It's because I come from the outside. Do you know it?"
    rin "因為我是從外面來的。你知道嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4764
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_251d293f:

    # hi "Why'd you be outside? It's raining buckets out there, if you haven't noticed."
    hi "你為什麼要出來？不知道你注意到沒，外面簡直是在貓狗齊下。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4769
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bcc78a0a:

    # rin "I haven't. It's raining pretty hard though. I was on a walk."
    rin "沒有，我沒注意到。不過，外面雨倒是下得蠻大的。我剛才在散步。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4771
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4e2d34b6:

    # hi "Is this what you call 'wallowing in self-pity?'"
    hi "他們說的“在自憐裡沉浸”是不是就是這意思？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4776
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9567d639:

    # rin "Do you think I'm pitiful?"
    rin "你覺得我很可憐嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4778
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ddb58c5d:

    # hi "No, I implied that you think you are."
    hi "沒有，我是在暗示你覺得自己可憐。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4783
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d04f0b0b:

    # rin "I'm not, and rain is not a sad thing."
    rin "我不覺得，而且雨也不會讓人傷心。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4788
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_02779218:

    # rin "Don't you ever walk in the rain?"
    rin "你從來沒在雨中走過嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4790
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a13a35de:

    # hi "I do, but only with proper equipment, like an umbrella."
    hi "走過，不過都會帶著恰當的雨具，比如一把傘。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4795
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ef730b2d:

    # rin "You just need to imagine you have a blue umbrella with white stripes."
    rin "你只用想像自己有一把帶白色條紋的藍傘就可以了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4797
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_43056c15:

    # hi "It might be tough when rain is falling on my head."
    hi "雨打在我腦袋上的時候，這麼想可能有些難。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4802
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e5c65b99:

    # rin "Just imagine harder."
    rin "再用力些去想就行了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4804
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4806
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_25700211:

    # "Yeah, she definitely is back to normal."
    "沒錯，她絕對恢復正常了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4808
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_73ba8a99:

    # "Those half-sarcastic, inconsiderate remarks that really push my buttons even though she doesn't mean it, that vacant, spaced-out stare that always expects more than it gives."
    "這些半尖刻的無心回答真的讓我有些抓狂，哪怕她不是有意的。那道漠然的茫茫目光裡，期待總是多於泄露。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4810
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9b78fc7d:

    # "It's so… very much like her."
    "所有這一切都……那麼像她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4815
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9cbab9a8:

    # rin "I may need to come in. I need some help with this water and clothes I'm wearing."
    rin "我可能需要進去。我需要有人幫忙弄下這些水，還有我身上的衣服。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4817
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_932b2747:

    # "My brain quickly solves this equation, and I stumble with my words, a stark display of contrast against Rin's easygoing self-invitation."
    "我的大腦飛速地解開了這個方程式，我開始結巴，與琳隨意的自發性邀請形成了鮮明的對比。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4819
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bbcd449a:

    # hi "But, Emi…"
    hi "但是，笑美……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4824
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_409c511a:

    # "Rin shakes her head vehemently, causing water to sprinkle everywhere."
    "琳猛烈地搖搖頭，把水甩得到處都是。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4826
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c8c9c35a:

    # rin "She left."
    rin "她走了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4831
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b7457483:

    # rin "Besides she would just worry and fuss until she could not worry or fuss any more, which always takes a troublesomely long time."
    rin "再說，她也會擔心，然後大驚小怪，直到她再也不能擔心和大驚小怪為止，每次都要用好長的時間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4836
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3894ffc0:

    # rin "It's in fact longer than I want to hear her fussing, and I thought you probably are not the fussing kind."
    rin "其實比我願意聽她大驚小怪的時間要長，我覺得你應該不是那種大驚小怪的人。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4852
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8d352ed3:

    # "She slumps down on my desk with a squishy sound."
    "她跌坐到了我的桌上，發出一道溼漉漉的聲音。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4854
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_6f478650:

    # "Her soaked clothes are making the desk and everything on it wet but she doesn't care."
    "她的衣服溼透了，把桌上的每件東西都弄溼了，不過她不在乎。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4856
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4858
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_86c397ea:

    # hi "Okay. Fine. I'll help you out."
    hi "好吧，行。我幫你弄。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4860
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f2442de3:

    # hi "I have a towel somewhere. Do you want dry clothes? Is a uniform fine? I'm taller than you, but…"
    hi "我記得在哪兒有條毛巾的。你想要乾衣服嗎？校服行不行？我比你高，不過……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4865
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ef494bfa:

    # rin "Everything is fine."
    rin "什麼都可以。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4870
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e5074b89:

    # "With a little searching I find a fresh uniform and a fluffy towel from the depths of my closet."
    "我稍稍找了找，從衣櫥底部拿出了一件乾淨的校服，還有毛茸茸的毛巾。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4875
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_507a5528:

    # "The towel in one hand and the uniform in the other, I turn to face Rin again, uncertain of the next step."
    "我一手拿著毛巾，一首拿著校服，轉身面向琳，不知下一步該做什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4877
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2e80a3cc:

    # "There is something wrong with me, a normal guy would just—{w=1.0}{nw}"
    "我覺得自己出了點問題，換做一個正常人，就會直接——{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4882
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b1d5d5de:

    # rin "Stop worrying. It is not a problem."
    rin "別擔心了，沒有問題的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4884
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_07c04b46:

    # "She probably could see right through my hesitant demeanor."
    "她可能可以把我猶豫的舉動直接看透。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4886
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7d48a506:

    # "As if I was completely transparent to her."
    "像是我在她面前是完全透明的一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4888
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cfdf9dbf:

    # "I push my anxiety away and concentrate on the eight buttons lined on her shirt, just like mine has."
    "我把緊張推到了一邊，將注意力集中在她襯衫上的八顆紐扣上，和我的襯衫一樣。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4890
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_611ba244:

    # "Only the first button is an obstacle, and after getting it over I undo the others with slightly less shaking hands."
    "只有第一顆紐扣像是道障礙，當我把它解開後，再去解剩下的那些時手就沒那麼抖了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4901
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ebf3ed8f:

    # "Throwing the soaked shirt aside, I reveal Rin's pale upper body, shrouded only in her light blue brassiere which instantly reminds me of her saying it's her favorite color."
    "我把那件溼透的襯衫丟到了一旁，露出了琳蒼白的上身，只剩下一件淺藍色的乳罩，我立刻想起了她曾說這是她最愛的顏色。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4903
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1229aacd:

    # "I try not to think too much about… stuff, but it's hard not to look at her body with what I can only think of as mixed feelings."
    "我試著不去過分想……事，不過很難在看著她身體的同時不產生那些……我只能說是混合的感受。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4905
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3564b3a0:

    # "I don't know what to think of this, so I just watch her. Rin looks… brittle."
    "我不知道該怎麼想，所以我只是看著她。琳看起來非常……脆弱。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4907
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a79d2366:

    # "She is like a shell, a fragile thing just barely holding together."
    "她像是一個空殼，一個易碎的物件，勉強維持成一個整體。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4909
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_24eacbe1:

    # "Her ribs, each of them visible under her pale skin, are moving up and down in the rhythm of her breaths."
    "她的肋骨在沒有血色的皮膚下清晰可見，隨著她呼吸的節奏上下起伏。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4911
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b912e64d:

    # "Rin always struck me as quite thin, but I realize now that the manic creative period before the exhibition opening might've caused her to lose weight."
    "琳給我的感覺總是很瘦，但我直到現在才意識到那段畫展前的瘋狂創造期讓她瘦了多少。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4913
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4c0f9d7f:

    # "Did she eat properly and enough? Definitely not and probably not."
    "那時她吃得夠好夠多嗎？一定不會，或許不會。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4915
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_512d4945:

    # "This ugly, yet beautiful bare minimum of a human body that belongs to someone I care about is a contradiction of aesthetics in itself, oddly becoming of her."
    "這具醜陋，然而又美麗的瘦削裸體屬於一個我在乎的人，這個事實本身似乎就是一個審美的矛盾，但卻奇怪得非常適合她。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4917
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fa911beb:

    # "My eyes follow her collarbone to her shoulder and down her arm until the abrupt end."
    "我的目光隨著她的鎖骨移向肩膀，然後向下挪去，看過她的手臂，直到那個突兀的盡頭。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4919
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f62cfa24:

    # "No, it's less than the bare minimum, I think with a passing pang of sadness and some guilt for thinking like that."
    "不，甚至比一具瘦削的裸體還要少，我想著，一陣痛苦的悲傷稍縱即逝，隨之掠過的還有一些愧疚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4927
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2e2886ad:

    # "Her arms, degenerated into almost nothing but bone and skin due to lack of use, look very short now that the long sleeves of her uniform are not covering them:"
    "她的手臂，由於缺乏使用，已經幾乎退化成了皮膚和骨頭，現在已經沒有她襯衫的長袖子去遮蔽它們了，讓它們看起來非常短。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4929
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b6b1f8af:

    # "My lack of any negative reaction makes me think that I've actually grown pretty accustomed of the various physical abnormalities of my schoolmates."
    "但我沒有產生任何負面的感受，看來我已經漸漸習慣這所學校裡學生們的各種肢體殘疾了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4931
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3f77f8ae:

    # "I always wondered why Rin keeps her shirt sleeves long, only tying them in a simple knot at where the elbow would be."
    "我總是好奇為什麼琳要把她的襯衫袖子留得那麼長，在手肘的位置把它們打成一個簡簡單單的結。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4933
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a2392e3a:

    # "It seems a bit impractical, but then again she is not exactly the pinnacle of practicality."
    "看上去有些不實用，不過，她也確實不是一個追求實用性的楷模。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4935
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ae1daa83:

    # "Maybe she likes it, maybe it is somehow important to her. Maybe there is no deeper meaning to it."
    "或許只是因為她喜歡那樣，或許那對她很重要。或許那其實沒什麼深刻的含義。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4937
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c45528be:

    # "I feel like asking, and almost do, but Rin's miserable state requires a higher priority of my attention."
    "我想要問，而且幾乎開口了，但我更需要去操心琳的糟糕現狀。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4944
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1fb4ce3e:

    # "She's stopped talking too, after we ran out of spiky greetings."
    "她也沒再說話了，我們已經用完了尖刻的問候語。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4946
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cd0c5c06:

    # "I guess there is no need for chitchat then."
    "我猜也已經沒有寒暄的必要了。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4951
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7a3f1c40:

    # "I pick up the towel from the bed and wrap it around her head, rumpling it all over her hair until most of the rainwater is hopefully soaked into the fabric."
    "我從床上拿起毛巾，裹在了她的頭上，在她的頭髮上揉著，直到我希望大部分雨水都被布吸走為止。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4956
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_322e26f2:

    # "She peeks from below the towel at me, looking up with impassive eyes."
    "她從毛巾下瞥著我，抬頭向上看，眼光漠然自若。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4958
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8dd0858a:

    # "It looks like she wants to say something without saying it."
    "看上去像是她想不出聲地說些什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4960
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f5174080:

    # "It's that kind of a look."
    "就是那種神情。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4962
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_71051f20:

    # "But I can't read what she is thinking about from her face, so I just keep on fussing with the towel around her shoulders and hair."
    "但我沒法靠她的表情推斷出她在想些什麼，所以我只是繼續用毛巾去擦乾她的肩膀和頭髮。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4964
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d7dbf791:

    # "The silence is oppressive, terrifying."
    "寂靜顯得壓迫，讓人害怕。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4966
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7263a715:

    # "Communication between us has suddenly been reduced to the movements of my hands and the towel, and Rin swaying her body to and fro."
    "驀然間，我們之間的交流只剩下了我的手和毛巾的動作，琳來回搖著自己的身體。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4968
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bf17d8b0:

    # "My jagged breathing and her quiet breaths, trying to find a common rhythm that just is not there."
    "我的呼吸參差不齊，她的卻平穩寧靜，它們像是在試圖尋找某種就是不存在的共同節奏。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4970
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b1731e57:

    # "I think I can hear her heartbeats, or maybe they are just mine redoubled."
    "我覺得自己可以聽見她的心跳聲，不過或許它們只是我自己的心跳，被反射成了回聲。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4972
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_04263afc:

    # "As I brush a rogue strand of hair aside from her ear, Rin suddenly presses her cheek against the back of my hand."
    "當我把一縷遊離的頭髮從她的耳邊撥開時，琳突然把自己的臉頰貼在了我的手背上。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4974
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fad31190:

    # "The contact is electric, a jolt of current surging through me."
    "這種接觸就像是觸電，一道電流傳遍了我的全身。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4979
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ae2fee98:

    # "Whether she seeks comfort, warmth or just my touch I wouldn't know, but I can't help touching her back, caressing her soft cheek with my hand."
    "我不知道她是在尋找慰藉，溫暖，還是僅僅是我的觸摸，但我情不自禁地回應了她，輕輕用手撫摸著她柔軟的臉。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4981
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1651c9cf:

    # "And with closed eyes, she kisses me, on the fingers, counting the joints with her lips…"
    "她閉上雙眼，然後吻了我，將吻印向我的手指，用自己的脣一個個數著我的關節……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4983
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_671ca505:

    # "I am saddened beyond my expressive capability."
    "我悲傷得難以言說。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4985
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2dd8ebac:

    # "Here we are, a boy and girl, both in love or something like that with each other, or maybe not… and yet…"
    "我們就在這兒，一個男孩和一個女孩，雙雙墜入愛河，或是類似的事，或是什麼也沒有……但是依然……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4990
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4993
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b89577d1:

    # n "{vspace=30}Something is broken, I can feel it in me and in Rin; in the way our gazes merely brush against each other, shying away from contact; in her closed, timid posture and in my way of touching her like a china doll, afraid of shattering her delicate form."
    n "{vspace=30}有東西破碎了，我能從自己和琳身上感覺到；在那種我們的目光接觸時一掃而過的時刻，在相望時怯身而逃；在她封閉，畏怯的姿態中；還有那種我像對待一個瓷娃娃一樣觸碰她的方式，生怕打碎她薄若蟬翼的存在。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4995
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a0ffa0d1:

    # n "In how we are closer than we have ever been, yet I'm not feeling happy. It's like yesterday."
    n "我們離對方前所未有的近，可我還是沒法開心起來。宛如昨天一般。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4997
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_711737af:

    # n "When did tenderness and forlornness become one and the same word, acts of affection start invoking only longing? …How, why did we end up like this?"
    n "從什麼時候起，柔情和孤獨變成了同一個詞，愛戀的舉動只會激起渴望和憂思了？……我們怎麼，為什麼會變成現在這樣？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4999
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_52c54526:

    # n "'No, don't answer that,' I'd like to say to myself, but fighting against the omniscience of self-awareness is a lost cause."
    n "“不，別回答，”我也想這麼對自己說，但人是無法反抗無所不知的自我意識的。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5001
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_82d61142:

    # n "Still, I am here, and Rin is here, and it feels like she might be able to solve whatever problems she has."
    n "可是依然，我就在這兒，琳也一樣，而且我感覺，她或許能解決自己的問題，不論它們是什麼。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5003
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_eab49758:

    # n "And if she can, why couldn't I? Why couldn't we?"
    n "如果她能，為什麼我不可以？為什麼我們不行？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5005
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_39d92670:

    # n "It feels like taking that step is too much, too difficult, too uncertain."
    n "似乎邁出的那一步太大了，太困難，太難以預料。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5007
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3bb38949:

    # n "So for now, all I can do is dry her up so she won't get a cold again."
    n "所以現在，我能做的只有將她擦乾，這樣她不會再得感冒。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5013
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5018
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0c18ed33:

    # "I pet her head, trying to sort out the hair that refuses to be sorted out even when wet."
    "我理了理她的頭，試圖把那些就算溼了後也不願屈服的頭髮撫順。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5020
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_259d0e28:

    # "A pair of dark, glazed eyes follows my every movement."
    "那雙玻璃般的深色眼睛跟隨著我的每個動作。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5022
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_6c9a16f1:

    # hi "Pants too?"
    hi "褲子也一樣嗎？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5027
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0ce96b76:

    # "She nods an answer, leans back and spreads her legs, with a grotesquely inviting gesture that makes a nasty feeling crawl up and down my spine like a bad premonition."
    "她點點頭，向後靠去，分開了雙腿，做出了一個怪誕的邀請姿勢，讓一種骯髒的感覺如噩兆一般地在我的脊椎裡上下爬動。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5029
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a5c6a2f9:

    # "It's not enough to sober me though, as the silence is starting to make me feel detached from myself."
    "但是它還不夠讓我清醒過來，寂靜越來越讓我感覺自己正脫離自身。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5031
translate zh_hant a4_rin_wb_and_ws_059d91d3:

    # "I move automatically, without thinking even though I should; I should talk to her about this, or at least about something."
